    # "Her whimpering sounds turn to moans as she fills with the same pleasure as I. I can feel my heart beating loudly in my chest, and her own beating underneath my hand."
    "Les seves queixes es converteixen en gemecs mentre sent el mateix plaer que jo. Puc notar com em batega fort el cor bategant al pit, i el seu batec sota la meva mà."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:3743
translate ca a4_lilly_blackout_a5da68b0:

    # "I can feel her hands clasp my wrists, their grip surprisingly tight as her chest rises in overwhelming pleasure."
    "Noto com les seves mans m'estrenyen els canells, m'agafa sorprenentment amb força mentre aixec el pit quan l'aclapara el plaer."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:3748
translate ca a4_lilly_blackout_ecef5baf:

    # "More… I want more…"
    "Més... En vull més..."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:3757
translate ca a4_lilly_blackout_344279df:

    # "I can feel my chest tightening as I rock back and forth frantically, both of us entirely taken with ourselves."
    "Noto com m'estreny el pit mentre em balancejo frenèticament endavant i endarrere, tots dos completament extasiats."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:3768
translate ca a4_lilly_blackout_b3556da5:

    # "Nothing… that unusual… I just need to take deeper breaths to steady… myself…"
    "Res... inusual... Només necessito respirar més profundament per a mantenir-me... jo..."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:3788
translate ca a4_lilly_blackout_c9228094:

    # "This feeling is just… normal…"
    "Aquesta sensació és... normal..."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:3808
translate ca a4_lilly_blackout_6ad076f7:

    # hi "Aah… aaaaaaaah…"
    hi "Aah… aaaaaaaah…"

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:3826
translate ca a4_lilly_blackout_7d2fd7e4:

    # "This isn't… I can't… this pain is too much…!"
    "Això no és... no puc... aquest dolor és massa...!"

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:3837
translate ca a4_lilly_blackout_69baefc0:

    # hi "AAAAARGH!"
    hi "AAAAARGH!"

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:3841
translate ca a4_lilly_blackout_3708b73c:

    # "I stumble backwards from Lilly with unseemly haste, clumsily hitting the back of my foot against the table and falling to the ground with an unceremonious crash."
    "M'allunyo de la Lilly amb una pressa impròpia, em colpejo maldestrament la part de darrere del peu contra la taula i caic a terra amb una patacada brusca."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:3843
translate ca a4_lilly_blackout_cc4534c1:

    # "Breathing wildly, I frantically scrape at the ribbon over my eyes as I lay on my back. I have to get this off, I have to get this off…"
    "Respiro violentament, tremolo frenèticament amb la cinta als ulls mentre m'estiro boca amunt. He de treure-me-la, he de treure-me-la..."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:3852
translate ca a4_lilly_blackout_949274e0:

    # "For a moment, everything goes blank. As the rush of newfound light assaults my eyes, my breathing slows from the brink of hyperventilation."
    "Per un instant, ho veig tot blanc. Quan l'esclat de llum m'ataca els ulls, la respiració se m'afluixa després d'estar al límit de la hiperventilació."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:3860
translate ca a4_lilly_blackout_dae983a3:

    # "Seconds pass, and I carefully measure out the rhythm of my heartbeats with every ounce of concentration I can muster."
    "Passen els segons i mesuro amb cura el ritme dels batecs del meu cor amb tota la concentració de què soc capaç."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:3862
translate ca a4_lilly_blackout_9e1f86ce:

    # "My heart is… normal. It's back to normal."
    "El meu cor és... normal. Ha tornat a la normalitat."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:3864
translate ca a4_lilly_blackout_e07ee6fc:

    # "My body feels utterly bizarre as I lay dazed on the floor looking at the ceiling. The adrenaline from before is still pouring through my veins, but my mind is completely exhausted."
    "Sento el meu cos completament estrany mentre em quedo a terra mirant el sostre. L'adrenalina d'abans encara em corre per les venes, però tinc la ment completament esgotada."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:3866
translate ca a4_lilly_blackout_c0c8ac85:

    # "I prop myself up as I hear Lilly getting off the bed and coming towards me."
    "M'aixeco quan sento a la Lilly aixecar-se del llit i acostar-se cap a mi."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:3882
translate ca a4_lilly_blackout_8d13c83a:

    # li "Hisao? Are you okay? Hisao!?"
    li "Hisao? Estàs bé? Hisao!?"

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:3884
translate ca a4_lilly_blackout_3a93b4e3:

    # hi "I'm fine, Lilly. I'm… fine."
    hi "Estic bé, Lilly. Estic... bé."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:3889
translate ca a4_lilly_blackout_7a88a0a0:

    # "She gives a sigh of relief, her worried expression collapsing."
    "Sospira alleujada i li desapareix la cara de preocupació."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:3891
translate ca a4_lilly_blackout_d6fa2694:

    # "Her face afterward is the very last I'd ever wanted to see from her. It's a face I'd detested when I first saw my parents in the hospital all those months ago."
    "La cara que feia era l'última que volia veure. És una cara que detestava quan la vaig veure per primera vegada en els meus pares a l'hospital, ja fa mesos."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:3893
translate ca a4_lilly_blackout_057d1852:

    # "Pity. Lilly… pities me."
    "Compassió. La Lilly... em compadeix."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:3898
translate ca a4_lilly_blackout_7579ecdf:

    # "I just close my eyes and turn away, powerless. I feel like throwing up."
    "Tanco els ulls i em giro, impotent. Tinc ganes de vomitar."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:3902
translate ca a4_lilly_blackout_d53ff7e7:

    # "I can hear the sound of Lilly moving away and quickly attending to herself, the ruffling of her clothing being pulled back on after a moment of searching just barely audible."
    "Sento que la Lilly s'allunya i es vesteix de pressa, la fressa que s'està posant la seva roba després d'haver-la buscat una estona sense fer en prou feines soroll."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:3904
translate ca a4_lilly_blackout_522ea682:

    # hi "Sorry…"
    hi "Perdona'm..."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:3910
translate ca a4_lilly_blackout_ffbbe680:

    # "She slowly shakes her head as she finishes buttoning up her top. Her kind smile looks so fragile, so delicate, that it makes my heart sink."
    "Fa que no amb el cap  a poc a poc mentre acaba de cordar-se la camisa. El seu somriure amable sembla tan fràgil, tan delicat, que em fa un nus el cor."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:3919
translate ca a4_lilly_blackout_be87ba86:

    # "Approaching carefully, she feels out the edge of the low table before taking a seat next to me, putting her arms around my chest."
    "S'apropa amb cura, temptejant la vora de la taula abans d'asseure's al meu costat i abraçar-me."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:3921
translate ca a4_lilly_blackout_dc80dc7d:

    # li "I'm sorry, Hisao. I shouldn't have pushed my desires onto you."
    li "Em sap greu, Hisao. No t'hauria d'haver empès als meus desitjos."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:3923
translate ca a4_lilly_blackout_ad769602:

    # hi "You don't need to apologize. I'd normally be fine, you've seen that much before."
    hi "No m'has de demanar perdó. Normalment no passa res, ja ho has vist abans."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:3925
translate ca a4_lilly_blackout_4c15caba:

    # hi "I guess I shouldn't have tried to push myself so far."
    hi "Crec que no m'hauria d'haver excedit tant."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:3927
translate ca a4_lilly_blackout_f22129d0:

    # "My eyelids feel heavy. Calmly sitting next to her like this is probably letting the adrenaline work itself out of my system, and letting my mind relax."
    "Em pesen les parpelles. Estar tranquil·lament assegut al seu costat deu estar deixant que l'adrenalina se'n vagi del sistema, i així puc relaxar la ment."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:3932
translate ca a4_lilly_blackout_f9973590:

    # li "So that's… why you never took the lead…?"
    li "Per això... mai prens la iniciativa...?"

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:3934
translate ca a4_lilly_blackout_b956c4cf:

    # hi "Yeah. I guess it's a good thing you like to, huh?"
    hi "Sí. Suposo que està bé que a tu t'agradi tenir-la, eh?"

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:3939
translate ca a4_lilly_blackout_bf54bda8:

    # "The joke seems to lighten her expression a little, a fact which helps let me feel less unease about my unreliable self."
    "Sembla que l'acudit li alleugeri una mica l'expressió, cosa que m'ajuda a sentir-me menys incòmode amb la meva forma de ser poc fiable."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:3941
translate ca a4_lilly_blackout_536d0e4e:

    # "Lilly's head comes to rest on my shoulder as I struggle to keep my eyes open, with more difficulty after each blink. I feel completely drained."
    "la Lilly descansa el cap sobre la meva espatlla mentre lluito per mantenir els ulls oberts, fet que em costa més amb cada parpelleig. Estic rebentat."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:3943
translate ca a4_lilly_blackout_3ebfb839:

    # li "It's okay, Hisao. It's all okay."
    li "Està bé, Hisao. Està tot bé."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:3947
translate ca a4_lilly_blackout_c82d5567:

    # "No sooner does she say this than a small, quiet tune escapes her lips. Entirely too tired to think, all I can do is listen to her soft humming."
    "Després de dir-ho, se li escapa una musiqueta tranquil·la dels llavis. Estic massa cansat per pensar, l'únic que puc fer és escoltar som taral·leja."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:3949
translate ca a4_lilly_blackout_c9a435b8:

    # "It's a soft, almost melancholic tune. It sounds familiar, but the more I try to remember its origin the less I seem able to concentrate."
    "És una melodia suau, gairebé melancòlica. Em sona familiar, però com més intento recordar d'on ve menys capaç em sento de concentrar-me."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:3951
translate ca a4_lilly_blackout_08caa52e:

    # "The feeling and scent of her head gently resting on my shoulder and her warm body against my side are soothing. The soft humming of her voice, too, relaxes my mind as much as her warmth relaxes my muscles."
    "La sensació i l'olor del seu cap descansant suaument sobre la meva espatlla i el seu cos càlid al meu costat em calmen. El suau taral·lejar de la seva veu em relaxa la  ment tant com la seva calidesa em relaxa els músculs."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:3953
translate ca a4_lilly_blackout_6209e6eb:

    # "This singular, quiet moment… after all this fracas, it makes me realize just how exhausted I've become. I can feel my eyelids slowly becoming heavier and heavier."
    "Aquest moment tranquil i extraordinari... després de tot aquest escàndol, m'adono que estic esgotat. Noto que les parpelles em pensen cada vegada més."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:3955
translate ca a4_lilly_blackout_1e92e876:

    # "Even with the chaos of before, I wish this moment would last forever."
    "Fins i tot amb el caos d'abans, m'agradaria que aquest moment durés per sempre."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:3957
translate ca a4_lilly_blackout_833d943f:

    # "Lilly and I together, sharing a single, solitary occasion together, just as we used to."
    "La Lilly i jo junts, compartint una ocasió única sols, com fèiem abans."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:3959
translate ca a4_lilly_blackout_342e3b25:

    # "But if that's the case… why does she feel… further away than she's ever felt before?"
    "Però aquesta vegada... per què la noto... més lluny del que l'havia notat mai?"

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:3976
translate ca a4_lilly_context_b10e84e7:

    # "The loud clatter of books falling into the return slot abruptly breaks the grip of silence over the school library."
    "L'espetec sobtat dels llibres mentre cauen a la bústia de retorn trenca el silenci que regna a la biblioteca de l'escola."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:3978
translate ca a4_lilly_context_4396b1ca:

    # "It's become a habit for me to come to the library at least once a week. Not only does the reading itself keep me busy, but discussing books with Hanako and Lilly also does."
    "M'he acostumat a venir a la biblioteca almenys una vegada per setmana. No només m'entretinc amb la lectura, sinó que també parlo de llibres amb la Hanako i la Lilly."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:3983
translate ca a4_lilly_context_006fa6f9:

    # "Obviously startled, Yuuko suddenly twists towards the direction of the noise. I'd have thought her used to people dropping books by now, since she does work here."
    "Veig que la Yuuko se sobresalta i es gira de sobte cap a la direcció d'on ve el soroll. Pensava que ja estaria acostumada que la gent deixés anar llibres, ja que treballa aquí."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:3988
translate ca a4_lilly_context_79f94846:

    # yu "Oh, hello Hisao. Back again?"
    yu "Oh, hola, Hisao. Tornes a ser aquí?"

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:3990
translate ca a4_lilly_context_5478e016:

    # "It takes me a moment to respond, my mind still distracted by the familiar melody of Lilly's humming that's hardly left my ears in the several days it's been since I fell asleep to it."
    "Trigo un moment respondre, encara estic distret per la melodia familiar que taral·lejava la Lilly, fins al punt que gairebé no hi he deixat de pensar d'ençà que m'hi vaig quedar adormit."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:3992
translate ca a4_lilly_context_64faeb61:

    # hi "Hmm? Oh, yeah. Just returning some books I borrowed."
    hi "Hmm? Oh, sí. Només volia tornar uns llibres que havia agafat."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:3994
translate ca a4_lilly_context_cfc18d6f:

    # "She casts her eyes downwards, presumably to the bin the books dropped into."
    "Mira cap avall, segurament cap a la caixa on van a parar els llibres que cauen."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:3999
translate ca a4_lilly_context_8a5e6a92:

    # yu "You're a very heavy reader, aren't you?"
    yu "Ets un lector àvid, oi que sí?"

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4001
translate ca a4_lilly_context_a4caf208:

    # hi "It's become a bit of a routine now. Passes the time, at least."
    hi "S'ha convertit una mica en una rutina. Per passar l'estona, com a mínim."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4006
translate ca a4_lilly_context_08d7fa84:

    # yu "I wish I had free time to pass…"
    yu "Tant de bo tingués temps lliure per passar-lo..."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4008
translate ca a4_lilly_context_7aed640b:

    # "From smalltalk to depression in less than five seconds. I think that's a new record for her. She seems a bit down in general today, even compared to normal."
    "De conversa banal a depressió en menys de cinc segons. Crec que és el seu nou rècord. Avui sembla una mica decaiguda en general, fins i tot en comparació amb com és normalment."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4010
translate ca a4_lilly_context_b25e04fa:

    # "Considering she has to work two jobs just to support herself, I could see how that would take a toll on her lifestyle."
    "Tenint en compte que té dues feines per poder mantenir-se, entenc que això li hagi pogut passar factura al seu estil de vida."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4012
translate ca a4_lilly_context_6ff23116:

    # "Come to think of it, the pay for her job here can't be all that bad. The idea of staff in such a prestigious private school going hungry strikes me as counterintuitive."
    "Ara que hi penso, el sou que guanya aquí no deu ser tan dolent. La idea que el personal d'una escola privada tan prestigiosa passi gana em sembla contraintuïtiva."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4014
translate ca a4_lilly_context_d465e84d:

    # hi "Working two jobs must take a lot of time. I'd probably never manage it."
    hi "Tenir dues feines deu treure't molt de temps. Segur que jo no podria."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4019
translate ca a4_lilly_context_27b105aa:

    # yu "You're lucky, being a student. Do you think you'll be able to go to university?"
    yu "En tens sort, de ser estudiant. Creus que podràs arribar a la universitat?"

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4021
translate ca a4_lilly_context_b98f695d:

    # "If she's asking, then I guess that's the expected result of having this kind of education. Private schools like this don't exactly come cheap."
    "Si ho pregunta, suposo que és perquè això és el que s'espera quan reps aquest tipus d'educació. Les escoles privades com aquesta no són precisament barates."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4023
translate ca a4_lilly_context_574e5ac9:

    # hi "I… guess. I have the money, I think."
    hi "Ho... suposo. Tinc prou diners, crec."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4025
translate ca a4_lilly_context_27790571:

    # hi "I've got plans which will require going to one, and my grades are good enough. It's more a matter of how I'll pay to do so."
    hi "Pels plans que tinc cal que hi passi per alguna, i les meves notes són prou bones. És més aviat cosa de com ho pagaré."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4030
translate ca a4_lilly_context_094fdc7e:

    # yu "University costs so much that I'm having to work two jobs to afford to enter it… paying for daily expenses too makes it a lot harder."
    yu "La universitat és tan cara que necessito dues feines per poder entrar-hi... a més, pagar-me les despeses diàries m'ho posa més difícil."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4035
translate ca a4_lilly_context_2f38f6c5:

    # yu "If you're reading this much though, that means you're doing well in school, right?"
    yu "Si llegeixes tant deu voler dir que et va força bé amb els estudis, oi?"

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4037
translate ca a4_lilly_context_5d3e7188:

    # "Interesting logical jump. Not an altogether wrong one, though."
    "Quin salt lògic més interessant. Tot i que no va mal encaminada."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4039
translate ca a4_lilly_context_f1fb6e95:

    # hi "I suppose so. I didn't find any of the exams very hard, aside from maybe one or two."
    hi "Suposo. Els exàmens no m'ha semblat gaire difícils, tret de potser un o dos."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4041
translate ca a4_lilly_context_5c4e593b:

    # hi "Do you mind if I ask what studies you're pursuing in university?"
    hi "Et fa res si et pregunto quina carrera estàs estudiant a la universitat?"

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4046
translate ca a4_lilly_context_f197f6e2:

    # "Yuuko appears to genuinely brighten at the question."
    "Sembla que la Yuuko realment s'alegra d'aquesta pregunta."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4051
translate ca a4_lilly_context_0292f071:

    # yu "Anthropology. To be specific, I'm specializing in the history of classical era Athenian civilization and democracy."
    yu "Antropologia. Per ser més específica, m'estic especialitzant en la història de l'era clàssica de la civilització i democràcia d'Atenes."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4053
translate ca a4_lilly_context_caff49c2:

    # "She really seems to know her stuff. Such enthusiasm is to be admired, and it's nice to see her genuinely excited about something."
    "Sembla que sap del que parla. Aquest entusiasme és admirable, i és agradable veure-la realment emocionada per alguna cosa."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4055
translate ca a4_lilly_context_c7be7acb:

    # "I guess even somebody like Yuuko can be happy if she has a visible road ahead of her."
    "Suposo que fins i tot algú com la Yuuko pot ser feliç si té un camí clar de cara al futur."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4057
translate ca a4_lilly_context_745ee9e5:

    # hi "That's good to hear. If you—{w=0.6}{nw}"
    hi "Que interessant això. Si—{w=0.6}{nw}"

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4065
translate ca a4_lilly_context_037a172f:

    # "Both of us jump at the sudden interruption coming from my pocket."
    "Tots dos fem un bot quan ens interromp un soroll que ve de la meva butxaca."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4070
translate ca a4_lilly_context_d38f7c4d:

    # "Apologizing profusely and quickly shuffling into the hallway as I fumble with the cover of my mobile phone, I glance at the screen."
    "Em desfaig en disculpes i m'afanyo cap al passadís mentre remeno la coberta del meu mòbil i miro la pantalla."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4072
translate ca a4_lilly_context_fd45864c:

    # "…Weird. It's a mobile number I don't recognize. Considering I can count the number of people with my number on one hand, I briefly wonder whether it's some telemarketer that lucked out."
    "...Que estrany. És un número que no conec. Tenint en compte que puc comptar amb els dits d'una mà les persones que tenen el meu telèfon, em pregunto un moment si deu ser un venedor telefònic que ha tingut sort."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4083
translate ca a4_lilly_context_5a3cec6a:

    # hi "Hello, Hisao Nakai speaking."
    hi "Hola, soc en Hisao Nakai."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4085
translate ca a4_lilly_context_752d5f98:

    # mystery "Geez, pick up faster next time. Anyway, guess who?"
    mystery "Renoi, agafa'l més de pressa la pròxima vegada. Per cert, saps qui soc?"

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4089
translate ca a4_lilly_context_44a5adf2:

    # "It only takes me a second to recognize the distinctively deep, brusque voice."
    "Només trigo un segon a reconèixer aquesta veu marcadament profunda i brusca."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4091
translate ca a4_lilly_context_51589031:

    # hi "Hey, Misha. Didn't expect you to call me."
    hi "Ei, Misha. No esperava que em truquessis."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4093
translate ca a4_lilly_context_b8fd86b4:

    # aki "Huh!? Ya actually think I sound like her?"
    aki "Eh!? De veritat creus que sono com ella?"

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4095
translate ca a4_lilly_context_a2ce63e0:

    # hi "Not at all, Akira. I don't remember giving you my number though, so I thought I'd mess with you."
    hi "Gens ni mica, Akira. Però no recordo haver-te donat el meu número, així que volia jugar amb tu."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4097
translate ca a4_lilly_context_efedc527:

    # aki "Oh, that? I got Lilly to give it to me. Not hard."
    aki "Ah, això? He fet que la Lilly me'l donés. Fàcil."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4099
translate ca a4_lilly_context_fca3ec90:

    # "She positively brims with pride at the statement. She's trying to get me caught up in her pace, I know it."
    "Fa aquesta declaració amb orgull. Està intentant que li segueixi el ritme, ho sé."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4101
translate ca a4_lilly_context_575580e1:

    # "I suppose I shouldn't be surprised that the two would share my number though, given how close they are."
    "Suposo que no m'hauria de sorprendre que hagin compartit el meu número, ja que són tan properes."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4103
translate ca a4_lilly_context_46dc5037:

    # hi "So, what's up?"
    hi "I, què vols?"

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4105
translate ca a4_lilly_context_8bf19bf3:

    # aki "You free right now?"
    aki "Tens temps ara?"

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4107
translate ca a4_lilly_context_06c6460c:

    # hi "I… guess? Why?"
    hi "Sí... suposo? Per què?"

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4109
translate ca a4_lilly_context_d5eb55b1:

    # aki "Could you meet me at the park in town? I just want to talk to you about some stuff."
    aki "Podríem quedar al parc que hi ha al centre? Només volia parlar amb tu d'una cosa."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4111
translate ca a4_lilly_context_e44bdb49:

    # hi "Is that an invitation to a date?"
    hi "M'estàs convidant a una cita?"

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4113
translate ca a4_lilly_context_430601da:

    # aki "What? Of course not…"
    aki "Què? És clar que no..."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4117
translate ca a4_lilly_context_ef380296:

    # "She sounds suddenly crestfallen, her previous teasing nature having instantaneously left. It seems strange for her."
    "De sobte, la noto alacaiguda, deixa de fer-me la guitza com fins ara a l'instant Sembla estrany per a ser ella."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4119
translate ca a4_lilly_context_5e564c74:

    # hi "Anyway, I don't see why not. When do you want to meet?"
    hi "Però bé, no veig perquè no. Quan vols que quedem?"

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4121
translate ca a4_lilly_context_34628b15:

    # aki "Kind of… now. Ish."
    aki "Et va bé... ara? Més o menys."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4123
translate ca a4_lilly_context_ee76dad4:

    # hi "Wait, right now? But it's—"
    hi "Què, ara mateix? Però si—"

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4125
translate ca a4_lilly_context_3f4f495b:

    # "The dead silence suddenly coming from the phone announces the fact that she has unceremoniously hung up."
    "El silenci sepulcral que de sobte ve del telèfon anuncia  que ha penjat sense gaires cerimònies."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4140
translate ca a4_lilly_context_c45b9d93:

    # "For a long time I just stand there, staring at the 'CALL ENDED' message on the screen while replaying the conversation in my head."
    "Em quedo una bona estona quiet, mirant el missatge de \"TRUCADA FINALITZADA\" a la pantalla mentre reprodueixo la conversa al meu cap."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4142
translate ca a4_lilly_context_97aa810e:

    # hi "What the hell, Akira?"
    hi "Què cony, Akira?"

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4150
translate ca a4_lilly_context_bac97ada:

    # "Throwing a glance up and down the street, I cross the road and step into the park."
    "Faig una ullada amunt i avall del carrer, creuo la carretera i m'endinso al parc."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4152
translate ca a4_lilly_context_27bb6298:

    # "I've learned to pace myself on such walks, mostly because Lilly's slower speed during our forays into town means I have to consciously slow myself down."
    "He après a anar al meu ritme quan passejo, sobretot perquè el pas lent de la Lilly durant les nostres sortides a la ciutat implica que he de saber anar més a poc a poc."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4154
translate ca a4_lilly_context_a172da94:

    # "That aside, I hope Akira didn't expect me to be immediately prompt."
    "A part d'això, espero que l'Akira no donés per descomptat que hi aniria de seguida."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4163
translate ca a4_lilly_context_7c65642d:

    # "It takes only a couple of seconds to spot her, waiting on a bench with a can of beer in her hand."
    "Només trigo un parell de segons en trobar-la, està esperant en un banc amb una llauna de cervesa a la mà."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4165
translate ca a4_lilly_context_fee4f508:

    # "The look she gives me as I walk up lacks any hint of acknowledgment or greeting."
    "Per la mirada que fa mentre m'hi apropo, no sembla que m'hagi reconegut ni m'estigui saludant."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4167
translate ca a4_lilly_context_e3e7661b:

    # hi "What's with that look? I needn't have come, you know."
    hi "I aquesta cara que poses? No tenia l'obligació de venir, saps."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4169
translate ca a4_lilly_context_799b22fd:

    # aki "I knew you would. You're that kind of person, after all."
    aki "Sabia que vindries. Al capdavall, ets així."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4176
translate ca a4_lilly_context_de720a90:

    # "I lower my brow at her remark as she disposes of the can, emptied by the time I arrived, and a metallic clatter rings out. Akira takes a seat on the old wooden bench, and I follow her lead."
    "Arrufo el front davant aquest comentari mentre es desfà de la llauna, que s'ha acabat abans no arribés, i sona un cop metàl·lic. L'Akira s'asseu en un vell banc de fusta i la segueixo."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4180
translate ca a4_lilly_context_6a0e996f:

    # "She takes another can of beer from beside her and opens it before speaking, taking a large gulp. She seems to really like that stuff."
    "Agafa una altra llauna de cervesa del seu costat i l'obra abans de parlar, en pren un gran glop. Sembla que li agrada molt."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4182
translate ca a4_lilly_context_1fa181ba:

    # hi "I suppose I don't need to ask what this is about, or rather, who it's about?"
    hi "Suposo que no cal que et pregunti de què es tracta, o més aviat, de qui?"

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4187
translate ca a4_lilly_context_4aadd998:

    # aki "I heard from Lilly that you asked about our family."
    aki "La Lilly m'ha dit que li has preguntat sobre la nostra família."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4189
translate ca a4_lilly_context_37ed510d:

    # "They share more than phone numbers, that's for sure. I'd probably be very worried right now if it weren't for the total lack of malice in her voice. Rather, her tone sounds almost wistful."
    "Sembla que comparteixen més que números de telèfon. Segurament estaria molt preocupada si no fos perquè no noto malícia a la seva veu. Més aviat, el seu to sona quasi melancòlic."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4191
translate ca a4_lilly_context_044459c9:

    # hi "Idle curiosity, mostly."
    hi "Tafaneria, principalment."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4193
translate ca a4_lilly_context_281691c6:

    # hi "…I have to admit, I'd never have guessed you two were half Scottish."
    hi "...si et soc sincer, no hauria endevinat mai que les dues fóssiu escoceses."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4198
translate ca a4_lilly_context_6135851a:

    # "She gives a wry chuckle of amusement."
    "Deixa anar una rialleta divertida."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4203
translate ca a4_lilly_context_28fc0738:

    # aki "I've heard that before, trust me."
    aki "M'ho solen dir, creu-me."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4208
translate ca a4_lilly_context_00c9ec65:

    # "The small smile falls from her face, her eyes looking ahead distantly."
    "Se li desdibuixa el mig somriure de la cara i mira endavant, distant."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4210
translate ca a4_lilly_context_a19eeb7e:

    # "Aside from the occasional elderly couple talking as they slowly walk the meandering paths, and the odd aging car, it's pleasantly quiet."
    "A part de l'ocasional conversa d'alguna parelleta gran que camina lentament pels camins serpentejants, i d'algun cotxe força envellit, s'hi està prou tranquil."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4215
translate ca a4_lilly_context_dab07617:

    # aki "She didn't tell you everything though, did she?"
    aki "Però no t'ho ha explicat tot, oi que no?"

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4217
translate ca a4_lilly_context_e25873a9:

    # hi "It was pretty brief. Your parents live in Scotland, she hasn't met them since she was twelve, and she wants to meet them again."
    hi "Ha estat froça breu. Els vostres pares viuen a Escòcia, no els ha vist des que tenia dotze anys i els vol tornar a veure."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4222
translate ca a4_lilly_context_a483f2b8:

    # aki "It's always surprised me how devoted she is to our parents, for all the good they did us."
    aki "Sempre m'ha sorprès que n'estigui tant dels nostres pares, després de tot el que ens van fer."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4224
translate ca a4_lilly_context_8bb184cf:

    # "The way she says it sounds almost derisive. She gives a small sigh, as if to quickly brush the feelings away."
    "El to en què ho diu és gairebé burleta. Deixa anar un petit sospir, com si volgués allunyar de seguida aquests sentiments."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4229
translate ca a4_lilly_context_34e31dc9:

    # aki "Why do you think they left, Hisao?"
    aki "Per què creus que van marxar, Hisao?"

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4231
translate ca a4_lilly_context_a37b9bea:

    # hi "Why do I think they left?"
    hi "Per què ho crec jo?"

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4233
translate ca a4_lilly_context_e5046525:

    # hi "From what Lilly told me, it was because of work. I guess a pretty decently-paying job was involved as well, given the way your parents seem to live."
    hi "Pel que m'ha dit la Lilly, va ser cosa de feina. Suposo que també involucrava una feina més que ben pagada, si tenim en compte com viuen els teus pares."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4235
translate ca a4_lilly_context_b1045e63:

    # hi "So Lilly went to a private school, and that's why she carries herself with the airs and graces of the upper class."
    hi "Així que la Lilly va anar a una escola privada, i per això té aquests aires i maneres de classe alta."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4237
translate ca a4_lilly_context_43e03065:

    # aki "Yeah. Since the business in Inverness boomed, our father decided to move directly to the same city as its headquarters."
    aki "Sí. D'ençà que el negoci a Inverness va expandir-se, el pare va decidir traslladar-se a la mateixa ciutat que hi havia la central."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4242
translate ca a4_lilly_context_a4d73718:

    # aki "That's just the conclusion I'd thought you'd come to, though. You're too good-natured."
    aki "Però aquesta és la conclusió on pensava que arribaries. Ets massa bona persona."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4244
translate ca a4_lilly_context_f1a3fc7c:

    # hi "You don't think they left for their career?"
    hi "No penses que van marxar per la feina?"

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4249
translate ca a4_lilly_context_eb2f7696:

    # aki "I'm sitting here bitching to you about it. What do you think?"
    aki "Estic aquí putejant-te sobre el tema. Què en penses tu?"

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4254
translate ca a4_lilly_context_3a97cd2b:

    # aki "Yamaku Academy. I've always felt that place was kinda creepy; like it was an isolated hideaway for those 'proper society' doesn't want to see nor hear."
    aki "L'acadèmia Yamaku. Sempre he pensat que era un lloc inquietant, com si fos un racó aïllat per aquells a qui la \"veritable societat\" no vol veure ni sentir."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4259
translate ca a4_lilly_context_9e685f35:

    # aki "They probably just rue the fact that Lilly wasn't old enough to be shoved there by the time they left."
    aki "Segur que només es van penedir del fet que la Lilly no era prou gran per venir aquí quan van marxar."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4261
translate ca a4_lilly_context_feda9b53:

    # "A long silence follows her abrupt and very harsh criticism of her own parents, and Yamaku."
    "Després d'aquesta crítica abrupta i molt dura als seus propis pares i al Yamaku, es fa un llarg silenci."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4263
translate ca a4_lilly_context_fad8d516:

    # "Lilly's blindness is hardly something that could be simply ignored for a high-class family attempting to keep up appearances, much less so when a lucrative offer is on the table."
    "La ceguesa de la Lilly no és una cosa que es pugui simplement ignorar per a una família de classe alta que intenta mantenir les aparences, i molt menys quan hi ha una oferta lucrativa sobre la taula."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4265
translate ca a4_lilly_context_37b5cc16:

    # "Eventually Akira gives a derisive snort, her feelings coming to a head."
    "Finalment, l'Akira deixa anar un esbufec irònic, els seus sentiments han explotat."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4267
translate ca a4_lilly_context_618b28b6:

    # aki "Moving to secure our financial future with his new job posting. Even at the time I hardly believed it."
    aki "Traslladar-se per  assegurar-nos el  futur financer amb el seu nou lloc de treball. Fins i tot en aquell moment en prou feines m'ho creia."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4269
translate ca a4_lilly_context_34adf406:

    # "Not wanting to simply be an avenue for her venting, I gently try to steer the discussion."
    "No vull ser només una via perquè es desfogui, així que intento dirigir suaument la discussió."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4271
translate ca a4_lilly_context_ee3e116b:

    # hi "So you stayed in Japan with Lilly, then?"
    hi "Així que et vas quedar al Japó amb la Llliy, oi?"

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4276
translate ca a4_lilly_context_00bf7e63:

    # aki "Either I stayed with her, or she went to live with an ailing grandmother and grandfather."
    aki "Era o bé em quedava amb ella, o bé l'enviaven a viure amb un avi i una àvia malalts."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4278
translate ca a4_lilly_context_429bb40c:

    # hi "What about Shizune's family? If you're cousins, then…"
    hi "I per què no la família de la Shizune? Si sou cosins, llavors..."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4283
translate ca a4_lilly_context_99b513a4:

    # aki "Our fathers hate each other. I'd have been more than happy to tell them to go screw themselves and live with them anyway, but Lilly wouldn't have wanted that."
    aki "Els nostres pares s'odien. No m'hauria importat una merda dir-los que es fotessin i viure amb ells de totes maneres, però la Lilly no hauria volgut."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4288
translate ca a4_lilly_context_067c560c:

    # aki "I'd also had an offer for a job by then, so we did our best to keep our parents' house in proper shape, and tried to continue our lives as if they'd never left."
    aki "També tenia una oferta de feina en aquell moment, així que vaig fer tot el que vaig poder per conservar la casa dels nostres pares en condicions, i intentar continuar les nostres vides com si no haguessin marxat."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4290
translate ca a4_lilly_context_457ca011:

    # hi "So you just lived by yourselves?"
    hi "Així que vau fer la vostra vida?"

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4295
translate ca a4_lilly_context_db25384f:

    # aki "Basically. Lilly had school and I had my job, so we weren't exactly languishing."
    aki "Com aquell qui diu. La Lilly anava a classe i jo a la feina, així que no estàvem per gaire melancolia."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4297
translate ca a4_lilly_context_81fe392c:

    # aki "With her schooling, her study, and having to do chores while I worked, though, I can't help feeling like I failed her. In the end, I tried to be there for her, and screwed it up."
    aki "Ella anava a l'esola, estudiava i feia les feines de casa mentre jo treballava, així que no puc evitar sentir que la vaig fallar. Al capdavall, tot i que em vaig quedar allà per ella, la vaig cagar."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4302
translate ca a4_lilly_context_ae806f5a:

    # aki "…Expecting a nineteen-year-old to be a mother for a blind child. It's ridiculous."
    aki "... Esperar que una noia de dinou anys fes de mare a una nena cega. És ridícul."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4304
translate ca a4_lilly_context_bf4d2bab:

    # "So… Lilly and Akira lived alone after their parents moved, with Lilly largely taking care of herself. I guess that explains her apparent independence, compared to many in Yamaku."
    "Així que... la Lilly i l'Akira van viure soles després que els seus pares marxessin, i la Lilly es va haver d'espavilar pràcticament sola. Suposo que això explica que sigui tan independent, si la comparem amb molts altres del Yamaku."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4306
translate ca a4_lilly_context_d972cd28:

    # "I may have lived alone much of the time since my parents both worked, but that's… just something else entirely."
    "Pot ser que jo hagi viscut sol gran part del temps, ja que els meus pares treballaven, però això és... una cosa completament diferent."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4311
translate ca a4_lilly_context_15b2a712:

    # aki "Sorry for making you listen to my moaning, Hisao."
    aki "Perdona que t'hagi fet escoltar les meves queixes, Hhisao."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4313
translate ca a4_lilly_context_00d94e0c:

    # hi "I don't mind at all, but… do you mind if I ask why you're telling me all this?"
    hi "No et preocupis, però... et puc preguntar per què m'estàs explicant tot això?"

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4318
translate ca a4_lilly_context_102e5b01:

    # aki "Hmph. You always were curious."
    aki "Bufa. Tu i la teva curiositat."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4323
translate ca a4_lilly_context_5b805e67:

    # aki "Context, I suppose."
    aki "Per context, suposo."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4325
translate ca a4_lilly_context_6501500c:

    # aki "Life isn't a fairytale, Hisao. Some people have to learn that the hard way."
    aki "La vida no és un conte de fades, Hisao. Hi ha gent que ho acaba aprenent a les males."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4327
translate ca a4_lilly_context_a8c2d354:

    # "She takes a long drink from the can in her hand, her face becoming more depressed than distant."
    "Fa un bon glop de la llauna que té a la mà, té cara de deprimida més que no pas de distant."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4334
translate ca a4_lilly_context_838ace95:

    # aki "I broke up with my boyfriend a few days ago. After I leave, we're not going to be able to see each other again."
    aki "Ho vaig deixar amb el meu xicot fa uns dies. Un cop marxi, no ens tornarem a veure mai més."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4336
translate ca a4_lilly_context_2d425fc6:

    # aki "But that's how life is. You can't just set your life up and expect it to stay that way forever; sometimes stuff happens that you have to roll with, even if it means hurting yourself or others."
    aki "Però així és la vida. o pots muntar la teva vida i esperar que es quedi així per sempre; de vegades passen coses i has de poder adaptar-te, encara que això suposi fer-te mal a tu o als altres."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4338
translate ca a4_lilly_context_e00e58dd:

    # "She takes a long breath before looking up at the bright orange sky."
    "Deixa anar un sospir llarg abans de mirar el cel brillant de color taronja."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4343
translate ca a4_lilly_context_121eddb8:

    # aki "Damn… if I smoked, I could take a nice, long drag right about now and look kinda cool."
    aki "Cony... si fumés, ara podria fer una bona calada i quedaria ben parida. "

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4345
translate ca a4_lilly_context_10c6e00e:

    # "I want to respond, to help her in whatever way I can, but I feel utterly useless. This kind of situation is one I've never been in, and I simply don't have the experience to say anything meaningful to comfort her."
    "Vull respondre, ajudar-la com sigui, però em sento totalment inútil. Mai m'havia trobat en una situació com aquesta, i simplement no tinc prou experiència per dir res assenyat que la consoli."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4347
translate ca a4_lilly_context_37b5281d:

    # "Akira looks over and evidently picks up on this, much to my embarrassment."
    "L'Akira mira amunt i se n'adona, me n'avergonyeixo."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4352
translate ca a4_lilly_context_b2d7271f:

    # aki "I must look pretty pathetic right now, whining about this to someone I barely know."
    aki "Et dec semblar molt patètica ara mateix, fent de ploramiques sobre tot això amb algú que en prou feines conec."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4354
translate ca a4_lilly_context_423130f5:

    # hi "Hardly, and I'm pretty much an expert on looking pathetic."
    hi "Què va, jo sí que soc tot un expert a semblar patètic."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4359
translate ca a4_lilly_context_e06c6d92:

    # "She gives a chuckle, the act feeling like a personal victory for me."
    "Se li escapa el riure, cosa que em sembla una victòria personal."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4364
translate ca a4_lilly_context_630b5f67:

    # aki "You're a good kid, Hisao. When I said that I approved of you being with my sister, I wasn't joking or just being nice."
    aki "Ets un bon noi, Hisao. Quan et vaig dir que em semblava bé que sortissis amb la meva germana, no feia broma ni volia semblar amable."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4376
translate ca a4_lilly_context_b8686c2b:

    # "She picks herself up off the seat with a grunt, one that seems ill-fitting given her age, and throws the now empty can into the bin after one last swig."
    "S'aixeca del seient amb un esbufec que sembla impropi per la seva edat, i llança llauna ja buida a la paperera després de fer-ne un últim glop."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4381
translate ca a4_lilly_context_91228a46:

    # aki "It's just unfortunate that doesn't really count for much in this world."
    aki "És una llàstima que això no serveixi de res en aquest món."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4386
translate ca a4_lilly_context_2b989b21:

    # aki "When I said that I was leaving for Scotland, I was doing it because a good position opened up in our company's headquarters."
    aki "Quan vaig dir que marxava a Escòcia, va ser perquè va aparèixer una vacant en un bon lloc a la seu de l'empresa"

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4388
translate ca a4_lilly_context_ad81ee48:

    # aki "When our folks told me that when we were at their place, though, they also gave Lilly a summons to rejoin them in Inverness."
    aki "Però quan els nostres pares m'ho van dir estavem a casa seva, i també li van demanar a la Lilly que tornés amb ells a Inverness."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4392
translate ca a4_lilly_context_c47047c6:

    # "No way…"
    "No fotis..."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4394
translate ca a4_lilly_context_5bc52b1b:

    # "Her evasiveness when asked about her future… that awkwardness that had steadily grown between us… that uncharacteristic outburst of anger…"
    "Tantes reserves quan li preguntava sobre el seu futur... aquella incomoditat que anava creixent entre nosaltres... aquells esclats d'ira tan poc propis d'ella..."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4396
translate ca a4_lilly_context_732614dd:

    # "All of them suddenly fit into place."
    "De sobte, tot encaixa en el seu lloc."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4398
translate ca a4_lilly_context_264f4200:

    # "The same family that she reminisced about after Hanako's birthday party, the same family that left her and Akira to themselves after taking flight to greener pastures…"
    "La mateixa família a qui recordava després de la festa d'aniversari de la Hanako, la mateixa família que la va abandonar a ella i l'Akira després de fugir cap a una vida millor..."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4400
translate ca a4_lilly_context_a5cfb198:

    # "Now I feel stupid for never cornering Lilly on what was bugging her. I'd never even considered if something had happened during her trip to her family's home at Inverness."
    "Ara em sento estúpid per no haver acorralat a la Lilly per preguntar-li què l'atabalava. No m'havia plantejat si havia passat alguna cosa durant el seu viatge a casa de la seva família a Inverness."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4402
translate ca a4_lilly_context_a76a37f6:

    # "And now, a sense of unease grows in my chest. If her family has summoned her to join them in Scotland, all the way on the other side of the Earth…"
    "I ara, em creix al pit una sensació d'inquietud. Si la seva família li ha demanat que vagi amb ells a Escòcia, a l'altra banda de la Terra..."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4404
translate ca a4_lilly_context_f7e6a317:

    # hi "Has she… accepted?"
    hi "Ha... acceptat?"

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4409
translate ca a4_lilly_context_44c43eec:

    # aki "Lilly hasn't told me whether she plans to accept, and it seems she hasn't told you, either."
    aki "No m'ho ha dit si al final ho acceptarà o no i, pel que sembla, a tu tampoc t'ho ha dit."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4411
translate ca a4_lilly_context_81b43770:

    # aki "That's why I called you down here to talk, Hisao."
    aki "Per això t'he demanat que vinguessis fins aquí per parlar, Hisao."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4413
translate ca a4_lilly_context_76ea7104:

    # hi "Context, huh…"
    hi "Context, eh..."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4415
translate ca a4_lilly_context_1e620894:

    # "I sit back, my feelings of worry and frustration no doubt written all over my face."
    "Torno a seure, els sentiments de preocupació i frustració se'm llegeixen a la cara."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4420
translate ca a4_lilly_context_b66e95af:

    # aki "Lilly's a strong person, Hisao, but she's not infallible."
    aki "La Lilly és una persona forta, Hisao, però també s'equivoca."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4422
translate ca a4_lilly_context_aa01a592:

    # aki "I guess it's my job to worry about her, being her older sister, but I think that you deserve to know."
    aki "Suposo que és feina meva preocupar-me'n, per això soc la germana gran, però pensava que mereixies saber-ho."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4424
translate ca a4_lilly_context_6896d184:

    # hi "I understand."
    hi "T'entenc."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4429
translate ca a4_lilly_context_71a3f6c8:

    # aki "You okay? You sound depressed."
    aki "Estàs bé? Sembles deprimit."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4431
translate ca a4_lilly_context_c36234e2:

    # hi "No, I'm just… thinking."
    hi "No, només... estic pensant."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4436
translate ca a4_lilly_context_7890c1eb:

    # aki "That's good. Thinking is good. Being rash won't get you anywhere."
    aki "Està bé. Pensar està bé. Ser impulsiu no et portarà enlloc."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4441
translate ca a4_lilly_context_21a13ee2:

    # "She looks at her watch, barely moving her wrist."
    "Mira el rellotge, sense prou feines moure el canell."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4446
translate ca a4_lilly_context_1418b269:

    # aki "I've got to go. Will you be okay?"
    aki "He de marxar. Estaràs bé?"

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4448
translate ca a4_lilly_context_7fa3a31a:

    # hi "I'll be fine, don't worry. I'll have to talk to Lilly about it and get everything sorted out."
    hi "Estaré bé, no et preocupis. He de parlar amb la Lilly i aclarir-ho tot."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4453
translate ca a4_lilly_context_0ea04cde:

    # "She gives a smile, but it doesn't feel all that genuine or sincere."
    "Somriu, però no em sembla tan sincer ni genuí."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4455
translate ca a4_lilly_context_5bc933f1:

    # "Really, both of us are dancing around the fact that Lilly's on the precipice of the biggest decision of her life and is trying to take the entire burden on herself."
    "Realment, tots dos li donem voltes al fet que la Lilly està a punt de prendre la decisió més important de la seva vida i està intentant assumir-ne tota la càrrega."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4457
translate ca a4_lilly_context_f867ee81:

    # "And part of that burden is the matter of our relationship."
    "I part d'aquesta càrrega és el tema de la nostra relació."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4463
translate ca a4_lilly_context_d9a0ea99:

    # "By the time I look up, Akira's already walking off with her hand held up."
    "Quan aixeco la vista, l'Akira ja ha marxat fent-me adeu amb una mà a l'aire."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4465
translate ca a4_lilly_context_ec0f74ef:

    # "For the first time in a long while, I finally have an answer to something. Perhaps not even that. But at least I now have the right question to ask."
    "Per primera vegada en molt de temps, finalment tinc la resposta a alguna cosa. Potser ni tan sols això. Però almenys ara sé quina pregunta he de fer."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4467
translate ca a4_lilly_context_bb698aa0:

    # "'Will you leave, or stay?'"
    "\"Marxaràs o et quedaràs?\""

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4486
translate ca a4_lilly_a_faraway_future_bd5adadd:

    # hi "Hurry, Lilly!"
    hi "Afanya't, Lilly!"

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4491
translate ca a4_lilly_a_faraway_future_3c3fb915:

    # li "I'm moving as fast as I can!"
    li "Vaig tan de pressa com puc!"

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4493
translate ca a4_lilly_a_faraway_future_d1af9a27:

    # "I can barely make out Lilly's voice over the deafening pounding of the rain. Even though I dislike pulling her around, the situation calls for it."
    "Amb prou feines distingeixo la veu de la Lilly damunt la tamborinada eixordadora que està caient. Encara que no m'agrada estirar-la, la situació ho requereix."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4495
translate ca a4_lilly_a_faraway_future_23d5d35d:

    # "I turn forward, my free hand over my head in a futile attempt to keep at least my hair dry. My vision seems to be in grayscale. This really is rotten weather for summer, and the last kind of climate I'd want for a date."
    "Em giro cap endavant, la meva mà lliure sobre el cap intento inútilment mantenir almenys els cabells eixuts. Sembla que hi veig en escala de grisos. Realment fa un temps horrible per ser estiu, i l'últim que voldria per a una cita."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4497
translate ca a4_lilly_a_faraway_future_041699b2:

    # "A pity. I'd even checked the weather forecast beforehand, one of the very few times I've ever done so, only for it to say that Sunday afternoon would be fine."
    "Una llàstima. Fins i tot havia consultat la previsió meteorològica, una de les poques vegades que ho he fet, i deia que el diumenge a la tarda faria bo."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4499
translate ca a4_lilly_a_faraway_future_9de41518:

    # "Looking to Lilly, her shoulders are by now completely drenched, with her right hand holding tightly to mine and her left gripping her retracted cane."
    "Miro a Lilly, té les  espatlles completament xopes,  la mà dreta agafada amb força a la meva i l'esquerra agafant-se al bastó retràctil."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4501
translate ca a4_lilly_a_faraway_future_0730553a:

    # "This horrid downpour came on just as we were between our destination and Yamaku, so we decided to try rushing the rest of the distance rather than doubling back."
    "Aquest horrible diluvi ha arribat just quan estàvem entre el nostre destí i el Yamaku, així que hem intentat córrer la distància que ens quedava en lloc de tornar enrere."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4503
translate ca a4_lilly_a_faraway_future_cfabfa60:

    # "Entirely unused to running this fast, Lilly's using all her concentration just to avoid tripping over."
    "No està acostumada a córrer tan ràpid, així que la Lilly ha de fer servir tota la seva concentració per evitar caure."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4508
translate ca a4_lilly_a_faraway_future_f3d4cd80:

    # li "Hisao, do you know where we're going!?"
    li "Hisao, saps on estem anant!?"

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4510
translate ca a4_lilly_a_faraway_future_ef98197c:

    # "Even she's reduced to shouting to try and be heard over the combined noise of the wind and the rain."
    "Fins i tot es veu obligada a cridar per intentar fer-se sentir per damunt d'aquest soroll combinat de vent i pluja."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4512
translate ca a4_lilly_a_faraway_future_9c5cd8ad:

    # hi "The Sha—"
    hi "Al Sha—"

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4514
translate ca a4_lilly_a_faraway_future_c0705c44:

    # "The rest of my voice is completely drowned out by an even heavier burst of rain."
    "La meva veu queda completament ofegada per una descàrrega de pluja encara més intensa."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4519
translate ca a4_lilly_a_faraway_future_2c1f44c0:

    # li "The what!?"
    li "Al què!?"

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4521
translate ca a4_lilly_a_faraway_future_a9b4e7fc:

    # hi "The Shanghai!"
    hi "Al Shanghai!"

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4526
translate ca a4_lilly_a_faraway_future_0fe76028:

    # li "How far is it!?"
    li "Estpa molt lluny!?"

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4528
translate ca a4_lilly_a_faraway_future_f7fae550:

    # hi "It shouldn't be far now!"
    hi "No deu quedar gaire!"

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4535
translate ca a4_lilly_a_faraway_future_bf9059c6:

    # "It doesn't take long before I call out to her once again."
    "No trigo a tornar a dirigir-m'hi a crits"

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4537
translate ca a4_lilly_a_faraway_future_86a9e7c2:

    # hi "It looks like we're safe, it's just up ahead!"
    hi "Sembla que estem salvats, està just aquí davant!"

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4539
translate ca a4_lilly_a_faraway_future_f9fee7cd:

    # "I quickly pull up to a stop just in front of the familiar exterior, the lantern outside still giving off its reliable glow, and wait for Lilly to catch her breath before going in."
    "M'aturo de seguida davant del familiar exterior, la llum de fora encara il·lumina una claror fiable, i espero que la Lilly recuperi l'alè abans d'entrar."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4541
translate ca a4_lilly_a_faraway_future_86b38a3b:

    # hi "Ladies first."
    hi "Les dames primer."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4553
translate ca a4_lilly_a_faraway_future_31abdff2:

    # "The tiny bell inside rings out when I hold the door open for her, a smile and a polite nod being my reward before entering myself."
    "La campaneta que hi ha a dins sona quan li obro la porta, i em recompensa amb un somriure i un cop de cap educat per deixar-la entrat abans de mi."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4562
translate ca a4_lilly_a_faraway_future_0fd9c78d:

    # "As I step in behind her and wipe my feet, only a quick glance is necessary to notice the distinct lack of activity. The Shanghai doesn't seem to get much in the way of patronage, and today is no different. Only a couple of tables are occupied."
    "Entro darrere seu i espolso els peus, amb una ullada ràpida n'hi ha prou per adonar-se que no hi ha gaire activitat. Sembla que el Shanghai no té gaire clientela, i avui dia no és diferent. Només hi ha un parell de taules ocupades."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4564
translate ca a4_lilly_a_faraway_future_32af7905:

    # "Summoned by the bell's ringing, a most expected person comes to greet us."
    "Evocada pel toc de la campana, la persona més esperada ve a saludar-nos."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4573
translate ca a4_lilly_a_faraway_future_0317a797:

    # yu "Welcome to the Shanghai!"
    yu "Benvinguts al Shanghai!"

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4575
translate ca a4_lilly_a_faraway_future_ee365ede:

    # "Yuuko looks chipper today. Trying to predict her moods is pretty hard, but it's a nice change from the norm."
    "Avui la Yuuko sembla animada. És difícil predir el seu estat d'ànim, però és un canvi agradable."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4580
translate ca a4_lilly_a_faraway_future_9f816954:

    # li "Hello, Yuuko."
    li "Hola, Yuuko."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4582
translate ca a4_lilly_a_faraway_future_20a67d9a:

    # hi "Hey."
    hi "Ei."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4587
translate ca a4_lilly_a_faraway_future_f94b4a7b:

    # yu "Good afternoon, you two."
    yu "Bona tarda, a tots dos."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4598
translate ca a4_lilly_a_faraway_future_d37eec43:

    # "She takes a deep bow, somewhat taken aback as she rights herself again and gets a better look at us."
    "Fa una gran reverència, una mica sorpresa quan es torna a adreçar i ens mira millor."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4603
translate ca a4_lilly_a_faraway_future_372260f1:

    # yu "What happened to you? You both look…"
    yu "Què us ha passat? Esteu..."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4605
translate ca a4_lilly_a_faraway_future_c6623834:

    # "Her eyes drift towards the glass of the door behind us."
    "Desvia els ulls cap al vidre de la porta que tenim darrere nostre."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4610
translate ca a4_lilly_a_faraway_future_84e01e70:

    # yu "Oh. Oh dear."
    yu "Oh. Verge santa."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4612
translate ca a4_lilly_a_faraway_future_72b7e221:

    # hi "We're inside now, at least. I think that's the most important thing."
    hi "Com a mínim ja estem dins. Crec que és el més important."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4617
translate ca a4_lilly_a_faraway_future_134242e1:

    # li "It's nice and cozy. You're lucky to be working inside today."
    li "Que agradable i acollidor. Tens sort de treballar dins avui."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4622
translate ca a4_lilly_a_faraway_future_bafefb69:

    # yu "It has been nice and quiet. I like days like this."
    yu "Sí que és agradable i tranquil. M'agraden els dies com avui."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4627
translate ca a4_lilly_a_faraway_future_d6ff5c2b:

    # yu "Oh wait, um, sorry… is there anything you'd like?"
    yu "O espera, um, perdona... vols prendre alguna cosa?"

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4632
translate ca a4_lilly_a_faraway_future_42c9bde6:

    # li "French vanilla tea, please."
    li "Te francès amb vainilla, si us plau."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4634
translate ca a4_lilly_a_faraway_future_cfadbcb3:

    # hi "I'll have the same."
    hi "Prendré el mateix."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4639
translate ca a4_lilly_a_faraway_future_dad6a814:

    # yu "Right. Coming right up."
    yu "D'acord. Ara us ho porto."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4644
translate ca a4_lilly_a_faraway_future_b3be57fd:

    # "She quickly skitters off with a determined look on her face, trying very hard not to forget our orders. If nothing else, she is at least dedicated to her jobs."
    "S'allunya ràpidament amb la mirada decidida, esforçant-se per no oblidar les nostres ordres. Si més no, com a mínim almenys es dedica a la seva feina."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4654
translate ca a4_lilly_a_faraway_future_c8ec0930:

    # "I lead Lilly to an empty seat before the two of us settle down. As usual, there's a large difference between my exhausted flopping down into my seat and Lilly's delicate sliding into hers, her cane set beside her."
    "Porto a la Lilly cap a un seient buit abans d'acomodar-nos-hi tots dos. Com de costum, hi ha una gran diferència entre la manera en què em deixo caure esgotat i la manera de lliscar-hi de la Lilly, amb el bastó al seu costat."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4656
translate ca a4_lilly_a_faraway_future_cf0d9a8d:

    # "For a while I just idly watch the rain falling outside. The occasional person runs down the street trying to stay as dry as possible, hands often tightly gripping a rain-soaked umbrella."
    "Durant una estona, observo la pluja que cau a fora. De tant en tant, passa alguna persona corrent pel carrer intentant mantenir-se seca, sovint agafant amb força un paraigua xop per la pluja."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4658
translate ca a4_lilly_a_faraway_future_e8fe3203:

    # "Lilly sits just as quietly as I, her eyes closed as she intently listens to all that's happening."
    "La Lilly s'asseu en silenci com jo, amb els ulls tancats mentre escolta atentament tot el que està passant."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4660
translate ca a4_lilly_a_faraway_future_6230c7f7:

    # "It's a comfortable, relaxing silence that exists between us; just the type that we'd so often shared together in the past months."
    "És un silenci còmode i relaxant aquest que regna entre nosaltres; com els que hem compartit tantes vegades aquests últims mesos."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4664
translate ca a4_lilly_a_faraway_future_a4513dca:

    # "For Lilly, at least."
    "Com a mínim per la Lilly."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4666
translate ca a4_lilly_a_faraway_future_21046cc4:

    # "I can't help replaying the words of her sister in my mind, at times contrasting them to both our time spent together since I entered Yamaku, and to the way we've been since we started dating."
    "No puc evitar reproduir les paraules de la seva germana a la ment, de vegades contrastant-les amb el temps que hem passat junts des que vaig entrar al Yamaku, i amb com hem estat des que vam començar a sortir."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4668
translate ca a4_lilly_a_faraway_future_8d2a97ba:

    # "No matter how much I try, I can't work Lilly out. It's as if the harder I try to second-guess her emotions and her potential decision, the more difficult it becomes to reach a clear conclusion."
    "Per molt que ho intenti, no aconsegueixo entendre a la Lilly. És com si com més intento endevinar les seves emocions i la seva decisió potencial, més difícil m'és arribar a una conclusió clara."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4670
translate ca a4_lilly_a_faraway_future_0179c646:

    # "It makes me doubt whether I'd ever really understood her. In the end, I'm going to have to ask, even though I very much want to avoid doing so."
    "Em fa dubtar si alguna vegada la vaig arribar a entendre de debò. Al final, hauré de preguntar-li, tot i que vull evitar-ho."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4675
translate ca a4_lilly_a_faraway_future_92f1e8a2:

    # li "You seem quiet today, Hisao."
    li "Avui estàs molt callat, Hisao."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4677
translate ca a4_lilly_a_faraway_future_ff728ce7:

    # hi "Really?"
    hi "De debò?"

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4682
translate ca a4_lilly_a_faraway_future_688acef4:

    # li "You seemed so enthusiastic about taking me out on a date, I'd assumed you had something specific you wanted to do."
    li "Semblaves molt entusiasmat amb la idea de tenir una cita, he assumit que hi havia alguna cosa en concret que volies fer."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4684
translate ca a4_lilly_a_faraway_future_52a4b0a1:

    # hi "No, not really. Just wanted to spend some time with you."
    hi "No, de fet no. Només volia passar una estona amb tu."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4689
translate ca a4_lilly_a_faraway_future_b9fa597a:

    # li "Is that so…"
    li "Era això..."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4691
translate ca a4_lilly_a_faraway_future_c2b1a298:

    # hi "Fine. There was one thing."
    hi "D'acord. Si que volia fer una cosa."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4696
translate ca a4_lilly_a_faraway_future_2d3dad68:

    # "A little grin finds its way onto Lilly's face, her knowing full well that she's bested me. It makes what I want to say all the more awkward."
    "Es dibuixa un mig somriure al rostre de la Lilly, que sap perfectament que m'ha superat. Això fa que això que vull dir-li sigui encara més incòmode."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4698
translate ca a4_lilly_a_faraway_future_16dd3234:

    # hi "It was just… Akira and I were talking."
    hi "Només que... l'Akira i jo vam estar parlant."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4703
translate ca a4_lilly_a_faraway_future_ff06eaa7:

    # li "Oh?"
    li "Oh?"

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4705
translate ca a4_lilly_a_faraway_future_920d2ab8:

    # hi "What's with that tone?"
    hi "A què ve aquesta veu?"

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4710
translate ca a4_lilly_a_faraway_future_00baee4f:

    # li "You two do seem to get on well, don't you?"
    li "Sembla que us aveniu prou bé, no?"

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4712
translate ca a4_lilly_a_faraway_future_98b4bb59:

    # hi "Well, I do think she's a pretty cool person to talk with. It'd be nice if any of the teachers were anything like her."
    hi "Bé, crec que és una persona molt guai amb qui parlar. M'agradaria que algun dels nostres professors fos com ella."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4717
translate ca a4_lilly_a_faraway_future_9c5ee411:

    # li "'Cool…'"
    li "\"Guai...\""

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4719
translate ca a4_lilly_a_faraway_future_a3756245:

    # "For a moment I try to place her tone of voice, my mouth curling into a smirk as I realize it."
    "Durant un moment intento endevinar el seu to de veu i, quan me n'adono, contrec la boca en un somriure."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4721
translate ca a4_lilly_a_faraway_future_1875caca:

    # hi "You're not jealous, are you?"
    hi "No estaràs gelosa, oi?"

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4726
translate ca a4_lilly_a_faraway_future_09e69c50:

    # li "I'm not jealous!"
    li "No estic gelosa!"

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4728
translate ca a4_lilly_a_faraway_future_312b664d:

    # "After her teasing me over such a thing on our first date, I don't feel too bad having a little laugh at her expense this time around."
    "Després que es burlés de mi per una cosa així en la nostra primera cita, aquesta vegada no em sento tan malament rient-me una mica a costa seva."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4730
translate ca a4_lilly_a_faraway_future_31d75a31:

    # "As we settle down though, it's only a minor distraction from the real point of why I brought Lilly here."
    "Mentre ens conformem, però, és només una petita distracció del punt real de per què he portat la Lilly aquí."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4732
translate ca a4_lilly_a_faraway_future_c3b4c78b:

    # hi "Don't worry, it was mostly just everyday stuff. That said, there was something Akira mentioned that I wanted to talk to you about."
    hi "No et preocupis, només eren coses del dia a dia. Dit això, l'Akira va dir una cosa que volia parlar amb tu."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4734
translate ca a4_lilly_a_faraway_future_b1c93272:

    # hi "When you went to see your family in Inverness a while back, she said…"
    hi "Em va dir que quan vau anar a veure a la vostra família a Inverness..."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4739
translate ca a4_lilly_a_faraway_future_9d034a7f:

    # li "Akira told you about my family's summons, hasn't she?"
    li "L'Akira t'ha dit que la meva família vol que torni, oi?"

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4743
translate ca a4_lilly_a_faraway_future_b0b69579:

    # "Seconds tick by while I try to read Lilly's face, an odd mixture of feelings written on it. She seems annoyed, but also somewhat confused."
    "Passen els segons mentre intento llegir la cara de la Lilly, on es dibuixa una estranya barreja de sentiments. Sembla molesta, però també una mica confusa."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4754
translate ca a4_lilly_a_faraway_future_7d67e62b:

    # yu "Um… here…"
    yu "Um... teniu..."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4756
translate ca a4_lilly_a_faraway_future_e485ecdc:

    # "Yuuko tentatively slides our drinks onto the table, her presence oddly small."
    "Yuuko deixa tímidament les nostres begudes a la taula, la seva presència es torna estranyament petita."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4767
translate ca a4_lilly_a_faraway_future_d4ddd1f6:

    # "As she walks back to the counter after a quick, polite nod, I realize the air between me and Lilly is thick and our expressions are both somewhat pensive."
    "Quan torna al taulell després d'un assentiment ràpid i educat, m'adono que l'aire entre jo i la Lilly és dens i les nostres expressions són una mica pensatives."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4772
translate ca a4_lilly_a_faraway_future_9269e1f1:

    # li "Even though she says I should lead my own life, she still interferes at the worst times…"
    li "Encara que em digui que he de viure la meva vida, no para d'intervenir en els pitjors moments..."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4774
translate ca a4_lilly_a_faraway_future_88b6f486:

    # hi "I don't think you should blame Akira here. She's just looking out for you, and it's not like I can't understand her concern over this."
    hi "No crec que tot sigui culpa de l'Akira. Només et vol cuidar, i entenc que estigui preocupada per tot això."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4779
translate ca a4_lilly_a_faraway_future_4c7c3c8a:

    # "Lilly's irritation gives way to an awkward, and largely unsuccessful, attempt to mask her feelings. She really doesn't deal well with being cornered on personal topics."
    "La irritació de la Lilly dona pas a un incòmode, i en gran part infructuós, intent d'emmascarar els seus sentiments. Realment no porta gaire bé que l'acorralin amb temes personals."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4781
translate ca a4_lilly_a_faraway_future_902423e2:

    # li "I know, but… I just wanted some more time. I knew you'd have figured it out eventually, but…"
    li "Ja ho sé, però... volia més temps. Sabia que tard o d'hora te n'assabentaries, tot i que..."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4783
translate ca a4_lilly_a_faraway_future_8e352e0e:

    # hi "You were intentionally hiding this from me? For how long were you planning to do so?"
    hi "M'ho estaves amagant intencionadament? Fins quan pensaves fer-ho?"

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4788
translate ca a4_lilly_a_faraway_future_a4782a7a:

    # li "As I said, I simply wanted more time to think it through. I wanted to be sure of my decision before telling you."
    li "Ja t'ho he dit, només volia més temps per pensar-m'ho bé. Volia estar segura de la meva decisió abans de dir-t'ho."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4790
translate ca a4_lilly_a_faraway_future_ff4ecda1:

    # hi "What did you decide to do, in the end?"
    hi "I què has decidit fer al final?"

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4792
translate ca a4_lilly_a_faraway_future_ada67f7a:

    # "I know what I want her to say, but an awful feeling refuses to leave my gut."
    "Sé el que vull que digui, però m'envaeix un mal pressentiment."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4797
translate ca a4_lilly_a_faraway_future_55b7a8e0:

    # li "My family does dearly want me to return to them, and Akira will be going as well. I could still teach as a career, whether it be here or there."
    li "La meva família té moltes ganes que torni amb ells, i l'Akira també tornarà. També podria fer la carrera d'ensenyança, tant aquí com allà."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4799
translate ca a4_lilly_a_faraway_future_bf0a5494:

    # hi "So… you're going."
    hi "Així... que te'n vas."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4801
translate ca a4_lilly_a_faraway_future_15dcc89c:

    # hi "How long have you known? I already know you were asked when you first went to Scotland, about a month ago."
    hi "Quant de temps fa que ho saps? Sé que t'ho van demanar la primera vegada que vas anar a Escòcia, ara farà un mes."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4806
translate ca a4_lilly_a_faraway_future_202a1eff:

    # li "Some… time."
    li "Fa... temps."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4808
translate ca a4_lilly_a_faraway_future_3a8d8bea:

    # "My frustration very nearly boils over. The fact that she's done this affects me more than it should."
    "La meva frustració està a punt d'esclatar. El fet que hagi fet això m'afecta més del que hauria de ser."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4810
translate ca a4_lilly_a_faraway_future_a3a6a606:

    # "For her to not only be leaving but to have been actively hiding her own plans from me, and after seeming for so long to be the one solid pillar of support and reliability I could depend on…"
    "Que no només se'n vagi, sinó que m'ho hagi ocultat activament, i després de semblar durant tant de temps que és l'únic pilar sòlid de suport i fiabilitat del que podria dependre..."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4812
translate ca a4_lilly_a_faraway_future_bde1f9ac:

    # "It feels as if the foundation underneath me is suddenly shifting drastically, much faster than I can adapt to. Perhaps this isn't so much frustration as sheer unease."
    "És com si de sobte els fonaments sobre els quals m'aguanto canviessin dràsticament, molt més ràpid del que puc adaptar-me. Potser això no és tant frustració com malestar."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4814
translate ca a4_lilly_a_faraway_future_5e04a1b9:

    # hi "Lilly…"
    hi "Lilly..."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4819
translate ca a4_lilly_a_faraway_future_0a3c47c8:

    # li "I'm sorry, I just… I wanted to think this through completely. I wasn't trying to take advantage of you, please—"
    li "Perdona, però... volia pensar-m'ho realment bé. No volia aprofitar-me de tu, si us plau—"

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4821
translate ca a4_lilly_a_faraway_future_af30fcfc:

    # hi "I know, Lilly. I know. This is just really sudden."
    hi "Ho sé, Lilly. Ho sé. Però és tot tan sobtat."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4823
translate ca a4_lilly_a_faraway_future_05b540cd:

    # hi "I guess this means that once you go, we'll be breaking up?"
    hi "Suposo que això vol dir que quan marxis, tallarem?"

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4825
translate ca a4_lilly_a_faraway_future_997b2472:

    # "For one of the few times I've seen since I met her, she's genuinely lost for words."
    "Aquesta és una de les poques vegades que ho he vist des que la vaig conèixer, realment s'ha quedat sense paraules."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4827
translate ca a4_lilly_a_faraway_future_85686520:

    # "She doesn't look surprised, no doubt because the fact had dawned on her once she became sure of her decision, but rather, she appears genuinely unsure of how to deal with the situation now that it's in front of her."
    "No sembla sorpresa, sense dubtar no pas perquè se n'hagi adonat un cop ha tingut clara la seva decisió, sinó perquè realment sembla insegura de com fer front a la situació que ara té al davant."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4832
translate ca a4_lilly_a_faraway_future_657ac031:

    # li "W-we could try pursuing a long-distance relationship. They're getting more and more common these days, after all…"
    li "P-podríem intentar tenir una relació a distància. Ben mirat, cada cop són més freqüents..."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4834
translate ca a4_lilly_a_faraway_future_6736385a:

    # "Even as she says it, the tone of her voice gives away that she doesn't truly believe what she's saying."
    "Fins i tot mentre ho diu, el to de la seva veu delata que realment no creu això que està dient."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4839
translate ca a4_lilly_a_faraway_future_76b2fe88:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4842
translate ca a4_lilly_a_faraway_future_c0d1cebd:

    # n "{vspace=90}Lilly is far too old-fashioned to be able to cope with a relationship without any kind of physical presence, and even I am, to an extent. All we would ever be to each other would be a voice from the other side of the world."
    n "{vspace=90}La Lilly està massa feta a l'antiga per poder fer front a una relació sense cap mena de presència física, fins i tot ho estic jo, en certa manera. L'únic que seríem l'un per l'altre seria una veu de l'altre costat del món."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4844
translate ca a4_lilly_a_faraway_future_9efd2aca:

    # n "In the end, trying to rationalize everything is futile. Any attempts to try and connect what's happening with the future or past just seem to get more difficult the more I concentrate."
    n "Al final, intentar racionalitzar-ho tot és inútil. Qualsevol iniciativa d'intentar connectar això que està passant amb el futur o el passat es fa més difícil com més m'hi concentro."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4846
translate ca a4_lilly_a_faraway_future_869038ad:

    # n "Those quiet moments when we just walked side by side, the precious time we spent with Hanako and Akira, the casual chatter we had during lunchtimes, the times we made love, the confessions of our feelings to each other…"
    n "Aquells moments tranquils en què simplement caminàvem braç a braç, el preuat temps que passàvem amb la Hanako i l'Akira, les converses casuals que teníem durant l'hora de dinar, les vegades que fèiem l'amor, la confessió dels sentiments l'un a l'altre..."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4848
translate ca a4_lilly_a_faraway_future_2165e71a:

    # n "{vspace=90}All pointless. All just a fleeting moment in our young lives."
    n "{vspace=90}Tot un sense sentit. Tot ha estat només un moment fugaç en la nostra joventut."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4854
translate ca a4_lilly_a_faraway_future_60f4104e:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

    old "[_hi_] We're just two children pretending to be adults, aren't we?"
    new "[_hi_] Només som dos nens que intenten fer d'adults, veritat?"

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4861
translate ca a4_lilly_a_faraway_future_ff9f76f5:

    # "A long, long silence hangs in the air between us. The noise of the other patrons drinking and talking only makes the situation feel more strange and disconnected."
    "Un silenci llarguíssim flota entre nosaltres. El soroll d'uns altres clients bevent i parlant només fa que la situació sembli més estranya i desconnectada."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4863
translate ca a4_lilly_a_faraway_future_4b992fd9:

    # "Lilly's face remains low, her dejected expression clouding it."
    "La Lilly baixa la cara,  amb una expressió d'abatiment que la torba."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4870
translate ca a4_lilly_a_faraway_future_7ac860c2:

    # li "I'm sorry, Hisao."
    li "Perdona'm, Hisao."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4872
translate ca a4_lilly_a_faraway_future_3d9c385b:

    # "A simple apology, and no more. She's left entirely without any further response or comment."
    "Una simple disculpa, i res més. No li queda res a dir, cap resposta ni comentari."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4874
translate ca a4_lilly_a_faraway_future_954b8a51:

    # "With a long sigh, I gather what's left of my thoughts and ask the final question I have for her."
    "Amb un llarg sospir, reuneixo els pensaments que em queden i li faig l'última pregunta que em queda."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4876
translate ca a4_lilly_a_faraway_future_7535769f:

    # hi "When will you be going?"
    hi "Quan marxaràs?"

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4881
translate ca a4_lilly_a_faraway_future_1914dcc7:

    # li "I'll be leaving with Akira, so it'll be a little less than a week."
    li "Marxaré amb l'Akira, així que d'aquí menys d'una setmana."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4883
translate ca a4_lilly_a_faraway_future_9612d7c7:

    # hi "The beginning of summer holidays?"
    hi "Al principi de les vacances d'estiu?"

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4888
translate ca a4_lilly_a_faraway_future_7923707e:

    # li "Just a little afterward, yes."
    li "Poc després, sí."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4890
translate ca a4_lilly_a_faraway_future_f8295a1d:

    # "Her tone is unusually slow and steady, her apologetic and depressed mood all the more written to her face as she tries to hide it in her voice."
    "El seu to és inusualment lent i fer, el seu estat d'ànim penedit i deprimit encara se li llegeix més a la cara encara que intenti amagar-lo amb la seva veu."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4892
translate ca a4_lilly_a_faraway_future_c348e4e3:

    # "In the end, I can't even keep my promise of going to Tanabata with her before she leaves."
    "Al final, ni tan sols puc complir la meva promesa d'anar junts al Tanabata abans que marxi."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4901
translate ca a4_lilly_a_faraway_future_2357e108:

    # "I look down, seeing my face reflected in the by now lukewarm cup of neglected tea sitting in front of me."
    "Miro cap avall, veig el reflex de la meva cara en la tassa de te tebi que tinc al davant."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4903
translate ca a4_lilly_a_faraway_future_a85802a6:

    # "I really thought I'd left this kind of expression behind."
    "Realment pensava que havia deixat enrere aquest tipus d'expressió."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4905
translate ca a4_lilly_a_faraway_future_ba2e964c:

    # "For a while I just stare down into the still surface, trying to sort through my emotions to get at what course of action I should take, whether it be right now or in the future."
    "Durant una estona em quedo mirant la superfície immòbil, intento ordenar les meves emocions per saber quin curs d'acció hauria de prendre, sigui ara mateix o en el futur."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4907
translate ca a4_lilly_a_faraway_future_aae462d8:

    # "But, just as before, the effort is wasted."
    "Però, igual que abans, l'esforç és inútil."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4913
translate ca a4_lilly_a_faraway_future_5380132b:

    # "I glance up to see Lilly gently sipping her cooled tea without complaint, her face drawn and shoulders slumped. She looks to be deep in thought too, a strangely cold atmosphere coming between us as we isolate ourselves to mull things over."
    "Aixeco la vista i veig a la Lilly prenent tranquil·lament el seu te fred sense queixar-se, té la cara demacrada i les espatlles caigudes. Sembla que ella també està sumida en els seus pensaments, i es crea entre nosaltres una atmosfera estranyament freda mentre ens aïllem per reflexionar."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4915
translate ca a4_lilly_a_faraway_future_9d081d5c:

    # "Even as Lilly's cup slowly empties, mine remains untouched."
    "Mentre la tassa de la Lilly es va buidant lentament, la meva segueix intacta."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4917
translate ca a4_lilly_a_faraway_future_d9485347:

    # "It's a long time before I notice the rain dying down outside and the few other patrons of the Shanghai having left."
    "Passa molt de temps abans no noto que la pluja s'està amainant i que els pocs clients del Shanghai han marxat."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4925
translate ca a4_lilly_a_faraway_future_a753b678:

    # "The chill of the rapidly darkening evening permeates the dormitory hallways. While trudging down the corridor to my room, I see an unwelcome movement from up ahead."
    "El fred de la nit, que s'enfosqueix ràpidament, impregna els passadissos del dormitori. Mentre avanço pel passadís fins a la meva habitació, veig un moviment poc grat més endavant."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4935
translate ca a4_lilly_a_faraway_future_e5d72a8b:

    # "Sure enough, the opening of the door opposite mine heralds the arrival of a bespectacled Kenji."
    "Efectivament, l'obertura de la porta davant de la meva anuncia l'arribada d'un Kenji amb ulleres."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4937
translate ca a4_lilly_a_faraway_future_449731e4:

    # ke "Hey man, what's…"
    ke "Ei tio, què et..."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4942
translate ca a4_lilly_a_faraway_future_9859feba:

    # ke "Woah dude, you look awful, I think. You okay?"
    ke "Bua xaval, fas mala cara, crec. Estàs bé?"

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4944
translate ca a4_lilly_a_faraway_future_b734c4d6:

    # "He really has a knack for making any situation better."
    "Realment té el do de millorar qualsevol situació."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4946
translate ca a4_lilly_a_faraway_future_e9af70a8:

    # hi "I… don't really want to go into it. It's late."
    hi "No... tinc gaires ganes de parlar-ne. És tard."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4951
translate ca a4_lilly_a_faraway_future_ef3d2913:

    # ke "Okay. That's cool."
    ke "Val. Està bé."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4953
translate ca a4_lilly_a_faraway_future_03485739:

    # ke "If you ever want to talk about it, I'm, you know, here."
    ke "Si necessites parlar-ne en algun moment, estic, ja saps, aquí."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4955
translate ca a4_lilly_a_faraway_future_f2f96068:

    # "I look at him for a moment before surrendering my stern front and awkwardly scratching the back of my neck, embarrassed by my standoffish response to him."
    "El miro un moment abans d'abandonar la meva postura severa i rascar-me la nuca amb poca traça, avergonyit per l'actitud distant que he tingut amb ell."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4957
translate ca a4_lilly_a_faraway_future_593ce0ad:

    # hi "Thanks, Kenji."
    hi "Gràcies, Kenji."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4962
translate ca a4_lilly_a_faraway_future_a6e1fca3:

    # ke "Hey, it's cool. That's what friends are for, right?"
    ke "Eh, cap problema. Per això estan els amics, no?"

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4964
translate ca a4_lilly_a_faraway_future_fc1df606:

    # hi "Yeah, you're right. Um, seeya."
    hi "Sí, tens raó. Um, ens veiem."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4969
translate ca a4_lilly_a_faraway_future_fcd31e4f:

    # "I open the door to my own dorm room and close it behind me as he quickly waves me off."
    "Obro la porta de la meva habitació i la tanco mentre em diu adeu amb la mà."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4973
translate ca a4_lilly_a_faraway_future_cb482eb4:

    # "The solid thud the door makes against the door frame sounds out a final call for the life I've led since coming to Yamaku."
    "El patapum que fa la porta contra el marc sona com una última crida a la vida que he tingut des que vaig arribar al Yamaku."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4975
translate ca a4_lilly_a_faraway_future_b79d6578:

    # "I just stand in my darkened room, fruitlessly attempting to work out what I should do from this point onwards."
    "Em quedo dret a l'habitació a les fosqueses, intentant infructuosament esbrinar què hauria de fer a partir d'ara."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4977
translate ca a4_lilly_a_faraway_future_8dbdeba6:

    # "Just what should I do…?"
    "Què hauria de fer...?"

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4994
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_ba9a2dc8:

    # "As class ends, I simply rest my head on my hand and stare out of the window to pass the time."
    "Quan acaba la classe, simplement descanso el cap a la mà i miro per la finestra per passar el temps."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:4999
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_76b2fe88:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5002
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_898d33e1:

    # n "{vspace=60}It's been a few days since Lilly told me her plans. I haven't been to our ordinary lunchtime haunt since then, not that there would be much point."
    n "{vspace=60}Ja han passat uns dies des que la Lilly em va explicar els seus plans. Des de llavors no he tornat al nostre lloc on soliem dinar, encara que no tingui gaire sentit."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5004
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_e5d953f7:

    # n "Hanako's been busy with the newspaper club she's newly joined, and has even begun talking in class with Naomi every now and then."
    n "La Hanako ha estat ocupada amb el club periodístic on fa poc s'ha unit, i fins i tot ha començat a parlar a classe amb la Naomi de tant en tant."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5006
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_1a8ff323:

    # n "Even Lilly, aside from the fact that a meeting between us would've been awkward in any case, has been run off her feet with class representative duties as the summer holidays approach."
    n "Fins i tot la Lilly, a part del fet que una trobada entre nosaltres hauria estat incòmoda en qualsevol cas, s'ha vist desbordada per les seves tasques de representant de classe a mesura que s'acostaven les vacances d'estiu."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5008
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_2054d377:

    # n "And now, they're just about here. With the end of today's bell, the summer holidays will have begun."
    n "I araestan a punt d'arribar. Amb el final de la campana d'avui, començaran les vacances d'estiu."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5010
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_163293c1:

    # n "{vspace=90}I suppose that all I'll end up doing will be visiting my parents for the duration and lazing about my old home, now that my previous plans are entirely askew."
    n "{vspace=90}Suposo que l'únic que acabaré fent serà visitar els meus pares durant aquest temps i vaguejar per la meva antiga casa, ara que els meus plans anteriors s'han torçat completament."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5012
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_3e00f6ea:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

    old "[_n_] {vspace=60}Meanwhile, Akira and Lilly will be en route to Scotland, to live out the rest of their lives there."
    new "[_n_] {vspace=60}Mentrestant, l'Akira i la Lilly posaran rumb cap a Escòcia, per viure-hi la resta de les seves vides."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5016
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_4b63c32f:

    # n "No matter how hard I try to rationalize the idea that once the summer holidays begin, my life will return to the way it was, it simply refuses to happen."
    n "Per molt que intenti racionalitzar-ho, la idea que una vegada comencin les vacances d'estiu la meva vida tornarà a ser com era, és simplement impossible."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5018
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_f3b4bd41:

    # n "Everyone's moving on with their lives. Lilly's rejoining her family, Akira's moving up in her father's business, Hanako's gaining new friends and hobbies, and even Yuuko's moving ahead with her university aspirations."
    n "Tothom continua amb les seves vides. La Lilly es reuneix amb la seva família, l'Akira ascendeix en el negoci del seu pare, la Hanako fa nous amics i aficions, i fins i tot la Yuuko segueix amb les seves aspiracions universitàries."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5020
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_7c233514:

    # n "Even I'm moving forward, in the end. With the grades I've gotten so far in Yamaku, much less after such a rocky beginning, the path to get into teaching science as a career seems straightforward."
    n "Al final, fins i tot jo estic avançant. Amb les notes que he tret fins ara al Yamaku, i molt menys després d'un començament tan rocambolesc, el camí per a entrar en l'ensenyament de la ciència com a carrera sembla senzill."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5022
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_28de7759:

    # n "{vspace=60}I suppose I should at least be happy about that much, but it doesn't really seem to help."
    n "{vspace=60}Suposo que almenys hauria d'alegrar-me'n, però no sembla que serveixi de res."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5027
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_7fc69830:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

    old "[_mi_] Hicchan~!"
    new "[_mi_] Hicchan~!"

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5031
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_31cbe561:

    # "I quickly stop my ruminating and turn to face the bubbly voice beside me, putting on the most upbeat expression I can muster."
    "Deixo ràpidament de rumiar i em giro cap a la veu alegre que tinc al costat, posant l'expressió més optimista que puc fer."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5037
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_0da964e2:

    # "As expected, Shizune stands flanking her. I have a sneaking suspicion they want something from me."
    "Com era d'esperar, l'acompanya la Shizune. Tinc la sospita que volen alguna cosa de mi."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5039
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_420db634:

    # hi "Hey Misha, Shizune. What's up?"
    hi "Ei, Misha, Shizune. Com va?"

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5044
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_e608c143:

    # mi "Well~…"
    mi "Bé~…"

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5049
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_0f6bb5cc:

    # mi "Shicchan and I were thinking~…"
    mi "La Shicchan i jo pensavem~…"

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5054
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_36865871:

    # mi "Since we're just two poor little girls that need help with all the work we've been given just before the holidays begin~…"
    mi "Com que som dues pobres noies que necessiten ajuda amb tota la feina que ens han donat just abans de començar les vacances~…"

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5056
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_891f4b43:

    # hi "Sure, I can help."
    hi "És clar, us ajudo."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5061
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_ca0c373d:

    # mi "But Hicchan, we're really nee—"
    mi "Però Hicchan, de debò nece—"

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5068
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_450279ba:

    # mi "What?"
    mi "Què?"

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5070
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_95ca2c51:

    # "I think I broke Misha."
    "Crec que he trencat a la Misha."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5075
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_e27c8d3f:

    # "Even Shizune raises an eyebrow at her accomplice's shuddering stop in her tracks."
    "Fins i tot la Shizune aixeca una cella davant del sobresalt de la seva còmplice."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5080
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_0fad199a:

    # mi "So you'll help us, Hicchan?"
    mi "Així que ens ajudaràs, Hicchan?"

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5082
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_bebd9a73:

    # hi "I just said I would, didn't I?"
    hi "Això acabo de dir, no?"

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5084
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_f917f931:

    # "It's hardly like I have anything better to do. Maybe helping them with their work will help take my mind off the situation."
    "No tinc res millor a fer. Potser ajudar-les amb la seva feina m'ajudarà a distreure'm d'aquesta situació."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5086
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_c75451c6:

    # "Misha seems genuinely ecstatic with my response, but Shizune's expression is clouded and difficult to read. I find myself quickly averting my eyes from her own, as it almost looks like a face of pity. No doubt, it must just be my imagination."
    "La Misha sembla realment entusiasmada amb la meva resposta, però l'expressió de Shizune és tèrbola i difícil de llegir. Aparto ràpidament la meva mirada de la seva, sembla que faci cara de llàstima. Sens dubte, deu haver estat imaginació meva."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5093
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_806c624c:

    # "This is hardly the first time I've been in the student council room. Indeed, I've found myself down here often, either to help Lilly with class rep work, or to sort out one thing or another with the Student Council itself."
    "Aquesta no és la primera vegada que estic a la sala del consell d'estudiants. De fet, hi he vingut sovint, per ajudar a la Lilly amb la feina de la classe, o per resoldre una cosa o una altra amb el mateix Consell d'Estudiants."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5095
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_14a1faa8:

    # "Now, though, it's quite a different place."
    "Ara, però, és un lloc molt diferent."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5104
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_83f33810:

    # "Papers and folders are strewn across every table in the room, only a solitary little black laptop atop a single desk sticking out from the mess."
    "Hi ha papers i carpetes escampades per totes les taules de la sala, només un portàtil negre i solitari sobre un escriptori destaca entre el desordre."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5106
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_fdf81ee5:

    # "It looks positively ancient, and I'd guess it has been valiantly serving its task in archiving information for years and years."
    "Sembla molt antic, i suposo que deu fer anys que compleix valentament la seva tasca d'arxivar d'informació."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5115
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_925159e8:

    # hi "So, what needs doing? This looks like a lot to do."
    hi "Va, què s'ha de fer? Sembla que hi ha molta feina."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5121
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_ef2b123c:

    # shi "…"
    shi "..."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5123
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_ba4011b2:

    # "Shizune's expression becomes determined as she signs. It's a worrying look."
    "L'expressió de Shizune es torna decidida mentre signa. És una mirada preocupant."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5128
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_52569f6a:

    # mi "Everything, Hicchan!"
    mi "Tot, Hicchan!"

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5130
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_7d608662:

    # "My worry was well placed."
    "En feia bé de preocupar-me."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5132
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_ad57d63e:

    # hi "Everything… you say?"
    hi "Tot... dius?"

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5137
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_ef2b123c_1:

    # shi "…"
    shi "..."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5142
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_8c2240c2:

    # mi "What's left on the desks is what needs to be done."
    mi "Tot això que hi ha a les taules és el que s'ha de fer."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5147
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_50ff37f0:

    # mi "It all needs to be digitally recorded, which is what the laptop is for."
    mi "Tot s'ha de gravar digitalment, per això hi ha el portàtil."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5149
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_6e8fd188:

    # hi "And I'm guessing that I'll be the one doing this?"
    hi "I suposo que aquesta feina em toca a mi?"

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5154
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_ef2b123c_2:

    # shi "…"
    shi "..."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5159
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_debbdb56:

    # mi "Shicchan says she saw you with the computers in the library a few days ago, and that you seemed really good with them~."
    mi "La Shicchan diu que fa uns dies et va veure amb els ordinadors a la biblioteca, i semblava que els sabies fer anar força bé~."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5161
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_a9b54e29:

    # "Good with computers? I can touch-type, I guess, but it still seems like an overestimation of my skills."
    "Fer anar bé els ordinadors? Puc teclejar, suposo, però encara sembla una sobreestimació de les meves habilitats."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5163
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_3a110911:

    # hi "I was just typing up homework…"
    hi "Només teclejava els deures..."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5165
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_da6d2c61:

    # hi "Wait, Shizune was watching me do that?"
    hi "Espera, la Shizune em vigilava mentre ho feia?"

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5170
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_ef2b123c_3:

    # shi "…"
    shi "..."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5175
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_deff8aba:

    # mi "One must know their allies before they can know their enemies, of course~."
    mi "Has de conèixer els teus aliats abans de saber quins són els teus enemics, és clar~."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5180
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_9a1c988d:

    # mi "Wow, that's pretty wise…"
    mi "Vaja, això és molt savi..."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5182
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_0308fdf1:

    # "For once, it's not very hard to work out who said what."
    "Per una vegada, no és molt difícil esbrinar qui ha dit què."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5184
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_63a8e993:

    # "Nonetheless, it doesn't seem worth fighting over. Sitting at a computer doing some typing hardly seems onerous, as far as tasks to help Shizune and Misha go."
    "No obstant això, no sembla que valgui la pena lluitar. Asseure's davant d'un ordinador i teclejar una mica no sembla una tasca feixuga per ajudar a la Shizune i la Misha."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5189
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_ef2b123c_4:

    # shi "…"
    shi "..."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5194
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_61012009:

    # mi "Besides, it will help to take your mind off things~."
    mi "A més, això t'ajudarà a distreure't una mica~."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5196
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_9a3c3f70:

    # hi "Take my mind off things? Take my mind off what things?"
    hi "Distreure'm una mica? Distreure'm una mica de què?"

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5201
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_07f61780:

    # "Misha's face goes blank as she translates this for Shizune, though the latter's response is only to glance away towards the window after briefly signing."
    "La cara de la Misha es torna blanca mentre tradueix a la Shizune, encara que la resposta d'aquesta última es limita a desviar la mirada cap a la finestra després de signar breument."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5206
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_ef2b123c_5:

    # shi "…"
    shi "..."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5214
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_c6f42b30:

    # "Misha's face quickly returns to a smile as she translates back. She was confused, I guess, but Shizune is harder to pin down."
    "La Misha torna a somriure ràpidament mentre es tradueix de nou. Estava confosa, suposo, però la Shizune és més difícil de precisar."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5219
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_3057b5b3:

    # mi "I was just thinking you may like to get your mind off the exams, of course~."
    mi "Estava pensant que et distrauria una mica dels exàmens, és clar~."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5221
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_fcf988cd:

    # hi "Either way, we may as well get into it sooner rather than later. I'll go along with you."
    hi "Sigui com sigui, posem-nos-hi abans no es faci tard. Aniré amb vosaltres."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5226
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_596f2d8c:

    # mi "That's the spirit, Hicchan~!"
    mi "Així m'agrada, Hicchan~!"

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5231
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_fe15ebab:

    # "And that's the fifth spreadsheet compiled and saved. Time for the next month's…"
    "I aquest és el cinquè full de càlcul compilat i desat. Toca el del mes següent..."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5233
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_e9400956:

    # "After a little bit of fussing around, we all managed to get a bit more organized."
    "Després d'una mica de merder, aconseguim organitzar-nos una mica millor."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5235
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_71298d2c:

    # "Shizune's been gathering up the loose sheets and, thankfully, sorting them into a neat pile next to me. Meanwhile, Misha's been handling the manual writing work, her girly pink pen leaving its unmistakable mark on paper after paper."
    "La Shizune ha anat recollint fulls solts i, per sort, els ha ordenat en una pila al meu costat. Mentrestant, la Misha s'encarrega d'escriure els documents a mà, el seu bolígraf rosa femení deixa la seva marca inconfusible en un paper rere un altre."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5237
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_6e82f307:

    # "Once I got myself into a rhythm, this really wasn't so bad. Shizune and Misha also seem to be in the swing of things, wordlessly communicating as they go about their business with fervor."
    "Una vegada he agafat el ritme, no ha estat tan dolent. La Shizune i la Misha també semblen haver agafat el ritme, comunicant-se sense paraules mentre es dediquen a les seves coses amb fervor."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5239
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_a694874c:

    # "I periodically glance at the sheet beside the laptop, apparently a list of student names and matching addresses, as I dutifully enter the data written on it. I don't pay a lot of attention to what I'm typing in until I reach about midway down the page."
    "De tant en tant faig una ullada al full que hi ha al costat del portàtil, aparentment una llista de noms d'estudiants i les seves adreces, menter introdueixo diligentment les dades que hi ha. No dedico gaire atenció al que estic escrivint fins que arribo a la meitat de la pàgina."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5241
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_7d3ca920:

    # "Hakamichi… class 3-3… Huh. Her family's home is in Saitama."
    "Hakamichi... classe 3-3... Eh. La casa de la seva família és a Saitama."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5243
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_b4309d74:

    # "My idle curiosity is ended abruptly as three light taps can be heard rapping on the door."
    "La meva curiositat ociosa s'acaba bruscament quan sento tres copets lleugers a la porta."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5253
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_f7e1eda8:

    # "Misha quickly skips over to check who it is, tapping Shizune's shoulder on the way past to let her companion know what's happening."
    "La Misha salta ràpidament per comprovar qui és, tocant l'espatlla de la Shizune de camí per avisar-la de què està passant."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5258
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_a9341c18:

    # mi "Ah, you're here~."
    mi "Ah, aquí estàs~."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5260
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_aca04e95:

    # hi "Hmm? Who is it?"
    hi "Hmm? Qui hi ha?"

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5262
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_dee41bf4:

    # "With a slight pause to enter Shizune's data into the file along with all the others, I look up to check who's at the door."
    "Faig una petita pausa d'introduir les dades de Shizune al fitxer juntament amb totes les altres, i aixeco el cap per comprovar qui hi ha a la porta."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5278
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_a2b150cf:

    # "…Lilly?"
    "...Lilly?"

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5280
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_167b33c7:

    # "After giving a cursory nod to Misha in greeting, she perks her head up in her trademark manner."
    "Després de saludar a la Misha amb una inclinació, aixeca el cap amb un gest característic."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5285
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_f01fae30:

    # li "Is that Hisao?"
    li "És en Hisao?"

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5287
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_eaea8177:

    # "She's pretty darned good at working out my voice from the smallest of phrases nowadays."
    "Ja és prou maleïdament bona distingint la meva veu a partir de frases insignificants."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5289
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_144e8118:

    # hi "Yeah, it's me. Um… hey."
    hi "Sí, soc jo. Um... hola."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5294
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_ffa1d780:

    # "The atmosphere feels slightly awkward as she bows. Neither of us knows quite how intimate we should be around each other, given she's leaving in just a matter of hours."
    "Noto que l'atmosfera està una mica enrarida quan em saluda. Cap dels dos sap fins a quin punt hauria d'intimar amb l'altre, ja que marxa d'aquí a unes hores."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5296
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_41a207a0:

    # "This is a fact that, thankfully, neither the oblivious Misha nor the hardworking Shizune pick up on."
    "Per sort, ni la inconscient Misha ni la treballadora Shizune se n'adonen."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5298
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_b13a2b6e:

    # hi "So… you've got work to do as well?"
    hi "Així... que tu també has de fer feina?"

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5303
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_901c995a:

    # li "Unfortunately. I arrived as soon as I could, but my class held me up with a surprise farewell party, and I had to get changed."
    li "Malauradament. He arribat tan aviat com he pogut, però la meva classe m'ha fet una festa de comiat sorpresa, i m'havia de canviar."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5305
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_1763c8c2:

    # "I glance down at the laptop's clock. It's pretty much the end of lunchtime, so I'm guessing Lilly managed to wrangle the last period off as well."
    "Miro el rellotge del portàtil. És gairebé el final de l'hora de dinar, així que suposo que la Lilly també se les ha arreglat per agafar-se l'última hora lliure."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5310
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_0ef735c8:

    # li "I take it Shizune is here as well?"
    li "Suposo que la Shizune també està aquí?"

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5317
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_ef2b123c_6:

    # shi "…"
    shi "..."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5322
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_705b2b16:

    # mi "Of course!"
    mi "És clar!"

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5327
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_ef2b123c_7:

    # shi "…"
    shi "..."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5332
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_eb343141:

    # mi "And I've been here during all of lunchtime as well!"
    mi "I també he estat aquí durant tota l'hora de dinar!"

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5334
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_2eb58b4d:

    # "That last comment was really not needed. Shizune's baiting Lilly into another argument, I can feel it."
    "Aquest últim comentari no era realment necessari. La Shizune està provocant a la Lilly amb una altra discussió, ho noto."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5339
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_3446cd56:

    # li "I'm sorry I can't be as hardworking as you, Shizune. I'll endeavor to hire more lackeys to do my work in future, I assure you."
    li "Perdona que no sigui tan treballadora com tu, Shizune. M'encarregaré de contractar més lacais en el futur, t'ho asseguro."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5341
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_babf5d15:

    # "And Lilly just took the bait, escalating things further."
    "I la Lilly acaba de picar, complicant més les coses."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5346
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_ef2b123c_8:

    # shi "…"
    shi "..."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5351
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_0db6c3cd:

    # mi "But aren't you the one always outsourcing work to your classmates~?"
    mi "Però no ets tu qui sempre fas fer la feina als teus companys de classe~?"

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5356
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_f3ab48c5:

    # li "The difference is that they choose to help, unlike your tyrannical grip on your own class."
    li "La diferència és que ells trien ajudar-me, no com la pressió tirànica que poses a la teva classe."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5361
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_ef2b123c_9:

    # shi "…"
    shi "..."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5366
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_0d32237c:

    # mi "Tyranny works~! Even if we did things differently, we still got the same results, right~?"
    mi "Pressió tirànica~! Encara que fem les coses diferents, tenim els mateixos resultats, oi~?"

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5371
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_2c1ee9bf:

    # li "This is school, not a police state. You will have to remind me when you were appointed class monarch, I'm afraid."
    li "Això és l'escola, no l'estat policial. Em sembla que m'hauràs de recordar quan va ser que et van fer reina de classe."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5376
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_ef2b123c_10:

    # shi "…"
    shi "..."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5381
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_51115c8e:

    # mi "You have to seize power, it's not as good if it's just handed to you~! But I guess you wouldn't really understand that, right~?"
    mi "T'has d'aferrar al poder, no n'hi ha prou que te'l donin~! Però suposo que tu això no ho deus entendre pas, oi que no~?"

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5386
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_ef2b123c_11:

    # shi "…"
    shi "..."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5391
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_30e27388:

    # mi "You'll also have to remind me when monarchs were elected into their positions~."
    mi "També m'hauràs de recordar quan és que es trien els monarques per eleccions~."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5393
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_f9bb9ba8:

    # "Lilly positively bristles at this. Shizune's two-hit combo forces her onto defense."
    "La Lilly li salta en contra. El combo de dos cops de la Shizune l'obliga a defensar-se."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5398
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_6ac5bd95:

    # li "Yet for all your vaunted power, you cannot get one person to help you without forcing him."
    li "Tanmateix, malgrat tot el poder que rens, no pots aconseguir que una persona t'ajudi sense forçar-la."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5403
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_ef2b123c_12:

    # shi "…"
    shi "..."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5408
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_7e7b6298:

    # mi "But Hisao volunteered~! He's such a hard worker, he's doing this instead of meaningless socialization, right~?"
    mi "Doncs en Hisao ho ha volgut~! És tan treballador, està fent això en comptes de socialitzar sense sentit, veritat~?"

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5413
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_b46dc41c:

    # li "Is that so. Hisao?"
    li "És així. Hisao?"

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5415
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_44351a77:

    # "Ah, this is bad. I've really ended up between a rock and a hard place."
    "Oh, això no acabarà bé. Al final estic entre l'espasa i la paret."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5417
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_d20dfc77:

    # "As much as it may pain me to do this, the truth has at least a chance of stopping this argument here and now."
    "Encara que em dolgui, si dic la veritat almenys tindré l'oportunitat d'aturar aquesta discussió aquí i ara."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5419
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_d621a843:

    # hi "It's okay, Lilly, they didn't harass me to come or anything."
    hi "Està bé, Lilly, no m'han obligat a venir ni res."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5424
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_d0950a30:

    # "Lilly gives me a disapproving grimace, silently radiating her strong feelings of displeasure in my general direction."
    "La Lilly fa una ganyoya de desaprovació, destil·lant en silenci els seus forts sentiments de disgust cap a mi."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5426
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_58c3de22:

    # "She can be quite scary when she wants to be, though thankfully that isn't often."
    "Pot fer força por quan s'ho proposa, tot i que, per sort, no és gaire sovint."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5431
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_ef2b123c_13:

    # shi "…"
    shi "..."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5436
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_984f30d6:

    # mi "Hicchan, you make that sound like it's a regular occurrence~…"
    mi "Hicchan, ho dius com si fos una cosa habitual~..."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5438
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_38e9aca9:

    # hi "It isn't?"
    hi "No ho és?"

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5440
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_fd92140a:

    # hi "In the end, it doesn't matter so long as everything's getting done at a good pace. Let's just get this work over with so we can go home."
    hi "Al capdavall, tant és sempre que aconseguim acabar la feina a un bon ritme. Acabem-ho tot per poder marxar cap a casa."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5451
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_204fc061:

    # "Shizune snorts derisively and gets back to marking off the sheet in front of her, while Lilly sighs and finds her way along the room with her hand following the filing cabinets lined along the wall."
    "A la Shizune se li escapa el riure per sota el nas i torna a posar-se a marcar el full que té davant, mentre la Lilly sospira i s'obre pas per l'habitació seguint amb la mà els arxivadors alineats al llarg de la paret."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5453
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_9eb6dd5c:

    # "This would mark the only time I've managed to successfully defuse one of these situations, but the grudging ceasefire built around mutual fear and respect makes this feel more like the Cold War than any real peace."
    "Aquesta és l'única vegada que he aconseguit calmar amb èxit una d'aquestes situacions, però l'alto el foc fet a contracor fet al voltant de la por i el respecte mutus fa que això sembli més la Guerra Freda que qualsevol pau real."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5455
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_fe7ae890:

    # "I can't take all the credit though; Lilly's leaving has surely affected Shizune to some extent, to make her give up so easily."
    "Però no puc atribuir-me tot el mèrit; que la Lilly marxi segurament ha afectat fins a cert punt a la Shizune, i per això s'ha rendit tan fàcilment."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5463
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_d79693f8:

    # "Moments before getting back to my work, I notice Lilly reaching up to grab something from above a filing cabinet. I almost offer to help, but her height gives her ample ability to take it down safely."
    "Abans de tornar a la meva feina, noto que la Lilly s'estira cap amunt per agafar alguna cosa de dalt d'un arxivador. Gairebé m'ofereixo a ajudar-la, però amb la seva alçada en té prou per poder  baixar-lo amb seguretat."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5469
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_97dfe1a2:

    # "Once she sets the strangely shaped device on the desk beside me, I realize just what it is… sort of… as she takes the old green covering off and sits down."
    "Quan posa l'estrany dispositiu a l'escriptori del meu costat, m'adono de què deu ser... més o menys... mentre li treu la vella coberta verda i s'asseu."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5478
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_be2f044e:

    # "At first glance it seems to be an old metallic blue typewriter, but it doesn't take me long to realize it's far from ordinary."
    "A primera vista sembla ser una vella màquina d'escriure d'un blau metàl·lic, però no trigo gaire a adonar-me que dista molt de ser normal."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5480
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_b8320dfe:

    # "It has far fewer keys than expected, and those it has show no lettering printed on them. Only the shadows cast by the tiny Braille dots on them give a hint to the thing's purpose."
    "Té moltes menys tecles del que esperava, i a les que té no s'hi veu cap lletra impresa. Només l'ombra que projecten els petits punts Braille et donen una pista al propòsit que té."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5482
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_ca6a2bcb:

    # hi "Blind typewriter?"
    hi "Una màquina d'escriure per cecs?"

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5494
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_b4369218:

    # li "Oh, this? Well, you're not far off."
    li "Oh, això? Bé, t'hi has acostat."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5496
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_3d9da9eb:

    # li "It's normally called a Perkins Brailler, but it's basically a typewriter for the blind, yes. It presses Braille into the page rather than text, which is why it has fewer keys."
    li "Es coneix com a màquina Perkins, però bàsicament és una màquina d'escriure per cecs, sí. Escriu braille en una pàgina en comptes de lletres, per això té menys tecles."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5498
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_c521b5a1:

    # hi "Huh… that's really neat."
    hi "Ja... és realment curiós."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5503
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_4e1cbe36:

    # "She gives a lighthearted grin at my curiosity over it. I have to admit that it appeals to my sense of novelty."
    "Somriu despreocupada davant la meva curiositat. He d'admetre que atreu el meu sentit de la novetat."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5508
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_a09a12dd:

    # "Without further ado, we each get back to our allotted tasks. The loud clunking of the mechanics in Lilly's Brailler and the tapping of the laptop's old and weary keyboard quickly fill the room."
    "Sense més preàmbuls, cadascú torna a la seva tasca. De seguida l'habitació s'omple del soroll mecànic de la màquina Brailler de la Lilly i el so empipador del vell teclat del portàtil."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5510
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_f752ff71:

    # "It's a nice atmosphere, really. Everyone knows what they have to do, and Lilly and I get to sit beside each other and exchange the odd word as we work away."
    "És un ambient agradable, de debò. Tothom sap què ha de fer, i la Lilly i jo ens asseiem l'un al costat de l'altre i intercanviem alguna que una altra paraula mentre avancem."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5512
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_2dd87bac:

    # "Nostalgic. That's what it feels like."
    "Nostàlgia. Això és el que sento."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5514
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_a89789bd:

    # "It's pleasant, but just slightly stained with the knowledge that our time together is nearing its end."
    "És una sensació agradable, però també està tenyida amb el fet de saber que s'està acabant el nostre temps junts."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5521
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_f4da2aa9:

    # li "Excuse me, Misha?"
    li "Disculpa, Misha?"

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5532
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_11011c7b:

    # "To properly address her, Misha bounces over from the filing cabinet she's peering into, in spite of Lilly's lack of sight. For a moment I think it strange, but then realize it's exactly what I do."
    "Per parlar-hi correctament, la Misha hi va fent saltirons des de l'arxivador on està mirant, malgrat que la Lilly no la veu. D'entrada se'm fa estrany, però després m'adono que faig exactament el mateix."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5534
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_213e5f33:

    # mi "What's up?"
    mi "Què passa?"

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5539
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_78956ae4:

    # li "Could you ask Shizune where the attendance records for class 3-2 are? I think they've been moved."
    li "Podries preguntar-li a la Shizune on són els documents d'assistència de la classe 3-2? Crec que els han mogut."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5544
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_983c7b7f:

    # mi "Okie dokie!"
    mi "Okie dokie!"

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5551
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_fc72e5b0:

    # "And with that, she flitters off to Shizune, who's working at a table behind us."
    "I dit això, voleia cap a la Shizune, que està treballant en una taula darrere nostre."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5553
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_a5c985e7:

    # "Lilly's familiarity with the council room, and the efficiency with which she works, remind me that she, Misha and Shizune used to all work together in the Student Council."
    "La familiaritat de la Lilly amb la sala del consell i l'eficiència amb què treballa, em recorden que tan ella, com la Misha i la Shizune, treballaven juntes en el Consell d'Estudiants."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5555
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_75c2c62a:

    # "Maybe this is a fitting end for her stay in Yamaku; working away just like she used to, surrounded by those she loves and, at least, liked."
    "Potser aquest és un final adequat per a la seva estada al Yamaku; treballant com abans, envoltada de qui estima i, almenys, apreciava."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5557
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_7f4aae86:

    # "I look up, getting taken off-guard by Shizune sorting through a drawer, rather than Misha."
    "Aixeco la vista i em sorprèn veure a la Shizune remenar un calaix, en comptes de la Misha."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5562
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_8dd98c90:

    # "Sure enough, she plucks out a manila folder, entirely blank save for the just barely visible bumps on its front, and holds it in front of Lilly."
    "Efectivament, treu una carpeta Manila, completament buida tret dels bonys en prou feines visibles que té al davant, i la posa davant de la Lilly."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5564
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_14e7e6c7:

    # "Lilly's hand flits over it to check what it is, her fingers feeling out the dots of Braille and confirming it's what she asked for."
    "La Lilly hi passa la mà per comprovar de què és, nota els punts de Braille amb els dits i confirma que és la que ha demanat."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5569
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_1dbf869f:

    # li "Thank you, Misha."
    li "Gràcies, Misha."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5571
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_77bc6cca:

    # "No reply."
    "No hi ha resposta."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5576
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_cd46d09c:

    # "No reply, that is, save for an odd grin… no… smile… on Shizune's face."
    "No hi ha resposta, excepte per una ganyota estranya... no... un somriure... a la cara de la Shizune."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5584
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_e1f13eaa:

    # "A couple of seconds pass before Lilly clicks that it isn't Misha behind her, but Shizune. Her momentary look of surprise is replaced by a slightly bashful smile."
    "Passen un parell de segons abans que la Lilly s'adoni que no és la Misha qui està darrere seu, sinó la Shizune. Substitueix l'expressió momentània de sorpresa per un somriure lleugerament tímid."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5586
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_5b16cebc:

    # "For a few moments, the room is all but still and silent."
    "Durant uns instants, l'habitació està tranquil·la i en silenci."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5588
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_f1858dd2:

    # "Eventually, though, Shizune strides back to her workstation and Lilly begins typing once again."
    "Finalment, la Shizune torna al seu lloc de treball i la Lilly comença a teclejar de nou."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5590
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_af0f0166:

    # "It only lasted a handful of seconds in all, but it feels like years of communication were made up for in that one silent exchange."
    "Només dura uns segons, però sembla com si aquest intercanvi silenciós hagi compensat anys de comunicació."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5597
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_82fc4164:

    # hi "There, finished."
    hi "Ja està, acabat."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5599
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_b6aa9297:

    # "I lean my head back and rub my eyes to try and work away their weariness. Staring at that small and rather poor screen has taken its toll."
    "Tiro el cap enrere i em frego els ulls per intentar dissipar el cansament. Mirar tan fixament aquesta petita i bastant pobra pantalla m'ha passat factura."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5606
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_ed69ccf3:

    # li "Excellent timing; the only thing left is to file these away and I'll have my workload finished as well."
    li "Molt oportú: a mi només em queda enviar aquests arxius  i també hauré acabat la meva feina."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5608
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_ca515b96:

    # hi "Good. I can pack up the Brailler and put it away while you do that."
    hi "Bé. Puc recollir la Parker i guardar-la mentre tu ho fas."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5613
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_10354753:

    # li "Thank you, Hisao."
    li "Gràcies, Hisao."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5615
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_3d60491d:

    # hi "Misha, are you and Shizune far from being done?"
    hi "Misha, us queda molta feina a tu i la Shizune?"

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5617
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_31447cd7:

    # "I look around for the two as I replace the cover over the Brailler, only to see them waiting at the door. I guess they must be waiting for us."
    "Les busco mentre poso la coberta sobre la màquina Brailler, però les veig esperant a la porta. Suposo que ens han estat esperant."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5625
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_a596d4c0:

    # "With a minimum of wasted time, we file and pack up everything that remains and join them."
    "Sense perdre gaire temps, arxivem i empaquetem tot el que queda i ens reunim amb elles."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5627
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_6a2981a1:

    # hi "Thanks for waiting, you two."
    hi "Gràcies per esperar, noies."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5632
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_ff1567c1:

    # mi "We couldn't just take off without you, Hicchan, you've been a great help!"
    mi "No podíem marxar sense tu, Hicchan, ens has estat de molta ajuda!"

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5637
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_95a65179:

    # "Shizune nods approvingly, pleased with my efforts."
    "La Shizune assenteix, satisfeta amb els meus esforços."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5639
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_8440583f:

    # hi "I guess… that's the last class representative work done and over with, then."
    hi "Suposo... que aquesta és l'última feina que et queda per fer com a delegada de classe."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5644
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_2d44ab79:

    # li "That's right."
    li "Així és."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5649
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_67fb6b53:

    # mi "I'll miss you, Lilly. I think it was fun working with you."
    mi "Et trobaré a faltar, Lilly. Crec que ha estat divertit treballar amb tu."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5654
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_48d67842:

    # li "Thank you, Misha. It's been good working with you… and Shizune."
    li "Gràcies, Misha. També m'ha agradat treballar amb tu... i la Shizune."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5659
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_3bfe89b2:

    # "Shizune thinks for a moment before formulating her response. It's not that she often communicates without thinking, quite the opposite, but this time it's even more considered than usual."
    "La Shizune pensa un moment abans de formular la seva resposta. No és que normalment es comuniqui sense pensar, tot al contrari, però aquesta vegada s'hi pensa més del que és habitual."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5664
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_ef2b123c_14:

    # shi "…"
    shi "..."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5669
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_cd45517b:

    # "Misha looks a little surprised before passing on the message."
    "La Misha sembla una mica sorpresa abans de transmetre el missatge."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5674
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_88fff0e6:

    # mi "Shizune says… you'd better do your work over there better than you did it here."
    mi "La Shizune diu... que serà millor que facis la teva feina allà millor del que l'has fet aquí."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5679
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_abb378c2:

    # "Far from taking offense, Lilly giggles into her hand."
    "Lluny d'ofendre's, la Lilly riu tapant-se la boca amb la mà."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5684
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_c41c2fd1:

    # li "If that's the case, then please tell Shizune to give those still here a little more understanding in the future."
    li "Si és així, si us plau digues-li a la Shizune que en el futur sigui més comprensiva amb tots els que encara estan aquí."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5686
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_3ade9737:

    # "Competitive until the last. Maybe Shizune and Lilly aren't so different after all."
    "Competitiva finsal final. Pot ser que la Shizune i la Lilly no siguin tan diferents."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5691
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_ef2b123c_15:

    # shi "…"
    shi "..."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5696
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_f4058150:

    # mi "Shicchan says that she'll be checking to make sure you live up to your end of the promise."
    mi "La Shicchan diu que s'assegurarà que compleixis la teva part de la promesa."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5701
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_ab36a226:

    # li "Then that's how it will be."
    li "Doncs així serà."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5706
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_8a3f90d7:

    # li "I'd better be off, then. Goodbye, Shizune. Goodbye, Misha."
    li "Serà millor que marxi. Adeu, Shizune. Adeu, Misha."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5711
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_05e6a5dc:

    # li "Hisao?"
    li "Hisao?"

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5713
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_f1521869:

    # "Lilly takes a hold of my arm in hers, there being no need for a cane if I'm here to guide her. With a nod of farewell to the two, we set off out the door and make our way to the school grounds."
    "La Lilly m'agafa el braç, no necessita un bastó si jo soc aquí per guiar-la. Amb un gest de comiat cap a les dues, sortim per la porta i ens dirigim al recinte de l'escola."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5715
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_c5e98d19:

    # "As I turn to wave goodbye to them, I notice Shizune's gaze lingering on Lilly. They may annoy each other, but family bonds aren't easily broken."
    "Quan em giro per acomiadar-me, veig que la Shizune està mirant a la Lilly. Pot ser que es molestin mútuament, però els llaços familiars no es trenquen tan fàcilment."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5720
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_4439ced6:

    # hi "Got all your papers sorted, then?"
    hi "Ja tens tots els papers en regla?"

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5725
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_0816d934:

    # li "Yes, they've all been filled out and handed in."
    li "Sí, ja els he emplenat i presentat."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5727
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_991b4147:

    # hi "On top of things as always, aren't you?"
    hi "Tu sempre estàs al dia, eh?"

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5734
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_0ae1a1d8:

    # "She gives an earnest smile at the compliment, but it feels as if her happiness is just a veneer over the fact that she's fully aware of how much she's leaving behind."
    "Aquest elogi li dibuixa un somriure, però sembla que aquesta felicitat és només una façana, ja que és plenament conscient de tot allò que deixa enrere."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5736
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_972a4365:

    # "It reminds me of how she was like when I first met her; always smiling, always that little bit aloof, always that little distance away from everybody."
    "Em recorda com era quan la vaig conèixer per primera vegada; sempre somreia, sempre una mica al marge, sempre una mica allunyada de tothom."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5738
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_54ec4834:

    # "Even now, she still maintains that air around many others, especially those she's not close to. I had hoped that our time together would have changed that fact."
    "Fins i tot ara, encara té aquest aire amb moltes altres persones, especialment aquelles amb qui no està gaire unida. Esperava que el nostre temps junts ho canviés."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5743
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_64b5a51f:

    # "Our pace slows, the two of us coming to a halt in the all but empty school gardens."
    "Alentim el ritme i ens aturem als jardins de l'escola, pràcticament buits."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5748
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_2e96ef00:

    # li "Hisao? Is something the…"
    li "Hisao? Hi ha alguna cosa que..."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5755
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_d26fefeb:

    # "Lilly's words are cut short as I turn and wrap my arms around her, pulling her tight. I may not usually be given to such impulsive actions, but I just want to be close to her, even if it's the last time I'll be able to."
    "La Lilly s'interromp quan em giro i la rodejo amb els braços, agafant-la amb força. Normalment, no soc tan impulsiu, però vull estar a prop seu, encara que sigui una última vegada."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5757
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_6ff384ec:

    # "All the other students have retreated to their dormitories and homes, only the ruffling of leaves in the breeze making any sound whatsoever."
    "Tots els altres estudiants s'han retirat als seus dormitoris i cases, només se sent la remor de les fulles que fan amb el ventet que bufa."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5762
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_60a360a8:

    # "As I draw back, I can see she has dropped her carefully maintained smile."
    "Quan me'n separo, veig que ha abandonat el somriure que havia mantingut curosament fins ara."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5764
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_f2e09604:

    # "Her hand hesitates, wanting neither to leave nor to stay on my features."
    "Li vacil·la la mà, que no vol ni marxar ni quedar-se amb mi."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5766
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_ca35306a:

    # "She is putting up a brave show, but her slight trembling gives her away. Lilly may be able to control herself well, but even she can't hold her composure together now."
    "Es fa la valenta, però els tremolors la delaten. Pot ser que la Lilly sigui capaç de controlar-se bé, però ni tan sols ella pot mantenir la seva compostura en un moment així."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5768
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_7c1c5db7:

    # "This is the woman I've come to love, but also the one who in all too short a time will leave the country forever."
    "Aquesta és la dona que he arribat a estimar, però també la que d'aquí a poc deixarà enrere aquest país per sempre."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5770
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_7ac860c2:

    # li "I'm sorry, Hisao."
    li "Perdona'm, Hisao."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5772
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_e2e0b00f:

    # hi "It's okay. You've got your own life to lead, after all."
    hi "Està bé. Després de tot, has de viure la teva vida."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5777
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_15fdc6c6:

    # "We walk up the hallway in the girls' dormitory hand in hand, our emotions by now largely quelled. Nevertheless, our hands grip each other's much more tightly than before."
    "Caminem agafats de la mà pel passadís del dormitori femení, amb les emocions ja prou calmades. No obstant això, ens agafem les mans amb molta més força que abans."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5779
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_7bd76dcb:

    # "Faint, muffled voices can be heard from Lilly's room, the origins of which aren't difficult to guess."
    "Des de l'habitació de la Lilly, se senten unes veus apagades que no costa massa endevinar de qui són."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5802
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_e3ead60d:

    # "The moment she opens the door, Hanako bursts through and wraps her arms around Lilly, taking her very obviously by surprise."
    "Quan obre la porta, la Hanako esclata i rodeja a la Lilly amb els braços, agafant-la òbviament per sorpresa."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5804
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_ec032f36:

    # ha "Lilly! Lilly!"
    ha "Lilly! Lilly!"

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5809
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_a30634e4:

    # li "Ha-Hanako…?"
    li "Ha-Hanako…?"

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5814
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_5d8fac92:

    # ha "I'm going to miss you… Lilly…"
    ha "Et trobaré a faltar... Lilly..."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5819
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_0a0e0fa3:

    # "As expected, she's on the verge of tears. Lilly gently rubs Hanako's hair with her hand in response, then pulls back and gives a warm, reassuring smile."
    "Com era d'esperar, està a punt de plorar. La Lilly li acaricia suaument els cabells a la Hanako en resposta, després es tira enrere i li dedica  un somriure càlid i tranquil·litzador."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5829
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_670423ef:

    # "Looking beyond Hanako, Akira can be seen getting up from the side of Lilly's bed and scratching her head."
    "Darrere de la Hanako, hi ha l'Akira que s'aixeca del costat del llit menter es grata el cap."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5834
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_0d666b3b:

    # "Her eyes turn from Lilly and Hanako to me, a stilted, weak smile hanging on her face. I try to return a more genuinely happy look, but the result is probably just the same."
    "Desvia els ulls de la Lilly i la Hanako cap a mi, amb un somriure forçat i dèbil a la cara. Intento tornar-li una mirada més genuïnament feliç, però el resultat deu ser el mateix."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5839
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_22eccbc9:

    # aki "So, everything set? Managed to hold back from killing Shizune?"
    aki "I doncs, tot preparat? Has pogut aguantar les ganes de matar a la Shizune?"

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5844
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_0f534d89:

    # "The comment draws an amused giggle from her sister."
    "Aquest comentari li provoca una rialleta de diversió a la seva germana."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5846
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_4282f3d6:

    # li "Yes, I have everything in order, and yes, I managed not to. Have you packed everything you need?"
    li "Sí, tot preparat i sí, me les he aguantat. Has fet la maleta amb totes les coses que necessitaràs?"

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5851
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_fd55f1ad:

    # aki "Got the two bags right here, but there's still some stuff left at the Hakamichis' home. I can pick that up while we wait there for tomorrow evening's flight, though."
    aki "Hi tinc dues maletes aquí, però encara em queden algunes coses a casa d'en Hakamichi. Ho puc anar a buscar mentre esperem el vol de demà a la nit."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5853
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_7b132e06:

    # "Akira gives the two large black traveling bags on the floor a hearty pat. She probably came to help pack and make sure everything was in order on Lilly's end, before going together with her."
    "L'Akira fa un copet efusiu amb la mà a les dues grans bosses negres de viatge de terra. Probablement havia vingut a ajudar-la i assegurar-se que tot estava en ordre per part de la Lilly, abans d'anar-se'n."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5858
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_e33dd8f6:

    # ha "Lilly… will you be okay… over there?"
    ha "Lilly... ja estaràs bé... allà? "

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5863
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_692726c4:

    # li "I'll be all right, I assure you. I'll have Akira looking after me as well, and you know that she's reliable."
    li "Estaré bé, t'ho prometo. L'Akira també em cuidarà, i ja saps que és de fiar."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5868
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_cc6cff5b:

    # ha "But…"
    ha "Però..."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5873
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_c27aae36:

    # li "Don't worry, Hanako. I have your phone number after all, so we can stay in touch. With Akira's help, I could send you things over the Internet as well."
    li "No et preocupis, Hanako. Ja saps que tinc el teu telèfon, així que estarem en contacte. Amb l'ajuda de l'Akira, et podré enviar coses per internet també."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5878
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_321a4a50:

    # aki "Hey, don't use me just because you won't learn how to use a computer."
    aki "Ei, no em facis servir d'excusa només perquè no vols aprendre com fer servir un ordinador."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5884
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_06fc1242:

    # "Hanako and Lilly both giggle briefly, the mood lightening ever so little."
    "La Hanako i la Lilly riuen breument, s'alleugereix una mica."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5889
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_912e6634:

    # li "That goes for you too though, Hisao. I promise I'll contact you once I'm in Scotland."
    li "Això també va per tu, Hisao. Et prometo que em posaré amb contacte amb tu un cop arribi a Escòcia."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5891
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_f64eb7b1:

    # hi "I know. I'll be looking forward to it."
    hi "Ho sé. Ho estaré esperant."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5893
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_2fce4c56:

    # "Her offer may be kind, but we both know that this is tantamount to breaking up. Neither of us has any illusions as to how well we'd manage a long-distance relationship."
    "La seva oferta és amable, però tots dos sabem que això equival a tallar. Cap dels dos es fa il·lusions sobre com de bé gestionaríem una relació de llarga distància."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5895
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_46ea4a21:

    # "With nary a word of prompting, the four of us begin the long, solemn walk to the school gate."
    "Sense dir res més, tots quatre iniciem el camí llarg i solemne fins a la porta de l'escola."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5900
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_4c33807a:

    # "The numerous lamps scattered around the Yamaku grounds fail to do much more than provide pinpoints of light in an otherwise dense darkness."
    "Les nombroses llums disperses pels terrenys del Yamaku no fan més que proporcionar punts de llum en una foscor ben densa."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5902
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_ec7feb10:

    # "A car parked on the road just outside the school grounds comes into view, its shining black exterior reflecting the dimly lit lamps of Yamaku. I call out to Akira in an effort to alleviate a bit the heavy atmosphere."
    "Apareix un cotxe aparcat a la carretera dels afores de l'escola, un exterior d'un negre brillant que reflecteix els llums poc il·luminats del Yamaku. Crido a l'Akira en un esforç per alleujar una mica aquesta atmosfera tan pesada."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5904
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_8e03de65:

    # hi "That your car? What kind is it?"
    hi "Aquest és el teu cotxe? De quin tipus és?"

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5909
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_a786796b:

    # aki "Don't know much about cars, do you? It's a Lancer Evo. Solid and speedy."
    aki "No en saps gaire de cotxes tu, oi? És un Lancer Evo. És sòlid i ràpid."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5911
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_758fbff3:

    # "Well, it's not as if her comment on my knowledge is off the mark. I've never really taken an interest in them."
    "Bé, no que el seu comentari sobre els meus coneixements estigui gaire equivocat. Mai m'han interessat gaire."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5916
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_72073cdd:

    # "She gives a small sigh."
    "Deixa anar un sospir contingut."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5921
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_f8a6f10e:

    # aki "She's been good. Pity I have to part with it tomorrow, just like the summerhouse. You guys were the last to visit it before it changed hands."
    aki "S'ha portat bé. Una llàstima que me n'hagi de despendre demà, igual que la casa d'estiueig. Vosaltres heu estat els últims a visitar-la abans del canvi de mans."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5923
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_17bf114b:

    # "Turning back from my rather faulty attempt at smalltalk, I glance at Hanako and Lilly, following behind us."
    "Miro enrere després del meu intent fallit de fer conversa, i veig a la Hanako i la Lilly seguint-nos."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5934
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_f3af2053:

    # "By rights, Hanako should be leading Lilly, but it's rather definitely the other way around as she clings tightly to Lilly's arm."
    "Per anar bé, la Hanako hauria de guiar a la Lilly, però és definitivament a l'inrevés, ja que s'agafa amb força al braç de la Lilly."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5936
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_6f9bd68e:

    # "It's a depressing sight."
    "És un espectacle depriment."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5941
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_e968acd8:

    # aki "So… I guess this is it."
    aki "Doncs... suposo que això és tot."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5946
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_499574f0:

    # li "Indeed."
    li "Efectivament."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5948
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_b9bf4797:

    # "Although the time for everyone to say their farewells is now, nobody really wants to take the first step. It's as if the longer nobody speaks, the better the chances of them simply not leaving."
    "Encara que ha arribat el moment d'acomiadar-se, ningú vol fer el primer pas. És com si com més temps passa sense que ningú digui res, més possibilitats hi ha que simplement no marxin."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5953
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_542810bd:

    # ha "Lilly… do you really have to go?"
    ha "Lilly... de debò te n'has d'anar?"

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5958
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_6fe8f020:

    # li "I'm sorry, Hanako. I won't be leaving you forever, though; I can still call you. Hisao will still be here as well."
    li "Em sap greu, Hanako. Però no marxaré per sempre: encara ens podem trucar. I en Hisao també es queda aquí."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5960
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_cf078391:

    # "I nod, but Hanako just clutches all the tighter to Lilly's arm."
    "Assenteixo, però la Hanako s'aferra encara més al braç de la Lilly."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5962
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_6141b3ec:

    # "After spending so long without anyone to call family, it must be excruciating to have to say goodbye to the one person that was as close to a mother as anyone could have been in her life."
    "Després de passar tant de temps sense ningú a qui dir família, deu ser insuportable haver de dir adeu a l'única persona que t'ha estat el més proper a una mare del que cap altra persona havia estat en la vida."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5967
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_bced5fc1:

    # "Lilly lets out a long, sad breath. All Akira and I can really do is stand by quietly on the sidelines, since the only person that can solve this would be Lilly herself."
    "La Lilly deixa anar un sospir llarg i trist. L'únic que podem fer l'Akira i jo és quedar-nos en silenci al marge, ja que l'única persona que pot resoldre-ho és la Lilly."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5969
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_c99a4530:

    # "Eventually, Lilly pulls her arm from Hanako's grip and holds both of her shoulders gently, a much more decisive way of address than I've ever seen Lilly take with her."
    "Finalment, la Lilly retira el braç de les mans de la Hanako i li agafa les espatlles amb suavitat, una manera molt més decisiva d'adreçar-se-li del que mai havia vist a la Lilly fer amb ella."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5974
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_95b7ae7f:

    # li "Hanako, remember when we first met?"
    li "Hanako, te'n recordes de quan ens vam veure per primera vegada?"

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5979
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_442386e6:

    # li "When you entered my room for the first time after overhearing my consoling of a friend, you didn't say a single word for the entire night. Even as I poured you tea and talked, you sat silently and simply listened to what I said."
    li "Quan vas entrar a la meva habitació després d'escoltar com consolava un amic, no vas dir res en tota la nit. Fins i tot quan et vaig servir el te i vaig parlar, vas seure i et vas limitar a escoltat tot el que deia."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5981
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_448c5b3b:

    # li "It took many quiet meetings like that before you began to open up to me, but as you began to, I felt some of the happiest moments I've ever felt."
    li "Vam tenir moltes trobades silencioses com aquesta abans no et comencessis a obrir amb mi, però quan vas començar a fer-ho, va ser un dels moments més feliços de la meva vida."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5986
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_14fa1c1a:

    # li "I didn't become your friend because I pitied you, Hanako. I became your friend because I knew you were hiding not just from me, but from everyone."
    li "No em vaig fer amiga teva perquè sentis llàstima de tu, Hanako. Em vaig fer amiga teva perquè sabia que t'amagaves no només de mi, sinó de tothom."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5988
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_0beea414:

    # li "Your ambitions, personality, interests, tastes… I didn't know any of them, and neither did anybody else."
    li "Les teves ambicions, personalitat, interessos, gustos... No en sabia res de tot això, ni jo ni ningú."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5993
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_249d521f:

    # li "As you showed yourself to me though, I began to realize the person that you were, and became sure that our meeting was a very special moment."
    li "Però quan em vas mostrar com eres, vaig començar a veure quin tipus de persona eres i vaig tenir la certesa que la nostra trobada era un moment molt especial."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:5998
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_8b1ee18e:

    # ha "But I…"
    ha "Però em..."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6000
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_74e89e51:

    # "Lilly cuts her words short as she brings her hand to Hanako's head and brushes her bangs to the side, gently pressing her lips to Hanako's forehead."
    "La Lilly interromp el que estava dient mentre apropa la mà al cap a la Hanako i li aparta el serrell capa un costat, i prem suaument els llavis contra el front de la Hanako."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6005
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_d867be5a:

    # "As she pulls her head back, leaving Hanako all but speechless and her eyes moist, Lilly beams a wide smile."
    "Mentre tira el cap enrere, deixant així a la Hanako sense paraules i amb els ulls humits, la Lilly fa un gran somriure."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6007
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_f7cb31f8:

    # li "I believe you are a very beautiful person, Hanako, and I am certain that you will become a strong and confident woman."
    li "Crec que ets una persona meravellosa, Hanako, i n'estic segura que et convertiràs en una dona forta i plena de confiança."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6009
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_aaf5ff3e:

    # li "You are a very dear friend, and someone whom I love very much. Just like Hisao, I will never forget you for as long as I live."
    li "Ets una amiga del meu cor  a qui estimo moltíssim. Com a en Hisao, no us oblidaré mentre estigui viva."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6014
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_379bea99:

    # li "I may be leaving, but you have your own life here to lead. Just as I do, you have your own friends and hobbies, and your own hopes after graduation. I want you to devote yourself to them, even after I'm not around any more."
    li "Pot ser que jo marxi, però tu tens la teva vida per fer aquí. Com jo, tens els teus amics i aficions, i les teves esperances després de la graduació. Vull que t'hi centris, fins i tot quan jo ja no hi sigui."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6019
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_125b77fe:

    # li "That is why I think you will be okay. Because you are your own self, with your own life. You yourself proved that to me."
    li "Per això crec que estaràs bé. Perquè ets tu mateixa i tens la teva vida. Tu mateixa m'ho has demostrat."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6024
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_2dff8f71:

    # "Hanako lowers her head in embarrassment, but nods as she does so."
    "La Hanako baixa el cap avergonyida, però assenteix mentre ho fa."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6026
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_6364306d:

    # ha "I… I understand…"
    ha "Ho... ho entenc..."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6028
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_12c90793:

    # ha "I know I have to say goodbye… I know you have to go your own way…"
    ha "Sé que t'he de dir adeu... Sé que he de continuar el meu camí..."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6033
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_8826e3ff:

    # ha "But… thank you, Lilly. For everything."
    ha "Però... gràcies, Lilly. Per tot el que has fet per mi."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6038
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_0009b234:

    # li "Thank you, Hanako. Will you be okay?"
    li "Gràcies, Hanako. Creus que estaràs bé?"

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6040
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_7350b77c:

    # "There are a few seconds of silence before the answer comes."
    "Es fan uns segons de silenci abans que arribi la resposta."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6045
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_8bfc9071:

    # ha "I will."
    ha "Ho estaré."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6050
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_15f77360:

    # "Lilly smiles, undoubtedly at least partly in relief."
    "La Lilly somriu, sens dubte, en part està alleujada."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6055
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_517ed3b0:

    # li "That makes me very happy, then. Goodbye."
    li "Doncs això em fa molt feliç. Adeu."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6060
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_6bacc818:

    # ha "Goodbye… Lilly."
    ha "Adeu... Lilly."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6065
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_e560bced:

    # li "And farewell to you as well, Hisao."
    li "Adeu-siau a tu també, Hisao."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6067
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_552d61f0:

    # hi "Goodbye. I'll miss you."
    hi "Adeu. Et trobaré a faltar."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6072
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_8923d8ed:

    # "She pauses for a moment before walking up to me. Her right hand, outstretched in front of her, takes a hold of my shoulder."
    "S'atura un moment abans d'arribar a mi. Amb la mà dreta, estesa davant seu, m'agafa a l'espatlla."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6074
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_9780c566:

    # "Her left hand slowly and daintily reaches towards my face, taking my cheek in her palm."
    "M'acosta la mà esquerra a la cara a poc a poc i amb delicadesa, i m'agafa la galta amb el palmell."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6079
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_b6985118:

    # "For a while she simply holds my face, her fingers just slightly moving to take in its contours. Usually her hand would be warm when doing such a thing, but the night air's given her skin a cool edge."
    "Durant una estona es limita a agafar-me la cara, movent els dits lleugerament per prendre'n el contorn. Normalment, la seva mà estaria càlida fent una cosa així, però l'aire nocturn li ha donat certa fredor a la pell."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6081
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_fccef445:

    # "I'm not sure how long we stay like this, her clouded eyes pointed just below my own as she wears a wistful, almost distant smile. Eventually, though, I take her cold hand in mine."
    "No n'estic segur de quant de temps ens quedem així, amb els seus ulls ennuvolats apuntant just sota dels meus, mentre fa un somriure melancòlic, quasi distant. Finalment, li agafo la seva mà freda entre les meves."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6083
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_a6c4bcb5:

    # "It's difficult to do so, but with a slight sigh I gently remove her hand from my cheek."
    "M'és difícil fer-ho, però amb un petit sospir li trec suaument la mà de la galta."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6085
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_d9cccd3b:

    # hi "I hope you have a long and happy life, Lilly, no matter where you might go."
    hi "Espero que tinguis una vida llarga i feliç, Lilly, sense importar on estiguis."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6090
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_8203cabc:

    # li "Thank you. I'll make sure to."
    li "Gràcies. M'asseguraré de tenir-la."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6092
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_f5d06184:

    # "She takes a long, trembling breath before turning slightly towards Akira's direction."
    "Fa un sospir llarg i tremolós abans de girar-se lleugerament en direcció a l'Akira."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6097
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_3c81d0b5:

    # li "Akira…"
    li "Akira..."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6102
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_d1001687:

    # aki "Okay."
    aki "D'acord."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6109
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_047d844d:

    # "With a nod, she takes Lilly's hand and begins to guide her to the car parked outside the gates. They both walk slowly and deliberately, as if their movements had been rehearsed in advance."
    "Assenteix, agafa la mà de la Lilly i comença a guiar-la cap al cotxe aparcat fora de les portes. Totes dues caminen a poc a poc i amb consciència, com si haguessin assajat els moviments prèviament."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6111
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_c20f7329:

    # "It's strange to feel like this now, watching somebody leave Yamaku. The feeling of unease I have now reminds me of the first time I walked through those black wrought iron gates, that always looked far too pompous for what they were."
    "Se'm fa estrany sentir-me així ara, veient a algú sorti advance rnt del Yamaku. La sensació d'inquietud que tinc em recorda la primera vegada que vaig travessar aquelles portes negres de ferro forjat, que sempre em van semblar massa pretensioses pel que eren."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6113
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_d6841d06:

    # "As they leave, all of us know full well that our lives are irreversibly changing. I'd always told myself that I just have to take life as it comes, but everything's changing so fast, so suddenly."
    "Quan marxen, tots sabem molt bé que les nostres vides canviaran irreversiblement. Sempre m'havia dit que m'havia d'agafar la vida com vingués, però tot està canviant tan de pressa, tan de cop."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6115
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_ad311e02:

    # "In the end, Lilly's an irreplaceable part of the lives of both Hanako and me."
    "Al final, la Lilly és una part insubstituïble de les vides tant de la Hanako com la meva."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6117
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_19040f0b:

    # "The noise of Akira opening the passenger door for Lilly brings me out of my thoughts, her hand waving back as Lilly gets in."
    "El soroll de l'Akira obrint la porta del seient de copilot per la Lilly em treu dels meus pensaments, s'acomiada amb la mà mentre la Lilly entra."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6122
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_f0115e92:

    # aki "Seeya guys! Take care of yourselves!"
    aki "Ens veiem nois! Cuideu-vos tots dos!"

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6127
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_01df98bf:

    # li "Goodbye Hanako, goodbye Hisao!"
    li "Adeu, Hanako, adeu, Hisao!"

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6132
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_69e37314:

    # "Hanako's hand quickly shoots up, her face brightened by her enthusiastic farewell."
    "La Hanako aixeca la mà ràpidament, amb la cara il·luminada per aquest comiat tan efusiu."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6134
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_ca4712cc:

    # ha "Goodbye Lilly! Goodbye!"
    ha "Adeu, Lilly! Adeu!"

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6136
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_3a680758:

    # hi "See you, Akira, and goodbye Lilly!"
    hi "Fins aviat, Akira, i adeu, Lilly!"

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6142
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_57b79083:

    # "The door shuts as we all put on our best happy farewell faces, Akira getting in the car herself and starting it up in short measure."
    "Tanca la porta mentre tots posem les nostres millors cares per un comiat feliç, l'Akira puja al cotxe i no triga a arrancar."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6144
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_0aa76c0a:

    # "Lilly's hand can just be seen waving through the tinted windows, both of our hands waving high as well."
    "Podem veure la mà de la Lilly fent adeu a través dels vidres tintats, les nostres mans també li fan adeu ben alt."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6146
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_30918448:

    # "Just as every other time I've done such things, I can't quite work out precisely why I, or Hanako, wave to her given that she'd never see us doing so. But it doesn't matter."
    "Com totes les vegades que he fet alguna cosa així, no sé exactament per què jo, o la Hanako, li fem adeu, ja que ella no podrà veure-ho mai. Però no importa."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6148
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_69789983:

    # "Even after that black, shiny car goes down the hill and disappears into the dark night, we carry on waving and seeing Akira and Lilly off."
    "Fins i tot després que aquest cotxe negre i brillant baixi pel turó i desaparegui a la nit fosca, continuem fent adeu i mirant com l'Akira i la Lilly se'n van."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6152
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_a7f3aa78:

    # "And then… they're gone."
    "I ja... han marxat."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6158
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_6eb63240:

    # "A strange stillness takes over as our hands return to our sides."
    "Una estranya quietud s'apodera de nosaltres quan ens tornem a posar les mans als costats."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6160
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_dd7606c1:

    # "I don't quite know what I should do or how I should feel. In the end, we just stand there silently staring down at where the car disappeared from sight."
    "No sé ben bé què hauria de fer o com hauria de sentir-me. Al final, només ens quedem mirant en silenci cap a la direcció on ha desaparegut el cotxe de la nostra vista."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6162
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_6bacc818_1:

    # ha "Goodbye… Lilly."
    ha "Adeu... Lilly."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6167
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_dbfdfe49:

    # "All I can do in response to her quiet, mournful goodbye is to place a hand on her shoulder."
    "L'únic que puc fer en resposta al seu comiat silenciós i trist és posar-li la mà a l'espatlla."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6172
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_cb55230d:

    # "She looks at me for a few moments before looking back down the hill, secure in the knowledge that I'm still around for her."
    "Em mira uns instants abans de tornar a fixar la vista turó avall, ben segura que encara estic al seu costat."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6174
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_f3fbaa5a:

    # "What we'll do from now doesn't seem all that uncertain. We all have our own ambitions now, just as Lilly said."
    "Les coses que farem a partir d'ara no semblen tan incertes. Ara tots tenim les nostres pròpies ambicions, com ha dit Lilly."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6176
translate ca a4_lilly_farewell_70bd43a9:

    # "But even so, it feels like there's a certain missing part in both of our lives now. Something that can never be replaced."
    "Però tot i així, sento que ara ens faltarà una part de les nostres dues vides. Una cosa que no podrem substituir mai."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6195
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_c230e22c:

    # "The snap of my mobile phone's closing contrasts with the ambient chatter and noise audible even in the hallway outside the library."
    "El cop quan tanco el telèfon mòbil contrasta amb la xerrameca i el soroll audibles fins i tot al passadís fora de la biblioteca."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6197
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_bf9a40af:

    # "It's the first day of the summer holidays. A time that had perpetually seemed so far away, and yet it's now not only here but also made painfully obvious by the students, or lack thereof, left in the school."
    "És el primer dia de les vacances d'estiu. Un moment que sempre m'havia semblat molt llunyana i, no obstant això, no només ha arribat, sinó que es fa dolorosament òbvia pels estudiants que queden a l'escola, o pel fet que no n'hi hagin."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6199
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_42240c69:

    # "Most students have returned home to spend the holidays with relatives by now. The few that are left are mostly chatting between themselves, usually about what they intend to do in the coming weeks."
    "A hores d'ara, la majoria dels estudiants han tornat a casa per passar les vacances amb família. Els pocs que queden estan xerrant entre ells, normalment sobre el que faran les pròximes setmanes."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6201
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_364b5e21:

    # "It makes me feel like the odd one out, for taking advantage of the school library being open for the first several days of the holidays."
    "Em senti com un estrany per aprofitar que la biblioteca de l'escola està oberta durant els primers dies de vacances."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6203
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_f303d1f5:

    # "Ostensibly it's for students to drop off any books they've borrowed and have yet to return, and for those who'll have their parents pick them up, to help pass the time until they get whisked away."
    "Se suposa que és perquè els estudiants deixin els llibres que han agafat en préstec i encara no han tornat, i per aquells a qui els seus pares els venen a recollir, per ajudar-los a passar el temps fins que se'ls emportin."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6205
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_a4d8e6c2:

    # "Thanks to the recent lengthy phone call from my parents, which had so rudely woken me from my sleeping on a beanbag at the back of the library, I'm now in the latter category."
    "Gràcies a la llarga trucada amb els meus pares, que em va despertar bruscament del meu somni en un puf al fons de la biblioteca, ara ho estic fent."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6207
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_2268f38f:

    # "Sliding my phone back into my pocket, this time remembering to set it to silent, I go back into the quiet and wholly placid room."
    "Torno a posar-me el telèfon a la butxaca, aquesta vegada recordo posar-lo en silenci,  torno a la sala silenciosa i totalment plàcida."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6212
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_1ec16507:

    # "It's a nostalgic sight. Just as when Lilly first led me to the library, the orange tint of sunset bathes the room in its light while Hanako sits on a beanbag silently reading and Yuuko fusses, just barely visible behind the counter."
    "És una visió nostàlgica. Igual que quan la Lilly em va portar per primera vegada a la biblioteca, el to ataronjat de la posta de sol banya la sala amb la seva llum mentre la Hanako s'asseu en silenci en un puf i la Yuuko es queixa, amb prou feines visible darrere del taulell."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6214
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_a22c10e9:

    # "Hanako especially has been noticeably more quiet than usual since yesterday's happenings, but I can't really blame her."
    "He notat a la Hanako especialment més callada del que és habitual des del que va passar ahir, però no la culpo."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6216
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_e41e40d4:

    # "It wasn't just me that depended on that person, after all."
    "Al cap i a la fi, no només jo depenia d'aquesta persona."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6218
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_73a1044c:

    # "I quietly walk back to the beanbag near her where I'd sat before, being doubly careful not to make any unnecessary noise."
    "Torno tranquil·lament al puf prop seu, on m'havia assegut abans, amb molta cura de no fer cap soroll innecessari."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6226
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_fc506990:

    # "The soft puff it gives as the bag takes my weight makes Hanako's eyes flick towards me, but only for a second."
    "El soroll suau que fa quan el meu pes hi cau, fa que la Hanako desviï els ulls cap a mi, però només durant un segon."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6228
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_5ae069f6:

    # "I get the feeling that Hanako's been quiet only partly out of sadness following Lilly's departure."
    "Tinc la sensació que la Hanako ha estat callada només en part per la tristesa després de la marxa de la Lilly."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6230
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_3f5aa039:

    # "Rather, she seems more thoughtful and measured than I'd expected; perhaps due to her desire of working out how to deal with Lilly's leaving rather than just being depressed over it. It makes me a little proud of her."
    "Més aviat, sembla més reflexiva i seria del que m'esperava; potser és degut al seu desig de saber com afrontar que la marxa de la Lilly en lloc de deprimir-se. Em fa sentir una mica orgullós."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6232
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_8dd5cb23:

    # hi "Hey, Hanako?"
    hi "Ei, Hanako?"

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6237
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_8af76095:

    # ha "Y-yeah?"
    ha "S-sí?"

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6239
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_15f3fe9d:

    # hi "Still going ahead with your idea of traveling?"
    hi "Tiraràs endavant amb la idea de viatjar?"

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6241
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_040d40ca:

    # "She gives a determined nod."
    "Assenteix amb decisió."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6243
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_2d2f501a:

    # ha "I'll be starting in a day or two. Naomi's decided to come with me, too."
    ha "Començaré d'aquí a un dia o dos. La Naomi també ha decidit venir amb mi."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6245
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_8965ccce:

    # hi "Wow, quick start. Where're you two headed to first?"
    hi "Uau, començareu aviat. On anireu primer?"

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6247
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_e4dc2de0:

    # ha "I think we're going to start by going north… then loop down and go southward."
    ha "Crec que començarem anant al nord... i enllaçarem per baix i anirem cap al sud."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6249
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_d86b2ae0:

    # hi "So… Hokkaido's going to be first?"
    hi "Així... començareu per Hokkaido?"

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6251
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_ec5d998a:

    # "She gives another nod, more tentative than the last. The significance of that place is not lost on either of us."
    "Torna a assentir, més tímida que abans. A cap dels dos se'ns escapa la importància d'aquest lloc."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6253
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_3aac17eb:

    # hi "Do you know how you're going to handle the traveling expenses and accommodations?"
    hi "Ja saps com  t'ho faràs per gestionar les despeses de viatge i allotjament?"

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6255
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_5d51648c:

    # ha "Yeah, I've worked everything out. I think it should be okay. Naomi says she has her side worked out, too."
    ha "Sí, ja ho tinc tot pensat. Crec que tot anirà bé. La Naomi diu que ja té la seva part resolta també."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6257
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_0ffaf789:

    # hi "You know that if you need anything you can just call, right? I gave you my number before. Any time of the day is fine."
    hi "Ja saps que si necessites qualsevol cosa em pots trucar, oi? Ja et vaig donar el meu telèfon. Ho pots fer a qualsevol hora del dia."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6262
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_5d116a26:

    # "She gives a smile, which in itself feels like a small personal victory."
    "Somriu, i ho sento com una petita victòria personal."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6264
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_297ee17f:

    # ha "I know."
    ha "Ho sé."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6266
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_ade826ab:

    # ha "Th-thanks… Hisao."
    ha "Gr-gràcies... Hisao."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6268
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_bfc017a5:

    # "Maybe Lilly was right. Although I may offer Hanako any help I can possibly give, I feel as if I know she doesn't need it."
    "Potser en Lilly tenia raó. Encara que li pugui oferir a la Hanako tota la meva ajuda, sento com si sabés que ja no la necessita."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6270
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_a996223f:

    # "She really has grown."
    "Realment ha crescut."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6274
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_76b2fe88:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6277
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_0686fd77:

    # n "{vspace=90}Hanako's plans for her holidays are in sharp contrast to my simple following of my parents' suggestion to stay with them."
    n "{vspace=90}Els plans de la Hanako per a les seves vacances contrasten amb els meus, que simplement segueixo el suggeriment dels pares de quedar-me amb ells."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6279
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_a462eee3:

    # n "Holidays had always made me feel less excited than most, though, so maybe this is just a return to the status quo."
    n "Però les vacances sempre m'havien fet menys il·lusió que la majoria, així que potser aquest és només un retorn a l'statu quo."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6281
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_68647169:

    # n "{vspace=30}Before my heart attack, I'd always lived so aimlessly that holidays weren't all that much different from my everyday life anyway."
    n "{vspace=30}Abans del meu atac de cor, sempre havia viscut tan esmaperdut que les vacances no eren gaire diferents de la meva vida quotidiana."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6283
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_e541360b:

    # n "After school I'd wander around a bit in the city, often hanging out with some friends, before making my way home to eat dinner with usually one of my parents, but rarely both."
    n "Després de l'escola, deambulava una mica per la ciutat, sovint sortia amb alguns amics, abans de tornar a casa per sopar amb, normalment, un dels meus pares, però rarament tots dos."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6285
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_946ed15d:

    # n "Their work schedules didn't leave much time for them to be home, and going there straight from school would just have meant I'd end up feeling bored. I was an urbanite through and through."
    n "Els seus horaris de feina no els deixaven gaire temps per ser a casa, i si anava a casa directament després de l'escola m'hi acabava avorrint. Era un urbanita de cap a peus."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6287
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_396ba483:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

    old "[_n_] {vspace=90}Since coming to Yamaku though, it feels like I've fundamentally changed as a person. The phone call with my parents erased any traces of doubt I might have held on that, in any case."
    new "[_n_] {vspace=90}Tot i això, d'ençà que vaig arribar al Yamaku, tinc la sensació d'haver canviat radicalment com a persona. En qualsevol cas, la trucada amb els pares m'ha esborrat els pocs dubtes que tenia al respecte."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6291
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_1bb18757:

    # n "While before I had exercised a fairly normal level of independence for a teenager, that being not a whole lot, my parents were more than pleased to hear of my newfound ability in taking care of myself."
    n "Mentre que abans tenia un nivell d'independència bastant normal per a un adolescent, que tampoc era gaire, els pares estaven més que satisfets de sentir parlar de la meva nova capacitat de tenir cura de mi mateix."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6293
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_34a8e981:

    # n "Laundry, cooking for myself, cleaning, all in addition to other general chores that come from living without parents around… just little menial things I've had to pick up, but with relative ease."
    n "Fer la bugada, preparar-me el menjar, netejar, a més d'altres tasques que has de fer quan vius sense pares a prop... petites coses de poca importància que he hagut de fer, però amb relativa facilitat."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6295
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_24ff359c:

    # n "{vspace=30}When I think about it, I'd always depended on them, even if they hadn't been at home all the time. To say I never depended on anyone after moving to the Yamaku dormitories would be far from the truth, though."
    n "{vspace=30}Quan hi penso, sempre n'he depès d'ells, encara que no fossin sempre a casa. Tot i això, dir que mai havia depès de ningú després de traslladar-me als dormitoris del Yamaku no seria veritat."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6299
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_76b2fe88_1:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6302
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_bc3775af:

    # yu "Um… excuse me…"
    yu "Um... perdona..."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6310
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_9f61e688:

    # "The two of us look up at the awkwardly fidgeting figure in front of us. Some things never change."
    "Els dos mirem la maldestra figura que tenim al davant. Hi ha coses que mai canvien."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6315
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_b0c07444:

    # yu "It's getting close to closing time, so um…"
    yu "S'acosta l'hora de tancar, així que um..."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6317
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_7fec998d:

    # "Oh, right. I'd forgotten that the library closes earlier during the holidays."
    "És veritat. M'havia oblidat que la biblioteca tanca abans durant les vacances."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6319
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_2f930d15:

    # "Hanako and I both get up and dust ourselves off, placing our books back on the shelf behind us. The fact that our tastes in reading material have a fair amount of overlap is useful at times."
    "La Hanako i jo ens aixequem, ens espolsem, i posem els llibres de nou a la prestatgeria de darrere. El fet que els nostres gustos sobre lectura coincideixin, és força útil de vegades."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6321
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_b643ba71:

    # "With a bow to Yuuko to apologize for taking so much time, Hanako takes her leave of us."
    "La Hanako fa un gest a la Yuuko per disculpar-se per trigar tant de temps, i se'n va."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6330
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_c64c5648:

    # ha "See you tomorrow, Hisao."
    ha "Fins demà, Hisao."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6332
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_361fdc97:

    # hi "Bye."
    hi "Adeu."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6337
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_02a5ba22:

    # "And with that, she walks out of the large, wooden, aging doors that herald the entrance to the library."
    "I tot seguit, surt per les grans portes de fusta envellida que anuncien l'entrada a la biblioteca."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6345
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_ead28dda:

    # yu "She's a quiet person, isn't she?"
    yu "No parla gaire, oi?"

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6347
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_5d478777:

    # "I suppose I should be surprised at a staff member sharing personal opinions like this, but after knowing Yuuko for a while it's largely expected. Our relationship is more personal, rather than one with her acting as an authority figure."
    "Suposo que m'hauria de sorprendre que un membre del personal comparteixi opinions personals com aquesta, però després de conèixer la Yuuko durant un temps, era d'esperar. La nostra relació és més personal que d'autoritat."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6349
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_c21c1acf:

    # hi "Yeah, I think that's just how she is."
    hi "Sí, crec que és així."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6351
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_a641a8a5:

    # hi "She's got a lot more confidence in herself these days, though."
    hi "Però últimament té més confiança en si mateixa."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6356
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_06131093:

    # yu "I don't know her as well as you do, but I think I agree. It's nice to see her talking to people here; she never used to do that before."
    yu "No la conec tant com tu, però hi estic d'acord. M'agrada veure-la aquí parlant amb gent; no acostumava a fer-ho mai."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6358
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_a0c35a68:

    # hi "Hey, Yuuko… you know about Lilly's leaving, right?"
    hi "Ei, Yuuko... t'has assabentat que la Lilly marxa, oi?"

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6363
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_99e7f5ee:

    # yu "She told me herself a few days ago. It must be hard, leaving everyone behind like she is."
    yu "M'ho va dir ella mateixa fa uns dies. Ha de ser dur fer com ella i deixar a tothom enrere."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6365
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_2de151c9:

    # "She quickly looks back to me after she says this, probably remembering that I went to her for advice on the relationship between Lilly and me before."
    "Després de dir això, em torna a mirar, probablement recordant que abans vaig anar a demanar-li consell sobre la relació entre la Lilly i jo."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6370
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_c07bcaeb:

    # yu "Are you going to be okay?"
    yu "Estaràs bé?"

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6372
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_2eb33a74:

    # "That's… a difficult question. It's something I'd rather not think about for now, though, given more pressing issues."
    "És... una pregunta difícil. Però és una cosa en la qual preferiria no pensar de moment, ja que tinc problemes més urgents."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6374
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_ff563af7:

    # hi "Something seems kind of off about this whole deal, don't you think?"
    hi "Hi ha alguna cosa que sembla que no està bé de tot això, no creus?"

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6376
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_f7fab151:

    # "Yuuko appears to think for a while, absentmindedly scrunching her face up in a variety of creative ways as she does so."
    "La Yuuko sembla pensar durant una estona i distretament, mentre ho fa, va fent diverses ganyotes de maneres creatives."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6381
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_e00e7b50:

    # yu "I don't think I really know her well enough to make that kind of judgment."
    yu "No crec que la conegui prou per poder fer aquesta mena de judici."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6383
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_470fe4d4:

    # yu "I'm sorry I can't be more help."
    yu "Em sap greu, m'agradaria poder-te ajudar."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6385
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_94da5892:

    # hi "Nah, that's fine. I'm just sort of thinking aloud."
    hi "Bah, no passa res. Només pensava en veu alta."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6387
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_353629b3:

    # "I give a deep sigh and scratch my head in frustration."
    "Sospiro profundament i em grato el cap en frustració."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6389
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_592ba264:

    # hi "There's just so much stuff happening at once that I have no control over… it feels like I'm being swamped."
    hi "Estan passant tantes coses a la vegada que no puc controlar... em sento desbordat."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6394
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_a02466f6:

    # yu "I think everyone goes through times like that."
    yu "Crec que tothom passa per èpoques així."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6396
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_e1938c88:

    # yu "What's important is to concentrate on what you can do, rather than what you can't do. At least, that's how I see it."
    yu "El que realment importa és concentrar-se en allò que sí que pots fer, no pas en allò que no pots. Com a mínim jo ho veig així."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6401
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_ae244c9c:

    # yu "If I didn't think like that, I don't think I'd be able to manage my life as it is."
    yu "Si no pensés així, crec que no podria ser capaç de fer la vida que tinc tal com és. "

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6403
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_f5959cf3:

    # "She says it with a smile and a light tone, but her words are far from any kind of joke. Being pulled between two jobs as she is, just to hopefully make enough money not only to live, but also for university, must be exhausting."
    "Ho diu amb un somriure i un to suau, però les seves paraules estan lluny de fer broma. Ha de ser esgotador tenir dues feines com ella, amb l'esperança de guanyar prou diners no només per viure, sinó també per pagar-se la universitat."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6405
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_d6bee763:

    # "Perhaps that's why, coming from her, this feels like it has more meaning than if it had come from most others."
    "Potser per això, venint d'ella, sembla que tingui més pes que si vingués d'alguna altra persona."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6407
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_c748970c:

    # hi "I guess you've got a point there."
    hi "Suposo que tens raó."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6409
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_fedcdbbb:

    # hi "Thank you for your advice once again, Yuuko."
    hi "Gràcies una altra vegada pel teu consell, Yuuko."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6422
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_b0e1783e:

    # "She bows deeply and smiles again, before making her way back to the counter where she spends so much of her time."
    "Fa una gran reverència i torna a somriure, abans de tornar darrere el taulell on es passa gran part del seu temps."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6429
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_8e53c0d9:

    # "The tiny wings of the cardboard crane in my fingers are only just visible in the dim light of my room, just a little of the moonlight being able to peek through the curtains and around their edges."
    "Les petites ales de la grua que tinc a les mans en prou feines són visibles a la penombra de l'habitació, només il·luminada per la llum de la lluna que s'entreveu a través de les cortines i ell voltant de les vores."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6441
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_b0dc09b0:

    # "I lie still in my dark bed for a long time, idly looking up at the little origami bird."
    "Em quedo estirat en el llit fosc durant una bona estona, mirant distretament el petit ocell d'origami."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6443
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_652c0d0b:

    # "It feels like a lot's happened since Lilly folded this, but at the same time it feels like very little has changed."
    "Sembla que han passat moltes coses des que la Lilly me'l va fer, però a la vegada sembla que molt poques coses hagin canviat."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6445
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_669beec2:

    # "Compared to everyone else, I'm back to square one. I might have a newfound idea of where I want to go in life, but that's hardly something that affects me now."
    "En comparació amb els altres, jo torno a ser al principi. Pot ser que tingui una idea nova d'on vull anar a la vida, però no és una cosa que m'afecta ara mateix."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6447
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_a4f09222:

    # "Hanako changed, I know that much. If anything, she just makes me feel like I've got no excuse to be like this, considering her previous situation."
    "La Hanako ha canviat, ho sé prou bé. En tot cas, em fa sentir que no tinc excusa per estar així, tenint en compte la seva anterior situació."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6449
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_bb80582e:

    # "Lilly, though…"
    "La Lilly, però..."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6451
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_3df5a7ad:

    # "I turn the bird in my fingers another way, looking at it from yet another angle."
    "Giro l'ocell que tinc entre els dits cap a una altra direcció, i el miro des d'un altre angle."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6455
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_76b2fe88_2:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6458
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_38281dd1:

    # n "{vspace=60}When I first met her, she seemed aloof and perhaps somewhat distant. Her actions were always careful, measured and precise, and her carefully maintained composure always gave the appearance of unerring confidence and serenity."
    n "{vspace=60}Quan la vaig conèixer, semblava que es mantenia al marge i potser una mica distant. Les seves accions sempre eren prudents, mesurades i precises, i la seva compostura, que mantenia amb cura,  sempre donava l'aparença d'una confiança i serenitat infal·libles."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6460
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_665d74fe:

    # n "In time, she became less formal. Just a bit, but enough. It felt good to see her lowering her inhibitions around me, and opening up, even just a little, of her own accord; it felt as if I was seeing her real self slowly become more vibrant and visible."
    n "Amb el temps, es va tornar menys formal. Només va ser una mica, però n'hi havia prou. M'agradava veure com es desinhibia i s'obria amb mi, encara que només fos una mica, per si sola; semblava que veiés com el seu veritable jo s'anava tornant, a poc a poc, més vibrant i visible."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6462
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_c1190410:

    # n "{vspace=30}Now, though, I'm beginning to have doubts."
    n "{vspace=30}Ara, però, començo a tenir dubtes."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6464
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_d96ebc33:

    # n "{vspace=30}Perhaps they're to be expected after what is, effectively, the two of us breaking up. They don't feel new or strange though, but rather like an old book being found and dusted off."
    n "{vspace=30}Potser és d'esperar després que, efectivament, talléssim. Però no em semblen nous o estranys, sinó com aviat com un vell llibre que es troba i se li treu la pols."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6466
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_2382be9e:

    # n "I soon realized after meeting Lilly that she saw me as she did Hanako; as someone who needed help and care. At first, I simply thought that we'd be fine as friends, helping each other through our limited time together in school."
    n "Després de conèixer a la Lilly, de seguida em vaig adonar que em veia com veia a la Hanako: com algú que necessitava ajuda i atenció. Al principi, simplement pensava que estaríem bé com a amics, ajudant-nos mútuament durant el nostre temps limitat junts a l'escola."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6468
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_00a18f1c:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

    old "[_n_] {vspace=60}But then I began to treasure our moments together more and more, from our quiet walks to our talking over lunch. The good sides of her personality became ever more obvious, and ever more likable."
    new "[_n_] {vspace=60}Però llavors vaig començar a apreciar cada cop més els moments plegats, des dels passejos tranquils fins a les nostres converses durant el dinar. La part bona de la seva personalitat es va fer cada cop més evident i agradable."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6472
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_a9f9b84c:

    # n "The absence caused by Lilly's trip to Scotland to visit her long-distant family and sick aunt only made me realize how much I liked just being around her, and I had thought that she felt a similar way."
    n "El fet que la Lilly marxés de viatge a Escòcia per visitar la seva família llunyana i la seva tia malalta, em va fer més evident com m'agradava estar al seu voltant, i vaig pensar que se sentiria d'una manera similar."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6474
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_dc12c94e:

    # n "{vspace=30}For her, though, maybe that wasn't everything to our relationship."
    n "{vspace=30}Però per a ella, potser això no ho era tot per a ella en la nostra relació."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6476
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_7647b861:

    # n "{vspace=30}Even after she returned to Japan, that just meant she lost her family once again after meeting them for such a brief time."
    n "{vspace=30}Fins i tot després de tornar al Japó, això només volia dir que tornava a perdre a la seva família més després d'haver-la conegut durant tan poc temps."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6478
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_da84624e:

    # n "She lived so much of her life without her family around, not to mention with Akira working long hours, that she had little choice but to be like that."
    n "Va viure tant de temps sense la seva família, per no parlar de les llargues jornades de feina de l'Akira, que no va tenir més remei que ser així."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6480
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_e32e3836:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

    old "[_n_] {vspace=60}I had thought her sense of independence to be a good and admirable trait. It was in stark difference to my reliance on my parents before my heart attack, as reluctant as I may have been to admit it."
    new "[_n_] {vspace=60}Pensava que el seu sentit de la independència era una qualitat bona i admirable. Era molt diferent de la meva dependència cap als meus pares abans de l'infart, per molt que em resistís a admetre-ho."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6484
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_bea2caa6:

    # n "However, it also meant that she never let people get too close to her."
    n "No obstant això, també significava que mai deixava que la gent se li acostés massa."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6486
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_a7d8f9e1:

    # n "She lost her family likely due to her blindness, went to a different school from anybody she knew because of it, and worked all the harder to make sure she didn't end up a burden on her sister and those around her."
    n "Segurament, va perdre a la seva família a causa de la seva ceguesa, això va fer que anés a una escola diferent de la dels seus coneguts, i es va esforçar al màxim per assegurar-se no acabar essent una càrrega per a la seva germana ni pels que l'envoltaven."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6488
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_ed437ec1:

    # n "{vspace=30}And now, Akira's going to Inverness, just like the family she thought she'd lost."
    n "{vspace=30}I ara, l'Akira anirà a l'Inverness, igual que la família que pensava que havia perdut."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6490
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_2fe0bd58:

    # n "She never told me of her plans, as conflicted as she was about them."
    n "Mai em va parlar dels seus plans, encara que li suposessin un dilema."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6492
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_f342a50c:

    # n "Lilly didn't want to be a burden on anyone, including me."
    n "La Lilly no volia ser una càrrega per a ningú, tampoc per mi."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6494
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_b39823f4:

    # n "{vspace=60}…I'm an idiot."
    n "{vspace=60}...Soc idiota."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6496
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_830c8bdf:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

    old "[_n_] {vspace=60}I never questioned it. I never tried to be there or asked when she needed me to."
    new "[_n_] {vspace=60}Mai ho vaig qüestionar. Mai vaig intentar ser-hi ni vaig preguntar-li quan més em necessitava."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6500
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_1f889ce0:

    # n "I just set my life up and expected it to stay that way forever, with the two of us having a nice long relationship where we pushed forwards towards our future together."
    n "Em vaig limitar a organitzar la meva vida i a esperar que fos així per sempre, els dos amb una relació bonica i llarga mentre avançàvem junts cap al nostre futur."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6502
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_befacc05:

    # n "{vspace=30}A small pit of frustration and anger at myself wells up in my chest."
    n "{vspace=30}Se'm fa un pou de ràbia i frustració contra mi mateix al pit."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6504
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_4fd87cd7:

    # n "{vspace=30}I just let everything happen, never even trying to help Lilly."
    n "{vspace=30}Vaig deixar que passés tot, sense intentar ajudar a la Lilly."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6506
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_2dc6b68f:

    # n "{vspace=30}Just her being there was enough. I thought I could keep going on if that were true."
    n "{vspace=30}En tenia prou que estigués amb mi. Pensava que podria seguir endavant si era així."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6508
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_69894263:

    # n "But that could never have been enough. It was a childlike dependence on somebody, without any attempt to understand or help their situation."
    n "Però això mai hauria estat suficient. Era una dependència infantil, sense intentar entendre-la ni ajudar-la en la seva situació."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6510
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_da43819c:

    # n "Thanks to that, I lost Lilly. I lost the one person I loved most because I wasn't there for her when she needed me."
    n "Gràcies a això, vaig perdre la Lilly. Vaig perdre la persona que més estimava perquè no hi vaig ser quan em necessitava."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6514
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_76b2fe88_3:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6525
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_1c9efa45:

    # "With an increasingly angry feeling washing over me, I turn over and set the crane back on the desk next to my clock, the place where it has lived since that day when she folded it for me."
    "M'envaeix un sentiment de ràbia cada vegada més fort, em giro i torno a deixar la grua a l'escriptori, al costat del rellotge, el lloc on ha viscut des d'aquell dia que la va fer per a mi."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6527
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_de5b6e29:

    # "Since that day when she herself said that my burdens needn't be my own."
    "Des d'aquell dia que ella mateixa em va dir que les meves càrregues no havien de ser només meves."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6529
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_727f61d6:

    # "The obnoxious bright red numerals of my alarm clock shine through the darkness of the room onto my tired eyes."
    "Els maleïts números vermells del meu despertador brillen en la foscor de l'habitació sobre els meus ulls cansats."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6531
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_4f028d73:

    # "Ten o'clock. Evening. Curfew will be soon."
    "Les deu en punt. Del vespre. Falta poc per l'hora del toc de queda."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6533
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_a57dbe1b:

    # hi "I wonder…"
    hi "Em pregunto..."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6535
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_2eb0cccd:

    # "Akira mentioned they'd be leaving this evening."
    "L'Akira ha dit que marxarien aquesta nit."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6537
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_acef77db:

    # "I've no idea exactly when their flight is… but that means there's a chance, however small, that they might not have already left."
    "No sé pas a quina hora és el seu vol... però això significa que hi ha la possibilitat, per petita que sigui, que encara no hagin marxat."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6539
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_16a9e1d9:

    # "Adrenaline starts to move through my body as I sit up on my bed, my eyes suddenly wide with possibility."
    "L'adrenalina se'm comença a moure pel cos mentre m'assec al llit, amb els ulls de sobte oberts a aquesta possibilitat."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6541
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_86465906:

    # "There's no guarantee they haven't left, indeed it's likely that they already have, but there's also a chance they haven't, however small it may be."
    "No hi ha cap garantia que no hagin marxat, de fet és probable que ja no hi siguin, però també hi ha la possibilitat que sí, per petita que sigui."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6543
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_8842d0a5:

    # "Just this once, just as I should have before…"
    "Només aquesta vegada, com hauria d'haver fet abans..."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6553
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_038be93d:

    # "I stand up and rush over to my cabinet, throwing out some clothes as fast as I can and sliding them on in quick succession."
    "M'aixeco i em llanço contra la calaixera, trec unes peces de roba tan ràpid com puc i me les poso amb rapidesa una després de l'altra."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6555
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_281779a4:

    # "Each second that goes by is a second that I can't regain, a second that may mean the difference between catching them and losing them forever."
    "Cada segon que passa és un segon que no puc recuperar, un segon que pot significar la diferència entre atrapar-les o perdre-les per sempre."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6557
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_a59cb53b:

    # "Even if I fail, I have to try. I can't let her leave everything behind without even trying to stop her. Without, just this once, being there for her."
    "Encara que falli, ho he d'intentar. No puc permetre que ho deixi tot enrere sense ni tan sols intentar aturar-la. Sense, per una vegada, ser-hi per a ella."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6559
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_bed2fbd5:

    # "With the last of my clothes slipped on, I hastily grab the phone off the desk. Luckily, the number for a local taxi company is still in my call history."
    "Em poso l'última peça de roba i agafo amb pressa el telèfon de l'escriptori. Per sort, encara tinc el número d'una companyia de taxis local a l'historial de trucades."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6569
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_73f94ba6:

    # "A gruff, unenthusiastic voice announces the name of the company while I pace around the room. It takes some effort to slow down my voice and keep it clear over the phone."
    "Una veu desagradable i sense entusiasme anuncia el nom de l'empresa mentre deambulo per l'habitació. Necessito fer un esforç per afluixar la veu i mantenir-la clara per telèfon."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6574
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_2d13187c:

    # "The chilly night air sweeps against me as I open the dormitory door, but nevertheless I keep up my brisk speed as I half-jog, half-run out to the school gates."
    "L'aire fred de la nit se m'endú quan obro la porta del dormitori, però, sigui com sigui, mantinc la velocitat mentre mig troto, mig corro cap a la porta de l'escola."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6576
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_2f4707f1:

    # "It may not be curfew just yet, but it's precariously close. If there were a guard around they'd no doubt have some questions for me, but it looks like I've managed to come out just before they arrive, or they're around a corner."
    "Encara no és l'hora del toc de queda, però està perillosament a prop. Si hi hagués un guàrdia al voltant, sense cap mena de dubte em farien algunes preguntes, però sembla que he aconseguit sortir just abans que arribin, o estan a la cantonada."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6581
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_2767990e:

    # "My pace picks up as I make my way through the school gardens, their night-time allure all but lost when I begin to run to the school gate."
    "Accelero el ritme a mesura que travesso els jardins de l'escola, que tenen un encís nocturn que quasi es perd quan començo a córrer cap a la porta."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6586
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_ac3c1260:

    # "The lamps of the courtyard, dim as they are, provide just enough illumination to light the way and prevent me from tripping over. The buildings themselves take on a rustic, almost antique-looking edge when I glance at them."
    "Les llums del pati, fosques com són, il·luminen prou per  veure el camí i evitar que m'entrebanqui. Els edificis adquireixen un aspecte rústic, gairebé antic, quan els observo."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6588
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_f315c250:

    # "Looking back, it seems strange that they once appeared so dark and looming to me. Now they just look to be somewhat anachronistic school buildings, the same as any others bar their age."
    "Evocant el passat, em sembla estrany que alguna vegada em semblessin tan foscos i tan amenaçadors. Ara només semblen edificis escolars una mica anacrònics, com que qualssevol altres de la seva època."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6593
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_e9c0f859:

    # "Leaving the gates behind me, I pull up to a stop just before the taxi. Parked just as Akira's car had been, its gaudy and brightly lit sign looks out of place in the quiet country backdrop."
    "Deixo les portes enrere i m'aturo just davant de la parada de taxis. N'hi ha un aparcat just com ho havia estat el cotxe de l'Akira, el seu rètol il·luminat ben llampant i brillant sembla fora de lloc en el tranquil paisatge rural."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6595
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_3a1267e7:

    # "I impatiently squeeze myself through the door, giving the driver the address for where the two should hopefully be staying."
    "M'esquitllo per la porta i li dono al conductor l'adreça de lloc on, amb una mica de sort, deuen passar la nit les dues."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6600
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_58f2b2be:

    # "By the time the taxi pulls up after its trip at maddeningly casual speed, it's well and truly deep into the night."
    "Quan el taxi s'atura després de fer el viatge a una velocitat desesperadament casual, ja és ben entrada la nit."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6602
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_37bf3143:

    # "The house is truly enormous, its sheer size much larger than I'd expected, and ominously still. Fearing the worst, I ask the driver to stay just in case my efforts are for naught."
    "La casa és realment enorme, molt més gran del que esperava, i amenaçadorament impassible. Tot tement el pitjor, demano al conductor que es quedi només per si de cas els meus esforços són en va."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6604
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_e944db00:

    # "A single press on the fancy intercom system outside the gate produces a short electronic melody in the otherwise silent road. It's not long before a somewhat deep, gruff voice can be heard from it."
    "Premo una vegada l'elegant sistema d'intèrfon situat fora de la porta que produeix una curta melodia electrònica en la carretera, fora d'això silenciosa. No triga a sentir-se una veu una mica greu i ronca."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6606
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_be123210:

    # mystery "This is the Hakamichi residence. Please state your name and why you're bothering us this late."
    mystery "Aquesta és la residència Hakamichi. Si us plau, digui el seu nom i per què ens molesta a aquestes hores."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6608
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_90588098:

    # "I press on despite inwardly wincing at the reasonable annoyance audible in his voice."
    "Continuo endavant malgrat la ganyota de disgust que puc percebre de la seva veu."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6610
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_cbbaed55:

    # hi "It's Hisao Nakai. I was hoping to meet Lilly or Akira, if they're still here."
    hi "Soc en Hisao Nakai. Esperava poder parlar amb la Lilly o l'Akira, si encara són aquí."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6612
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_846a09e2:

    # "Surprisingly, I manage to summon quite some energy to my voice, enough to make the other side of the intercom silent."
    "Sorprenentment, aconsegueixo infondre energia a la meva veu, suficient per fer callar l'altra banda de l'intèrfon."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6617
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_61ac5710:

    # "A few seconds pass, but just before I press the button again and ask what's going on, a light turns on outside the front door."
    "Passen uns segons, però just abans que torni a prémer el botó i preguntar què està passant, s'encén la llum de fora de la porta principal."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6619
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_ab7e43c5:

    # "I strain my eyes to try and make out who is coming through, but as he comes past a large parked car with fishing rods sticking out the back, his identity becomes clear."
    "Forço la vista per intentar esbrinar qui ve, però quan passa per davant d'un gran cotxe aparcat amb canyes de pescar que surten per darrere, la seva identitat se'm fa evident."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6621
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_327f639b:

    # "His face is typically placid and emotionless as he saunters up to the gate. He's still childlike in his mannerisms, despite his demeanor. With the press of a few buttons from behind the fence, the gate slowly opens."
    "Veig que té una cara serena i freda quan s'acosta a la porta. Malgrat el seu comportament, encara continua sent un nen. Prem uns botons des de darrere de la tanca, i la porta s'obre lentament."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6626
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_0fb78a13:

    # hh "Hisao? What are you doing here?"
    hh "Hisao? Què hi fas aquí?"

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6628
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_5a07f050:

    # "I think this is the most emotion I've ever heard from his voice, not that it would be hard to reach that mark."
    "Crec que és la frase amb més emoció que li he sentit dir mai, i no és gaire difícil arribar a aquesta xifra."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6630
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_9520de16:

    # hi "Akira told me that she and Lilly would be staying here before they left for their flight."
    hi "L'Akira em va dir que ella i la Lilly s'estarien aquí abans d'agafar el seu vol."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6632
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_4a42b9c4:

    # hi "I need to talk to Lilly, just one last time. Are they still here?"
    hi "He de parlar amb la Lilly, una última vegada. Encara són aquí?"

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6637
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_eea43587:

    # "The look on his face says everything."
    "La mirada que fa ho diu tot."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6639
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_f996ddbf:

    # "I failed. I was too late. The one time when I actually needed to act quickly, and…"
    "He fracassat. He arribat massa tard. L'única vegada que realment necessitava actuar amb rapidesa, i..."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6644
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_8b668806:

    # hh "Actually… it's possible…"
    hh "De fet... és possible..."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6646
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_fd0429d9:

    # hi "What? What is it?"
    hi "Què? Què és possible?"

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6651
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_a0a7133f:

    # "He's a bit taken aback by my fervor, but I can't help it at this point."
    "El sorprèn una mica el meu fervor, però a aquestes altures ja no puc evitar-ho."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6656
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_7897afdf:

    # hh "They left not long ago; only a few minutes before you arrived, in fact. If you go straight to the airport, you might be able to… Hisao!?"
    hh "No fa gaire que han marxat: només uns minuts abans que arribessis, de fet. Si vas directe a l'aeroport potser pots... Hisao!?"

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6658
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_4db42ee8:

    # "I dart back towards the waiting taxi, grabbing what little money is left in my pocket as I go."
    "Torno corrent al taxi que m'espera, agafant els pocs diners que em queden a la butxaca."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6660
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_766e170c:

    # hi "Thanks, Hideaki!"
    hi "Gràcies, Hideaki!"

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6662
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_0f6858a5:

    # "With that I take a seat, and in short order bark out my destination."
    "Dit això, m'assec i de seguida crido el meu destí."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6670
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_bea83b36:

    # "My chest beats wildly as I tear down the street, my body twisting this way and that to slip between the pedestrians walking back and forth beside me."
    "El meu pit batega desbocat mentre avanço pel carrer, moc el cos d'un costat a l'altre per lliscar entre els vianants que caminen al meu voltant."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6672
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_a2cf25ed:

    # "With the road solidly blocked by taxis and other cars, dropping off passengers and picking up others in the time they have to wait, we ended up having to stop almost a block away."
    "La carretera totalment bloquejada per taxis i altres cotxes, que deixen passatgers i en recullen d'altres en el temps d'espera, així que acabem parant gairebé un carrer més enllà."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6674
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_84f1d378:

    # "But that's in the past now. What matters is reaching Lilly."
    "Però això ja és cosa del passat. Ara només m'importa arribar fins a la Lilly."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6676
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_fdf91a2d:

    # "One foot hits the ground, the other quickly following without the slightest thought, as if my legs have taken on a life of their own and all my mind can do is concentrate on the view ahead of me."
    "Toco amb un peu a terra, i l'altre el segueix de seguida sense pensar-s'ho dues vegades, com si les meves cames tinguessin vida pròpia i l'únic que la meva ment pot fer és concentrar-se en la vista que tinc davant."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6678
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_6e32a68d:

    # "Just one glimpse of that long hair of hers. That long, yellow hair that was the same color as the wheat that stretched as far as the eye could see."
    "Només vull veure aquella llarga cabellera. Aquells cabells llargs i grocs del mateix color que el blat que s'estenia fins on arribava la vista."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6680
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_fa2be615:

    # "In the end, I depended on Lilly, just like Hanako did. Even after we started going out, it still doesn't feel like she really ever let herself depend on me."
    "Al final, depenia de la Lilly, igual que la Hanako. Fins i tot després que comencéssim a sortir, sento que realment no es va permetre dependre de mi."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6682
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_609f07a6:

    # "Except for one moment. That one moment where we held each other tightly on that bright yellow field."
    "Excepte una vegada. Aquell moment en què ens vam abraçar amb força en aquell camp d'un groc brillant."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6684
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_a878ddca:

    # "At that time she must have feared losing me just as she did everyone else. That's why, just this once…"
    "En aquell moment devia témer perdre'm, igual que havia perdut a tothom. Per això, només aquesta vegada..."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6686
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_59d30a79:

    # "The night air wraps around me, draining every last remnant of warmth out of my body, to the extent that it feels more like midwinter than a summer night."
    "L'aire nocturn m'envolta, i absorbeix fins a l'últim rastre de calor del meu cos, fins al punt que em sembla més ple hivern que no pas una nit d'estiu."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6688
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_292c4f6f:

    # "My fingers, my hands, my feet… they all feel increasingly cold."
    "Els dits, les mans, els peus... tots estan cada vegada més freds."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6690
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_315e78d9:

    # "The sound of the passing crowds is reduced to no more than a background hum while the sound of my shoes hitting the pavement echoes loudly, every step surging towards the person I have to catch."
    "El so de les multituds que passen es redueix a un murmuri de fons, mentre que el so de les meves sabates colpejant el paviment ressona fort, cada pas que avanço cap a la persona que he d'atrapar."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6692
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_04e3d0eb:

    # "Forced by my chest tightening in response to the cold of the night, I rest an arm over it to try and settle it down."
    "Sento una pressió al pit en resposta al fred de la nit, que em força a reposar-hi un braç per intentar apaivagar-lo."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6705
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_687e7c5a:

    # "When the airport comes into view, though, I realize this feeling as one I've felt before."
    "Quan veig l'aeroport, però, m'adono que aquesta sensació ja l'he sentit abans."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6707
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_824a85b8:

    # "Not now… of all the times for this, please not now."
    "Ara no... de tots els moments que hi havia, si us plau, ara no."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6709
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_12e629cf:

    # "I take a gulp and soldier on regardless, pushing my body as far as it will go."
    "Empasso saliva i continuo endavant, empenyent el cos fins al límit."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6711
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_7368db56:

    # "Sweat pours off me as I hurtle forward, my shoulder hitting someone's side and my mind suddenly flooding with emotions and memories."
    "Noto la suor mentre em precipito cap endavant, amb l'espatlla colpejo el costat d'algú i la ment se m'inunda d'emocions i records."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6713
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_41ccefa5:

    # "I continue on without an apology. I have to keep moving now. If I stop, I'm not sure I could begin again, and even if I could it would all be for naught if I'm not in time."
    "Continuo sense disculpar-me. He de seguir avançant. Si m'aturo, no estic segur que pugui tornar a començar, i encara que pogués, tot seria en va si no hi arribo a temps."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6717
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_775b1f43:

    # "I hit another person, then another, offering little resistance to getting bounced about."
    "Colpejo a una altra persona, després a una altra, i ofereixo poca resistència al fet que em rebotin."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6719
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_362a0cbe:

    # "My feet feel numb. My arms are losing all feeling. My chest forces me to hunch over awkwardly, tightening ever more."
    "Noto que se m'han entumit els peus. I els braços han perdut tota sensibilitat. El pit m'obliga a encorbar-me feixugament, m'apreta cada vegada més."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6728
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_67322b7e:

    # "That afternoon in the snow… that time when my life irreversibly changed… images of Iwanako and that damned letter flash over and over in my mind, the first love I'd lost thanks to my condition."
    "Aquella tarda a la neu... aquell moment en què la meva vida va canviar irreversiblement... les imatges de la Iwanako i aquella maleïda carta em passen una vegada i una altra pel cap, el primer amor que vaig perdre gràcies a la meva malaltia."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6730
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_028739e2:

    # "I can't let that happen again. I don't care what happens to me any more, I just need to see her one last time."
    "No em puc permetre que això torni a passar. Ja no m'importa el que em passi, només necessito veure-la una última vegada."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6732
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_95756268:

    # "…There!"
    "...Allà!"

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6737
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_031dce2a:

    # "A sliver of yellow and white comes into view some distance down the road, her figure silhouetted by the lights emanating from the airport entrance."
    "Una taca groga i blanca apareix en la distància a la carretera, la seva figura es retalla per les llums que emanen de l'entrada de l'aeroport."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6739
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_c92725b9:

    # hi "Lilly! Lilly!"
    hi "Lilly! Lilly!"

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6741
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_c0dfd6a2:

    # hi "Lilly! Stop, please! Lilly!"
    hi "Lilly! Para, si us plau! Lilly!"

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6743
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_eb259ac0:

    # "Come on Lilly, I know your hearing's far beyond nor—"
    "Vinga, Lilly, sé que la teva oïda supera de llarg la no—"

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6755
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_7f83092f:

    # hi "Gah!"
    hi "Ahh!"

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6757
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_48aaf4fe:

    # "My view suddenly spins out of control and ends up on the ground, my body haphazardly sprawled after hitting someone and stumbling over."
    "La vista se'm descontrola de sobte i acabo a terra, amb el cos estès de qualsevol manera després de colpejar algú i ensopegar-me."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6766
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_8c1e0008:

    # "Before I can assess the damage, an unbelievable pain ignites in my body. All my thoughts are blanked as I curl up and frantically clutch at my chest."
    "Abans de poder avaluar els danys, un dolor increïble s'encén per tot el cos. Se'm queda la ment en blanc mentre m'arrauleixo i m'abraço frenèticament el pit."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6768
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_7e3bd36a:

    # mystery "Hey, are you okay? That was a really bad fall."
    mystery "Ei, estàs bé? Has tingut una molt mala caiguda."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6770
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_51b5cf01:

    # "This pain… I can't…"
    "Aquest dolor... No puc..."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6772
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_ec2bc502:

    # hi "Argh… aaaaaargh!"
    hi "Argh… aaaaaargh!"

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6781
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_bf1313c3:

    # "Any sharp knock could do me in. Any overexertion. I thought I could overcome my limits this once…"
    "Qualsevol cop fort podria acabar amb mi. Qualsevol sobreesforç. Vaig pensar que aquesta vegada podria superar els meus límits..."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6783
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_8a92dc11:

    # mystery "Something's wrong with him!"
    mystery "A aquest noi li passa alguna cosa!"

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6792
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_f315adc1:

    # mystery "What's the matter, are…"
    mystery "Què et passa, estàs..."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6810
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_4f933043:

    # "The voices of those gathering around me are gradually replaced by a loud ringing in my ears. By now I'm unable to move my head, my eyes turn upwards to see the mute moving of their lips."
    "Les veus de la gent que s'aplega al meu voltant se substitueixen gradualment per un xiulet que sona a les orelles. Ja no puc moure el cap, miro cap amunt per veure el mut moviment dels seus llavis."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6846
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_524a5b2e:

    # "Even as I clutch my chest, I realize I can't feel my fingers any more, nor my feet. It feels like my entire body is shutting down, starting from my extremities."
    "Mentre m'agafo el pit, m'adono que ja no puc sentir els dits, ni els peus. Sembla que tot el meu cos s'estigui apagant, començant per les extremitats."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6854
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_307b6b0e:

    # "With one last effort, I turn my head down the road towards the airport entrance that's casting its light over me."
    "Amb un últim esforç, giro el cap en direcció a la carretera cap a l'entrada de l'aeroport que m'està il·luminant."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6856
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_6e0710c5:

    # "Lilly is there, behind the crowd. Her head is tilted, but only just slightly."
    "La Lilly és allà, darrere de la multitud. Té el cap inclinat, però només lleugerament."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6860
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_a443acca:

    # "I can feel my vision dimming as I try to yell out, but nothing emerges from my mouth despite my best efforts. Slowly but surely, my vision begins to black out the scene before me."
    "Sento que la meva visió s'esmorteeix mentre intento cridar, però no em surt res de la boca malgrat els meus esforços. De mica en mica, la visió comença a enfosquir l'escena que tinc al davant."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6862
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_80dafa12:

    # "So… this is how it ends."
    "Així... és com s'acaba."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6864
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_a5d7a5db:

    # "I failed. I was so close, so very close, but at the very last moment my condition seized my chance at a new life and dragged me back."
    "He fallat. Estava tan a prop, tan a prop, però en l'últim moment la meva malaltia m'ha arrabassat una nova vida i m'ha arrossegat enrere."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6866
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_9a381bab:

    # "Now I'm going to die, sprawled out just meters from an airport, with a crowd of babbling people surrounding me and with Lilly leaving for Scotland just a little distance ahead."
    "Ara moriré, estès a pocs metres d'un aeroport, amb una multitud de gent balbucejant rodejant-me i amb la Lilly marxant cap a Escòcia només una mica més endavant."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6868
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_d4f09e9d:

    # hi "Li… lly…"
    hi "Li… lly…"

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6872
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_1e8b3d6f:

    # "That last word extinguishes the last of my energy. The world falls into a deep, inescapable blackness as every muscle in my body shuts down."
    "Aquesta última paraula apaga les meves últimes energies. El món cau en una profunda i ineludible foscor, cada múscul del meu cos s'apaga."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6874
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_d27645d9:

    # "I'm sorry, Lilly."
    "Perdona'm Lilly."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6876
translate ca a4_lilly_false_cadence_24574dca:

    # "I was too late."
    "He arribat tard."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6890
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_maudlin_sky_ce617998:

    # "…"
    "…"

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6892
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_maudlin_sky_442941ca:

    # "……"
    "……"

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6894
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_maudlin_sky_b010f1b9:

    # "………"
    "………"

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6896
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_maudlin_sky_e2df87d1:

    # "What's… going on…?"
    "Què... ha passat...?"

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6898
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_maudlin_sky_3daec68d:

    # "As I slowly open my eyes, a bright, white light assaults my retinas."
    "Obro els ulls lentament i una llum blanca i brillant m'ataca les retines."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6900
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_maudlin_sky_ceedbdec:

    # "For minutes I just lay where I am, mindlessly staring ahead while my scattered thoughts coalesce in my slowly waking mind."
    "Durant minuts em quedo estirat on estic, amb la mirada perduda mentre els pensaments dispersos es fusionen en la meva ment que es desperta lentament."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6906
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_maudlin_sky_29b87ea6:

    # "Slowly but surely, the white begins to come into focus as a bare expanse begins to be drawn across my field of vision."
    "De mica en mica, el blanc comença a enfocar-se a mesura que una extensió nua comença a dibuixar-se a través del meu camp de visió."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6908
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_maudlin_sky_fa514712:

    # "It's only when the light fixture comes into view that my mind clicks that this is the ceiling above me."
    "Només quan veig el llum, m'adono que estic mirant el sostre que tinc al damunt."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6913
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_maudlin_sky_cea97aa2:

    # "Slowly levering myself up, I silently absorb through all my senses the details of the room I'm in."
    "M'aixeco a poc a poc, absorbeixo en silenci a través de tots els meus sentits els detalls de l'habitació on estic."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6915
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_maudlin_sky_e9afdd61:

    # "The smell and taste of strong bleach hang in the air, lending the impression of a place just slightly too clean to be natural."
    "L'olor i el sabor de lleixiu floten a l'aire, i fa l'efecte de ser un lloc una mica massa net per ser natural."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6917
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_maudlin_sky_f4608723:

    # "Inoffensive pale peach-colored walls, all perfectly painted without a crack, stain or imperfection. A single framed painting hangs on the wall, perfectly straightened. Like the walls, it's as boring and inoffensive as can be."
    "Les parets inofensives d'un color préssec pàl·lid, perfectament pintat sense esquerda, taca o imperfecció. Un únic quadre emmarcat penja de la paret, perfectament centrat. Com les parets, és d'allò més avorrit i inofensiu."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6919
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_maudlin_sky_30ce39e3:

    # "My attention's grabbed by the translucent curtain waving across my vision, my eyes following it to the open window it covers."
    "Em crida l'atenció la cortina translúcida que es mou davant meu, la segueixo fins a la finestra oberta que està tapant."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6921
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_maudlin_sky_d4466daf:

    # "When I move my right arm to try to lift myself up and look through it, I feel the catheter dig in uncomfortably. It's only now, too, that I notice the cannula tubes winding around my cheeks and into my nose."
    "Quan moc el braç dret per intentar aixecar-me i mirar-hi a través, noto que el catèter se'm clava incòmodament. També ara m'adono dels tubs de cànula que em rodegen les galtes i m'arriben al nas."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6923
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_maudlin_sky_cbd6ff49:

    # "After some fidgeting, I settle for just looking around the corner of the window."
    "Després de moure'm una mica, em conformo a mirar per la cantonada de la finestra."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6928
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_maudlin_sky_39dc330f:

    # "Beyond the thick leaves of several large trees, I can see the greenery below, backing out onto a field. A customary island of green on the outskirts of the city."
    "Més enllà de les fulles espesses dels grans arbres, puc veure la vegetació de sota, que dona a un camp. Una illa verda habitual als afores de la ciutat."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6930
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_maudlin_sky_8bc9f154:

    # "Judging by the sun outside, it's noon. Of which day, though, I'm not sure."
    "Si he de jutjar pel sol de fora, és migdia. Però no n'estic segur de quin dia deu ser."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6932
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_maudlin_sky_9e390ba4:

    # "So… I'm in a hospital once again."
    "Així que... torno a ser en un hospital."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6934
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_maudlin_sky_ef37c3dd:

    # "I let out a long, tired breath as I try to collect my scattered thoughts, my mind seemingly cast in a dozen directions all at once with as many emotions running through me."
    "Deixo anar un sospir llarg i cansat mentre intento ordenar tants pensaments dispersos, sembla que la ment se m'ha llançat cap a una dotzena de direccions alhora amb tantes emocions."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6939
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_maudlin_sky_9d13f4ff:

    # "After slowly lying back down, I decide to start at the beginning; why I'm here."
    "Després de tornar a estirar-me lentament, decideixo començar des del principi: per què soc aquí."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6941
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_maudlin_sky_12690de9:

    # "I cast my mind back, but I can't work out a smooth recollection of what happened. The events of last night… or whichever night it was… come back more as a series of snapshots than any cohesive memory."
    "Faig memòria, però no aconsegueixo esbrinar què va passar. Els esdeveniments d'ahir a la nit... o de la nit que fos... em tornen com una sèrie d'instantànies més que com un record cohesiu."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6948
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_maudlin_sky_2b4a93a1:

    # "Lying on my bed looking at the origami bird."
    "Estirat al llit tot mirant l'ocell d'origami."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6955
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_maudlin_sky_c2c37c49:

    # "Talking to Hideaki outside the Hakamichi residence."
    "Parlant amb Hideaki fora de la residència Hakamichi."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6962
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_maudlin_sky_6eb7b7d2:

    # "Running down the street, passing pedestrians and bumping into more and more of them."
    "Corrent pel carrer, passant als vianants i xocant-hi cada cop més."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6971
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_maudlin_sky_41a38e7b:

    # "Falling."
    "Fracassant."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6977
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_maudlin_sky_880407de:

    # "Looking up at the searingly bright airport entrance, seeing Lilly's back as I lay on the ground…"
    "Mirant cap a l'entrada de l'aeroport, brillant, veient l'esquena de la Lilly mentre jo estava a terra..."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6979
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_maudlin_sky_ce617998_1:

    # "…"
    "…"

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6984
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_maudlin_sky_4992c769:

    # "The silence of the private room suddenly feels overwhelming."
    "El silenci de l'habitació privada de sobte em sembla aclaparador."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6988
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_maudlin_sky_76b2fe88:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6991
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_maudlin_sky_8d70b7ea:

    # n "{vspace=30}So that's it. I had my chance to correct my mistake, and I blew it."
    n "{vspace=30}Així que això és tot. Vaig tenir l'oportunitat de corregir el meu error, i la vaig desaprofitar."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6993
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_maudlin_sky_3a74baf3:

    # n "Whether I was at fault for neglecting my medication and disregarding to pace myself, or my body was for giving out so soon, it doesn't matter now."
    n "Tant si la culpa va ser meva per negligir la medicació i no respectar el meu ritme, o del meu cos per rendir-se tan aviat, ara ja no importa."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6995
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_maudlin_sky_9f3156a6:

    # n "All that matters is that, once again, I'm alone."
    n "L'única cosa que importa és que, una altra vegada, estic sol."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6997
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_maudlin_sky_03fe5d3a:

    # n "The pastel blue pillow yields with little resistance as I let myself fall back onto the bed, its starchy case, along with the starchy sheets, providing little comfort."
    n "El coixí blau cel cedeix sense posar resistència quan em deixo caure de nou al llit, amb la funda emmidonada, juntament amb els llençols emmidonats, no són gaire còmodes."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:6999
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_maudlin_sky_2f00b30c:

    # n "Compared to the darkness of last night's events, the bright light of the room around me is striking. All it does, though, is emphasize how otherworldly places like this are."
    n "En comparació amb la foscor dels esdeveniments d'ahir a la nit, la llum brillant de l'habitació que m'envolta és sorprenent. L'únic que fa, però, és emfatitzar com en són d'irreals, els llocs com aquest."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7001
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_maudlin_sky_1350d402:

    # n "{vspace=30}Arrhythmia."
    n "{vspace=30}Arrítmia."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7003
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_maudlin_sky_d2b19279:

    # n "{vspace=30}A strange word. A foreign, alien one. One that you don't want to be in the same room with."
    n "{vspace=30}Una paraula estranya. Desconeguda, aliena. Una amb la que no vols compartir habitació."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7005
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_maudlin_sky_96ac1846:

    # n "A rare condition. It causes the heart to act erratically and occasionally beat way too fast. It can be fatal."
    n "Una malaltia poc freqüent. Fa que el cor actuï de manera erràtica i, ocasionalment, que bategui massa ràpid. Pot ser mortal."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7007
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_maudlin_sky_e288a988:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

    old "[_n_] {vspace=30}'It was a miracle that you were able to go on so long without anything happening,' they said."
    new "[_n_] {vspace=30}\"Va ser un miracle que poguessis aguantar tant de temps sense que passés res\", em van dir."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7011
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_maudlin_sky_408ceeff:

    # n "And then, it did. My condition had taken away everything; my old school was of no importance any more. My home was reduced to a faraway place. Both my friends and my first love simply stopped visiting after a length of time."
    n "I llavors, ho va fer. La meva malaltia m'ho havia tret tot; la meva antiga escola ja no tenia importància. La meva llar es va reduir a un lloc llunyà. Tant els meus amics com el meu primer amor simplement van deixar de visitar-me al cap d'un temps."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7013
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_maudlin_sky_f9e6cf5e:

    # n "I became cynical and embittered. Distant and subdued. In my defense, no person could avoid that after such a thing happening to them, but nonetheless I left the hospital as a very definitely changed person."
    n "Em vaig tornar cínic i amargat. Distant i apagat. En la meva defensa, cap persona podia evitar-ho després que li passés una cosa així, però, tot i això, vaig sortir de l'hospital com una persona definitivament canviada."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7015
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_maudlin_sky_a6a5fcd0:

    # n "Things changed. I made new friends in Hanako, Shizune and Misha. I found a new sense of 'home' in my dormitory, a new interest in science and the world around me, and I found a direction to my life that I had never felt before."
    n "Les coses van canviar. Vaig fer nous amics com la Hanako, la Shizune i la Misha. Vaig trobar una nova sensació de \"llar\" al meu dormitori, un nou interès per la ciència i el món que m'envoltava, i vaig trobar una direcció cap a on enfocar la meva vida que no havia sentit abans."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7017
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_maudlin_sky_2aa2e2bb:

    # n "{vspace=30}But I'd also discovered other things."
    n "{vspace=30}Però també vaig descobrir altres coses."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7019
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_maudlin_sky_61c19a31:

    # n "The sense of isolation in Yamaku and its surrounds was not entirely unwelcome, the quiet giving a peace of mind I might not have found elsewhere, but it gave the area a feeling of being pushed out of the way, of being kept out of sight."
    n "La sensació de soledat al Yamaku i els seus voltants no era del tot desagradable, el silenci em donava una pau mental que no hauria trobat en cap altre lloc, però li donava a la zona la sensació de ser apartada, fora de la vista."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7021
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_maudlin_sky_3a0a54af:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

    old "[_n_] {vspace=60}People in the streets would sometimes glance awkwardly, or quickly turn their heads as they realized they were staring. Even if my condition wasn't visible, my uniform was."
    new "[_n_] {vspace=60}La gent de vegades em mirava estranyada o girava el cap quan s'adonaven que m'estaven mirant. Encara que la meva malaltia no fos visible, l'uniforme sí que ho era."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7025
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_maudlin_sky_23b597cd:

    # n "Even if it weren't, I was still different. I took seventeen pills a day, morning, midday and night. My scar, though hidden behind clothing, was still a permanent mark of my condition. And most of all, there was the very real possibility of death."
    n "Encara que no fos així, era diferent. Prenia disset pastilles al dia: matí, migdia i vespre. La meva cicatriu, amagada darrere de la roba, continuava sent una marca permanent de la meva malaltia. I sobretot, hi havia la possibilitat real de morir."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7027
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_maudlin_sky_ea217089:

    # n "A bad fall. An absentminded hard hit on the back. A simple sprint taken too far. Anything could have set my heart off, and several times I teetered on the edge of the abyss even with all the care I took of myself."
    n "Una mala caiguda. Un cop fort a l'esquena mentre estava distret. Un simple esprint que anés massa lluny. Qualsevol cosa podria haver fet esclatar el meu cor, i diverses vegades m'he balancejat a la vora de l'abisme, fins i tot amb la cura que tenia de mi mateix."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7029
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_maudlin_sky_fde3c202:

    # n "{vspace=30}But that was fine. I could have lived with all that."
    n "{vspace=30}Però no em feia res. Podia viure així."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7031
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_maudlin_sky_ae934372:

    # n "Because there was one final thing I'd found, or rather refound, after entering Yamaku."
    n "Perquè hi havia una última cosa que havia trobat, o més aviat tornat a trobar, després d'entrar al Yamaku."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7033
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_maudlin_sky_61b8a803:

    # n "{vspace=30}Which was once again snatched away before my eyes."
    n "{vspace=30}Que una altra vegada em van tornar a prendre."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7035
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_maudlin_sky_7bb73334:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

    old "[_n_] {vspace=30}It's only now that I realize just how delicate my newfound sense of happiness was. Everything depended on her, the linchpin of my life since I first entered Yamaku as a sullen, confused and aimless transfer student."
    new "[_n_] {vspace=30}És ara que m'adono que delicada era aquesta recentment descoberta sensació de felicitat. Tot depenia d'ella, era l'eix de la meva vida d'ençà que vaig entrar al Yamaku com a estudiant acabat de transferir, malhumorat, confús i sense rumb."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7039
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_maudlin_sky_460f09cc:

    # n "Lilly Satou was the one person I could depend upon above all others, and who reciprocated the love that I felt for her. But I failed her, and only realized it all too late."
    n "La Lilly Satou era l'única persona de qui podia dependre per sobre de totes les altres, i que corresponia l'amor que sentia per ella. Però la vaig fallar, i no me'n vaig adonar fins que ja era massa tard."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7041
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_maudlin_sky_4bf652b4:

    # n "I thought that I could just set my life up and continue that way forever, but the real world doesn't work like that. I finally realized the meaning of those words, only to be struck down as I confronted my failure to do so in time."
    n "Creia que podria establir-me la vida i continuar així per sempre, però el món real no funciona així. Finalment, vaig entendre el significat d'aquestes paraules, a temps per enfrontar al meu fracàs per no haver-ho fet a temps."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7043
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_maudlin_sky_e49a48d7:

    # n "{vspace=30}…"
    n "{vspace=30}…"

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7045
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_maudlin_sky_bc2810bc:

    # n "{vspace=30}The surroundings I'm in now are all too familiar. It's as if Yamaku was but a dream, and I'm still recovering from my first major heart attack."
    n "{vspace=30}L'entorn on estic ara em resulta massa familiar. És com si el Yamaku només fos un somni, i jo encara m'estigués recuperant del meu primer gran atac de cor."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7047
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_maudlin_sky_45f0335e:

    # n "Maybe that's why I feel so tired. It feels almost as if I've lived the entire last few months of my life in the space of minutes."
    n "Potser per això estic tan cansat. És com si hagués viscut els últims mesos en qüestió de minuts."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7050
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_maudlin_sky_76b2fe88_1:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7055
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_maudlin_sky_28109729:

    # "The weight of my eyelids closes my eyes, my physical and mental exhaustion letting me offer no resistance."
    "El pes de les parpelles em tanca els ulls, l'esgotament físic i mental no em deixa oferir resistència."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7057
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_maudlin_sky_62de665f:

    # "Unintelligible mumbling from ahead of the bed stirs me out of my sleep."
    "L'inintel·ligible murmuri davant del llit em fa sortir del son."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7059
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_maudlin_sky_ab44f2d8:

    # "With my eyes still closed, I can focus and make out someone, presumably a nurse, bidding farewell to a doctor."
    "Amb els ulls encara tancats, puc enfocar i distingir a algú, presumiblement algú d'infermeria, que s'acomiada d'un metge."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7064
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_maudlin_sky_97920bbb:

    # "As I open my eyes, I notice the door closing in my peripheral vision."
    "Quan obro els ulls, veig la porta tancada en la meva visió perifèrica."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7066
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_maudlin_sky_a75c819b:

    # "The doctor stands reading some notes off a clipboard held in his hand, carefully looking over the pages."
    "El metge està dempeus llegint algunes notes d'una carpeta de pinça que té a la mà, mirant-ne atentament les pàgines."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7068
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_maudlin_sky_accd39a1:

    # "After consulting his obviously very important documents, he looks up and notices my gaze. It's now that I notice something slightly odd about his expression and general disposition, but I can't quite put my finger on it."
    "Després de consultar els seus documents, evidentment molt importants, aixeca la vista i nota la meva mirada. Noto alguna cosa estranya en la seva expressió i disposició general, però no n'estic segur."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7070
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_maudlin_sky_52c546d2:

    # "Doctor" "Ah, I see you're awake… Mr. Nakai."
    "Doctor" "Ah, veig que estàs despert... Sr. Nakai."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7072
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_maudlin_sky_2b2db0bc:

    # "His quick glance to my bed end, to verify my name, shows that his documents obviously didn't have it written on them."
    "Fa una ullada ràpida al meu capçal, per verificar el meu nom, cosa que demostra que en els seus documents no hi estava escrit."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7074
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_maudlin_sky_34d0fab9:

    # "Doctor" "I must admit this is a bit unfortunate; your parents visited just earlier while you were asleep. I could notify them you're awake now, if you'd like."
    "Doctor" "He d'admetre que això és una mica desafortunat: els teus pares t'han visitat fa una estona mentre dormies. Puc avisar-los que ja t'has despertat, si vols."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7076
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_maudlin_sky_03b6c41d:

    # hi "Um… thanks. That would be good."
    hi "Um... gràcies. Estaria bé."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7078
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_maudlin_sky_9d241277:

    # "I give a somewhat dazed reply, most likely the one he'd expect, before really thinking about what I'm saying."
    "Responc una mica atordit, probablement he dit allò que ell esperava, en comptes de pensar realment què estava dient."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7080
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_maudlin_sky_56a38a2c:

    # "Doctor" "Not a problem."
    "Doctor" "Cap problema."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7082
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_maudlin_sky_fcaf871d:

    # "Doctor" "If you have any questions you'd like to ask, I'll be happy to answer them. That is, unless you'd prefer to rest; the anaesthetic's still going to be affecting you a bit, I'm afraid."
    "Doctor" "Si tens alguna pregunta, estaré encantat de respondre-te-la. Tret que prefereixis descansar: em sembla que l'anestesia encara t'afectarà una mica."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7084
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_maudlin_sky_273dfb86:

    # "The anaesthetic… of course. That'd be why I felt so strange the first time I woke up."
    "L'anestèsia... és clar. Per això em vaig sentir tan estrany la primera vegada que em vaig despertar."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7086
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_maudlin_sky_d6987177:

    # "I slowly shake my head, not wanting to dislodge any pipes or cause myself any more discomfort than necessary. The doctor politely puts down his clipboard in response."
    "Nego a poc a poc amb el cap, intentant no desmuntar cap tub ni causar-me més molèsties de les necessàries. El metge baixa educadament la seva carpeta com a resposta."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7088
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_maudlin_sky_4b02dd70:

    # hi "I guess my main question is… what exactly happened?"
    hi "Suposo que la meva pregunta principal és... que ha passat exactament?"

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7090
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_maudlin_sky_8f6530f6:

    # "Doctor" "To put it simply, you've unfortunately had another heart attack. While not as severe as your first, you were very lucky it occurred so close to a hospital."
    "Doctor" "En poques paraules, desgraciadament has patit un altre infart. Tot i que no ha estat tan greu com el primer, vas tenir molta sort que et passés a prop de l'hospital."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7092
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_maudlin_sky_2c426f58:

    # "Doctor" "After being stabilized, you were taken to the operating room. What followed was keyhole surgery in order to insert a temporary pacemaker."
    "Doctor" "Després d'estabilitzar-te, et van portar al quiròfan. Et van fer una laparoscòpia per posar-te un marcapassos temporal."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7094
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_maudlin_sky_05023011:

    # "Doctor" "All in all, the incident happened two days ago, with emergency treatment being carried out very soon afterward. Since then, we've kept you under close observation while you were asleep."
    "Doctor" "Fet i fet, l'incident va tenir lloc fa dos dies, i el tractament d'urgències es va dur a terme poc després. Des de llavors, t'hem tingut en estricta observació mentre dormies."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7096
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_maudlin_sky_ea2b3856:

    # hi "Will I be all right? Are there any lasting problems?"
    hi "Em posaré bé?  Tindré algun problema a la llarga?"

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7098
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_maudlin_sky_15cdd2b2:

    # "Doctor" "Compared to the procedure carried out for your first heart attack, this was relatively minor."
    "Doctor" "Comparat amb el procediment que et van fer en el teu primer infart, aquest va ser relativament menor."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7100
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_maudlin_sky_78aabafb:

    # "Doctor" "While you will have to undergo surgery once more in a few days' time to remove the pacemaker, assuming there are no complications, there should be no lasting implications."
    "Doctor" "Tot i que hauràs de tornar a operar en un parell de dies per treure't el marcapassos, si no hi ha complicacions no hi hauria d'haver conseqüències duradores."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7102
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_maudlin_sky_402c6b87:

    # "He continues talking, the subject shifting to a repetition of facts about arrhythmia and my medications that I already know for the most part. I start to nod and feign interest, while my mind drifts."
    "Continua parlant, el tema canvia a una repetició de fets sobre l'arrítmia i la meva medicació que, en gran part, ja conec. Començo a assentir amb el cap i a fingir interès, mentre em divaga la meva."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7104
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_maudlin_sky_5504fe60:

    # "I begin to think about how perfectly hung the inoffensive painting hanging on the wall behind his shoulder is, and how neat and sterile the surroundings are, even including the doctor himself."
    "Començo a pensar en com de ben penjat està el quadre inofensiu que hi ha a la paret darrere de la seva espatlla, i com de net i estèril està l'entorn, fins i tot el mateix metge."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7106
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_maudlin_sky_b0b5b022:

    # "Doctor" "If my mumbling bores you, you are quite welcome to say so, Mr. Nakai. Lord knows, I lose track of myself sometimes."
    "Doctor" "Si la meva xerrameca l'avorreix, pot dir-ho, Sr. Nakai. Déu sap que de vegades perdo la noció del que dic."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7108
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_maudlin_sky_ca9898bb:

    # "He gives a short chuckle at his self-deprecating joke as I grimace awkwardly, having been rather badly caught out."
    "Deixa anar una petita rialleta amb la seva broma autocrítica mentre jo faig una ganyota incòmoda, ja que m'ha ben pillat."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7110
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_maudlin_sky_827844db:

    # "The doctor's chuckle sounds different from that of the nurse at Yamaku though, come to think of it. As I ponder why, I realize why the man in front of me feels just that little bit 'off'."
    "La rialleta del metge sona diferent de la de l'infermer del Yamaku, ara que hi penso. Mentre hi reflexiono, m'adono de per què l'home que tinc davant em sembla una mica \"estrany\"."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7112
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_maudlin_sky_e47855b8:

    # "His smile is neat and sterile. He delivers his little joke perfectly, with a customary inoffensive chuckle."
    "Té un somriure net i estèril. Fa la seva broma a la perfecció, amb el seu habitual somriure inofensiu."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7114
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_maudlin_sky_01bbd401:

    # "It is like, rather than talking to the man whose name is neatly printed on the nametag pinned to his lab coat, I'm merely interacting with an actor reading off a prerehearsed script, every action having been choreographed beforehand."
    "És com si, en lloc de parlar amb l'home que té el nom que està tan ben imprès a l'etiqueta de la seva bata de laboratori, simplement estic interactuant amb un actor que llegeix un guió que ja ha assajat, amb cada acció coreografiada prèviament."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7116
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_maudlin_sky_3815c80b:

    # "I suppose he has to be this way though, being a doctor."
    "Però suposo que deu ser així, sent metge."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7118
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_maudlin_sky_0f92f24f:

    # "He has to keep his neat and sterile smile when chatting to the girl with cancer slowly spreading through her body, when reassuring the woman who'll surely die from childbirth, and with every other terminally and critically ill patient."
    "Ha de mantenir el seu somriure net i estèril quan parla amb la noia amb un càncer que s'estén lentament pel seu cos, quan tranquil·litza a la dona que segurament morirà de part, i amb tots els altres pacients terminals i crítics."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7120
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_maudlin_sky_78c74756:

    # "That little bit of distance. That little bit of aloofness."
    "Aquesta petita distància. Aquesta mica de llunyania."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7122
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_maudlin_sky_d42281cb:

    # "It makes me wonder if I've been too harsh, especially considering it's a disposition far from being adopted only by people in his profession."
    "Em fa preguntar si he estat massa dur, especialment tenint en compte que és una disposició lluny de ser adoptada només per la gent de la seva professió."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7124
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_maudlin_sky_c097bdd1:

    # "After all, the one I loved kept that same distance from others herself."
    "Al cap i a la fi, la persona que estimava es mantenia lluny de la resta."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7126
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_maudlin_sky_12818236:

    # "Looking up to the doctor again, I realize I've been in thought with my head bowed for some time."
    "Miro al metge una altra vegada, m'adono que he estat pensant amb el cap cot durant una estona."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7128
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_maudlin_sky_cf9710f3:

    # "Doctor" "I understand you must still be tired. You've been through a lot, and as I mentioned before, the anaesthetic would still be affecting you."
    "Doctor" "Entenc que encara deus estar cansat. Has passat per moltes coses i, com t'he dit abans, l'anestesia encara et fa efecte."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7130
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_maudlin_sky_48ff0e06:

    # "Doctor" "If you don't mind, I'll let you get some rest and tell your parents you've woken up for you."
    "Doctor" "Si no et fa res, et deixaré descansar una mica i els diré als teus pares que ja t'has despertat."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7132
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_maudlin_sky_f349f0dc:

    # hi "I think… that would be good. Thank you."
    hi "Crec... que això estaria bé. Gràcies."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7136
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_maudlin_sky_23369489:

    # "He gives a curt nod before picking up his clipboard and making his way to the large white door in the corner of the room, closing it behind him with a thud."
    "Assenteix secament abans d'agafar la carpeta i fer el seu camí cap a la gran porta blanca a la cantonada de l'habitació, i la tanca darrere seu amb un cop sord."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7138
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_maudlin_sky_d9632a50:

    # "In the end, I'm alone again."
    "Al final, torno a estar sol."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7140
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_maudlin_sky_ca7b35be:

    # "Lilly's gone. Akira's gone. Hanako would be traveling, and even my parents have already left the hospital."
    "La Lilly ha marxat. L'Akira ha marxat. La Hanako deu estar viatjant, i fins i tot els meus pares ja han marxat de l'hospital."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7142
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_maudlin_sky_b9d04e28:

    # "Four pale peach walls, one white ceiling, and a single open window to look out towards the world outside."
    "Quatre parets de color de préssec pàl·lid, un sostre blanc i una sola finestra oberta per mirar cap al món exterior."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7144
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_maudlin_sky_4959cd8d:

    # "It's hard to think of the future when the past is crowded around you, claustrophobic in its neat, sterile, starchy, bleach-smelling grip."
    "És difícil pensar en el futur quan tens el passat al teu voltant, claustrofòbic de tan net, estèril, emmidonat i amb olor de lleixiu."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7146
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_maudlin_sky_9387de60:

    # "Lost for what to do or focus on, I content myself with sleeping the time away as if this were all just another dream like Yamaku had been."
    "No sé què fer ni en què concentrar-me, així que em conformo a passar el temps dormint, com si tot això no fos més que un somni, tal com ho havia estat el Yamaku."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7158
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_bright_sky_79ff7ebb:

    # "White."
    "Blanc."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7160
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_bright_sky_31c7853c:

    # "A sterile, clean white for a sterile, clean room."
    "Un blanc estèril i net per a una habitació estèril i neta."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7169
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_bright_sky_78899b46:

    # "My eyes open, and I simply stare at the ceiling for some time. It's about as interesting as the television would be, mounted in its metal rack hanging off the ceiling ahead of the bed."
    "Obro els ulls i em quedo mirant el sostre una bona estona. És tan interessant com ho seria un televisor, muntat en el seu suport metàl·lic i penjat del sostre davant del llit."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7171
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_bright_sky_bfe368bf:

    # "Indeed, the television saw its entire use during the time my parents were here. Left on quietly as they waited for me to wake, it was about as banal as it had been the first time I'd ended up in the hospital."
    "De fet, la televisió es va fer servir durant el temps que els meus pares van ser aquí. La deixaven encesa en silenci mentre esperaven que em despertés, era tan banal com ho havia estat la primera vegada que vaig acabar a l'hospital."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7173
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_bright_sky_6cb04864:

    # "Earlier today an attending nurse had offered to turn off the EKG's speakers. I refused simply because the sound is so entirely normal to me now."
    "Avui, algú del personal d'infermeria m'ha ofert a apagar els altaveus de l'electrocardiograma. M'hi he negat simplement perquè el so ja m'és completament normal."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7175
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_bright_sky_40950ab4:

    # "It's almost comforting, in a way. The metronome-like regularity gives at least some feeling that time is moving, even in a place such as this."
    "És gairebé reconfortant, en certa manera. La regularitat del metrònom almenys em fa la sensació que el temps es mou, fins i tot en un lloc com aquest."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7177
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_bright_sky_ad2bfc25:

    # "After some time of listening to its beeping while I fully awaken, though, I realize there's another sound in the room."
    "Però després d'una estona escoltant com pita mentre m'acabo de despertar, m'adono que hi ha un altre so a l'habitació."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7181
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_bright_sky_e63a28a1:

    # "Concentrating all my efforts on listening, a task made rather easy by the lack of distractions, a tiny tinny melody can be heard."
    "Concentro tots els meus esforços per escoltar, una tasca prou fàcil per la manca de distraccions, i puc escoltar una petita melodia enllaunada."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7183
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_bright_sky_e27ea15c:

    # "Light and quiet, the music sounds almost fragile as it's dwarfed by the EKG's pulses."
    "Lleugera i tranquil·la, la música sona quasi fràgil, ja que l'eclipsa els batecs de l'electrocardiograma."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7188
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_bright_sky_7022bc55:

    # "Tilting my head just slightly to the side in an effort to see the source of the melody without dislodging any of the sensors and pipes stuck onto me, I notice a little wooden box sitting on the nightstand next to the bed."
    "Inclino lleugerament el cap de costat per veure l'origen de la melodia sense treure'm de sobre els sensors i tubs que tinc enganxats, i veig una capseta de fusta a la tauleta de nit al costat del meu llit."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7199
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_bright_sky_23ce919e:

    # "My mouth opens just slightly while I silently watch the tiny yellow metal drum slowly rotate inside, the little bumps on its surface gradually moving in and out of sight."
    "Obro lleugerament la boca mentre observo en silenci el diminut tambor metàl·lic groc com gira lentament a l'interior, la part rugosa es mou gradualment apropant-se i allunyant-se de la meva vista."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7201
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_bright_sky_2baeebfa:

    # "This music box… it's the one I gave…"
    "Aquesta capseta de música... és la que li vaig donar..."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7210
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_bright_sky_bc60a917:

    # "The creaking of the door breaks me out of my reverie, my head and heart remaining still as my eyes turn to see who comes through."
    "El xerric de la porta em treu del meu somni, el meu cap i el meu cor romanen quiets mentre giro els ulls per veure qui entra."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7212
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_bright_sky_0faf4acb:

    # "Long tan skirt… peach off-the-shoulder sweater… pale, almost porcelain skin… blue clouded eyes and long, yellow hair…"
    "Faldilla llarga de color marró... jersei de color préssec amb les espatlles al descobert... pell pàl·lida, gairebé de porcellana... ulls blaus ennuvolats i cabells llargs i grocs..."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7217
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_bright_sky_559af9a8:

    # "All I can do is stare as Lilly slowly walks into the room, her fingers lightly running over the wall for orientation, and my mind comes to a shuddering halt."
    "L'única cosa que puc fer és mirar com la Lilly entra lentament a l'habitació, recorrent la paret amb els dits per orientar-se, i la ment se m'atura de cop."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7219
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_bright_sky_cd2fa9eb:

    # hi "L… Lilly…?"
    hi "L… Lilly…?"

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7224
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_bright_sky_ad90a727:

    # "She stops midstride, her entire body tensing."
    "S'atura a mig camí i se li tensa tot el cos."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7226
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_bright_sky_9d3115ec:

    # li "Hisao? Was that you?"
    li "Hisao? Ets tu?"

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7228
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_bright_sky_7ff56e16:

    # "Her voice is quiet and pensive, echoing her expression."
    "La seva veu és tranquil·la i pensativa, com un eco de la seva expressió."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7230
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_bright_sky_b9a1bf8f:

    # hi "I thought you were…"
    hi "Em pensava que estaves..."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7235
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_bright_sky_76f852c5:

    # "Lilly takes one tentative step forward, then another, as if she were holding herself back."
    "La Lilly fa un pas endavant vacil·lant, i després un altre, com si s'estigués frenant."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7240
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_bright_sky_8bf00222:

    # "Her control over her composure is for naught though, and she finally rushes over to where I lay as the last of her resistance falls."
    "Però el control sobre la seva compostura és en va, i finalment s'afanya cap a on estic estirat quan deixa de oposar-s'hi."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7245
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_bright_sky_615df9ae:

    # "I'm slightly taken aback when she grabs hold of me, hunching over as tears begin to fall from her cheeks, since only minutes ago I thought she was on the other side of the world. After a moment of hesitation, I rest my right hand on her soft shoulder."
    "Em sorprèn una mica que s'agafi a mi, arraulida mentre les llàgrimes comencen a caure-li per les galtes, perquè fa només uns minuts pensava que estava a l'altra banda del món. Després d'un moment de vacil·lació, li poso la mà dreta sobre l'espatlla suau."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7247
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_bright_sky_d063b79e:

    # li "Hisao! Hisao!"
    li "Hisao! Hisao!"

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7249
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_bright_sky_2383feb5:

    # "Lilly's body trembles as her tears blot the pale green sheets, her emotions flooding through her carefully maintained exterior."
    "El cos de la Lilly tremola mentre les llàgrimes taquen els llençols de color verd pàl·lid, les seves emocions vessen a través del exterior curosament cuidat."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7251
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_bright_sky_138f761b:

    # "With her face now closer, and made easier to see for her pale skin being lit by the sunlight from the window, I notice her cheeks being redder than they should be."
    "Amb la cara encara més a prop, i més fàcil de veure perquè la seva pell pàl·lida està il·luminada per la llum del sol que ve de la finestra, noto que les galtes estan més vermelles del que haurien."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7253
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_bright_sky_6857e244:

    # hi "It's okay, Lilly. I'm okay. You don't need to—"
    hi "Està bé. Lilly. Estic bé. No t'has de—"

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7258
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_bright_sky_3c4cbbc5:

    # "She rights herself quickly, her crying forcefully stifled with both sadness and stubbornness remaining in her moistened eyes. Her prideful nature, always having been something to contend with, takes me off guard."
    "Es recompon amb rapidesa, afoga el plor amb força, però en els seus ulls humits s'hi pot veure la tristesa i la tossuderia. La seva naturalesa orgullosa, que sempre havia estat una cosa a què enfrontar-me, m'agafa desprevingut."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7260
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_bright_sky_cfd8b174:

    # li "Stop telling me not to worry about you, Hisao!"
    li "Para de dir-me que no em preocupi, Hisao!"

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7262
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_bright_sky_d570c6eb:

    # li "Just this once… let me cry…"
    li "Només aquesta vegada... deixa'm plorar..."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7264
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_bright_sky_6b59a7d2:

    # "I'm caught speechless. She waits for a response, but her composure breaks again after a handful of seconds."
    "Em quedo sense paraules. Espera una resposta, però es torna a descompondre passats uns segons."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7269
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_bright_sky_b10ea51d:

    # "I swallow hard to try and settle my own emotions while she weeps onto my bed, a strange mixture of relief and depression welling up."
    "Empasso saliva per intentar calmar les meves emocions mentre plora sobre el meu llit, amb una estranya barreja d'alleujament i depressió."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7271
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_bright_sky_4ab06efb:

    # "Lilly's… here. She's really here. If I couldn't feel her skin under my hand, I'd hardly believe my own eyes. My efforts weren't for nothing; my body's attempt to take away everything that was important to me once again has been foiled."
    "La Lilly està... aquí. Està aquí de debò. Si no pogués sentir la seva pell amb la meva mà, en prou feines em creuria el que estic veient. Els meus esforços no van ser en va; l'intent del meu cos de treure'm tot allò que era important per a mi s'ha tornat a veure frustrat."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7273
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_bright_sky_21c3b91b:

    # "But now… I don't feel as happy about it as I thought I would."
    "Però ara... No em sento tan feliç com pensava."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7275
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_bright_sky_fc8175de:

    # "Seeing her here, crying like this over me… this is the one thing I'd wanted to avoid since coming to love her, no, even since leaving the hospital."
    "Veient-la aquí, plorant per mi... aquesta és l'única cosa que volia evitar d'ençà que vaig començar a estimar-la, no, fins i tot des que vaig sortir de l'hospital."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7277
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_bright_sky_5ab0ccaf:

    # hi "I'm sorry, Lilly. It's my fault I'm here; I shouldn't have tried to push myself so far."
    hi "Perdona'm Lilly. És culpa meva haver acabat aquí: no hauria d'haver-me exigit tant."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7279
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_bright_sky_70045f6c:

    # "I give a self-deprecating snort."
    "Deixo anar un esbufec d'autocrítica."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7281
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_bright_sky_263447a1:

    # hi "After months of keeping myself together so nobody'd worry over me, I went and did something like this. I guess I'm pretty dumb."
    hi "Després de mesos de fer el cor fort perquè ningú es preocupés per mi, va i faig una cosa així. Dec ser força idiota, ves."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7287
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_bright_sky_4c310ec4:

    # "With a couple of sniffs and a long breath, Lilly manages to pull herself together and calm down a little."
    "Amb un parell de sanglots i respirant profundament, la Lilly aconsegueix recobrar la compostura i calmar-se una mica."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7289
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_bright_sky_36cdc331:

    # "Despite her red cheeks, moist eyes and the lines of her tears still visible, she delicately wears that weak smile she seemed to so often give."
    "Malgrat tenir les galtes vermelles, els ulls humits i les línies de les llàgrimes encara visibles, llueix amb delicadesa aquest dèbil somriure que semblava fer tan sovint."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7291
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_bright_sky_62ed6aab:

    # li "You needn't blame yourself. I heard later that it happened as you were running down the road after me, right?"
    li "No t'has de culpar pas. Més tard em van dir que tot això va passar quan corries per empaitar-me, és veritat?"

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7293
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_bright_sky_f5bfd183:

    # hi "Still…"
    hi "De totes maneres..."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7295
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_bright_sky_ed07cda3:

    # "She wipes her eyes with the back of her hand, returning more to her old self as the rush of emotions wears off."
    "Es neteja els ulls amb el dors de la mà, tornant a ser la d'abans a mesura que li passa la foguerada d'emocions."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7300
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_bright_sky_7dc38a4f:

    # li "Why did you run after me, Hisao?"
    li "Per què em vas córrer al darrere, Hisao? "

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7305
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_bright_sky_f0a4a48c:

    # "I move to respond, but notice her face tightening."
    "Em disposo a respondre, però noto que se li tensa la cara."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7307
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_bright_sky_5cecbfbf:

    # li "Even after I'd said goodbye, and I'd left Yamaku Academy…"
    li "Fins i tot després d'acomiadar-me de vosaltres i deixar l'academia Yamaku..."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7309
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_bright_sky_47d7944f:

    # "She takes a moment to steady herself, her emotions almost bubbling up once again."
    "Es pren un moment per calmar-se, les emocions tornen a desbordar-se."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7311
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_bright_sky_1472af80:

    # hi "I just wanted to say that I'm sorry."
    hi "Només et volia dir que em sap greu."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7316
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_bright_sky_ea6c2158:

    # li "Sorry?"
    li "Et sap greu?"

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7318
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_bright_sky_fe4607b7:

    # hi "For the times when I wasn't there when you needed me."
    hi "Per les vegades que no hi vaig ser quan em necessitaves."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7320
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_bright_sky_942fa342:

    # hi "Until now, I thought you just being there would be enough. I only needed you by my side to make any day feel better."
    hi "Fins ara, pensava que n'hi havia prou amb el fet que hi fossis. Només et necessitava al meu costat per fer  que qualsevol dia fos millor."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7322
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_bright_sky_0ad085a1:

    # hi "Even if my body may be like this, I want to help you, Lilly; to be there when you need someone."
    hi "Encara que el meu cos sigui així, et vull ajudar, Lilly; vull ser-hi quan em necessitis."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7327
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_bright_sky_ad4dab0f:

    # li "But you always were there, Hisao…"
    li "Però si sempre hi has estat, Hisao..."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7329
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_bright_sky_bc3b14d8:

    # hi "Why did you want to go to Scotland, Lilly?"
    hi "Per què volies tornar a Escòcia, Lilly?"

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7334
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_bright_sky_a49feb44:

    # li "Why…? I told you before: because Akira was going, and because of my family's summons to their home."
    li "Per què...? Ja t'ho vaig dir: perquè l'Akira hi anava i perquè la meva familia volia que tornés a casa."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7336
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_bright_sky_65ea5a14:

    # hi "Why didn't you say that you wanted to go?"
    hi "Per què no em vas dir que tu hi volies anar?"

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7341
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_bright_sky_46bf4748:

    # li "I—"
    li "Em—"

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7343
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_bright_sky_ceb456d9:

    # hi "I'm not stubborn often, but this one time I think I need to be. I want you to stay here, Lilly."
    hi "No solc ser tossut, però crec que aquesta vegada ho he de ser. Vull que et quedis, Lilly."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7345
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_bright_sky_14043a9f:

    # hi "I want you to stay where everyone you know lives, and where all your dreams and ambitions were made. If you choose to stay, I'll never leave your side. I won't let you lose another person."
    hi "Vull que et quedis on viuen tots els que t'estimen i on vas crear els teus somnis i ambicions. Si tries quedar-te, no marxaré mai del teu costat. No et deixaré que perdis cap altra persona."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7347
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_bright_sky_b19a9566:

    # hi "When I had my heart attack, I was snatched away from everyone and everywhere I knew. You showed me a new life after I came to Yamaku. I'd lost my past, but you showed me a future."
    hi "Quan vaig tenir l'atac de cor, em van apartar de tothom i de tot allò que coneixia. Em vas ensenyar una nova vida quan vaig arribar al Yamaku. Havia perdut el meu passat, però tu em vas ensenyar el futur."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7349
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_bright_sky_8e112973:

    # hi "It's true that I haven't always been there for you. I'm unreliable, sometimes I lied, and I thought I'd come to understand you when I hadn't even understood myself."
    hi "És cert que no sempre hi he estat per tu. No soc gaire de fiar, de vegades menteixo i  pensava que et podria entendre quan no m'entenc ni a mi mateix."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7351
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_bright_sky_200b9dc5:

    # hi "Be that as it may, I want to give you a future as well. I want to be there for you, to share both your burdens and your happiness, just like I promised back in Hokkaido."
    hi "Sigui com sigui, també et vull donar un futur. Vull ser-hi per tu, per compartir tant les teves càrregues com les teves alegries, tal com et vaig prometre a Hokkaido."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7353
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_bright_sky_b5c3a343:

    # hi "I want you to trust me. I know I had problems coming to put my trust in you, after losing so many people I'd known after my heart attack, but that's how I know that being unable to trust others can feel awful."
    hi "Vull que confiïs en mi. Sé que vaig tenir problemes per confiar en tu, després de perdre tanta gent que coneixia quan vaig patir l'atac de cor, però per això sé que no poder confiar en els altres és horrible."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7355
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_bright_sky_ea2e91e8:

    # hi "That's why I can't watch you just throw everything away like this. I never want you to go through what I did. I would do anything to stop that."
    hi "Per això no puc veure com et desfàs de tot d'aquesta manera. No vull que passis pel que jo vaig passar. Faria el que fos per evitar-ho."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7360
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_bright_sky_c514b58e:

    # li "You can be quite steadfast when you want to be, can't you?"
    li "Ets força tenaç quan t'ho proposes, oi que sí?"

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7362
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_bright_sky_4a6e6c2f:

    # hi "As I said, it isn't often."
    hi "Com t'he dit, no passa gaire sovint."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7364
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_bright_sky_4738ae2a:

    # "My weak smile drops, though, as the IV in my arm digs in a little. It's a harsh reminder of my tether to my condition."
    "Però el meu feble somriure es desvaneix quan la via intravenosa del braç se'm clava una mica. És un dur recordatori del meu lligam amb la meva malaltia."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7369
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_bright_sky_808b4975:

    # "Lilly's face tenses as I let out a small gasp of pain, immediately making me wish I'd stifled it better. All I can do is sigh in defeat."
    "La cara de la Lilly es tensa mentre deixo anar un petit crit de dolor, immediatament desitjo haver-lo reprimit millor. L'únic que puc fer és sospirar derrotat."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7371
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_bright_sky_751edab2:

    # hi "I tried to not let anyone worry over me for the entire time since I left the hospital, but I can't even stop the one person I love most from crying over me."
    hi "Vaig intentar que ningú es preocupés per mi durant tot aquest temps que he estat fora de l'hospital, però ni tan sols puc evitar fer plorar a la persona a qui més estimo."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7373
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_bright_sky_2563af23:

    # hi "Even if I might finally be able to put my feelings into words, I feel pretty useless with a body like this."
    hi "Fins i tot encara que pogués posar els meus sentiments en paraules, em sento força inútil amb un cos com aquest."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7375
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_bright_sky_ef9bdcb4:

    # hi "Every time I tried to reach towards something, it was just snatched away, and even now things only turned out for the better due to luck."
    hi "Cada vegada que intentava aconseguir alguna cosa, me l'arrabassaven, i fins i tot aquesta vegada les coses només han sortit bé gràcies a la sort."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7377
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_bright_sky_e3b3eabd:

    # hi "I guess that's something else I should apologize for. All I can ever do is make you worry. Even now, there's very little chance I'll live anywhere near a full life."
    hi "Suposo que és una altra cosa per la qual hauria de disculpar-me. Només faig que preocupar-te. Fins i tot ara, hi ha molt poques possibilitats que tingui una vida plena."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7379
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_bright_sky_5afa8a5d:

    # "The feeling of Lilly's warm, soft hand moving over my left cheek makes me lift my head up, her smile gentle and warm as she touches me."
    "La sensació de la mà càlida i suau de la Lilly acariciant-me la galta esquerra em fa aixecar el cap, té un somriure suau i càlid mentre em toca."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7384
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_bright_sky_6d551158:

    # li "I think that is something very natural for you to say. You were always so sincere and self-conscious."
    li "Crec que és molt normal que em diguis això. Sempre has estat molt sincer i amb consciència de tu mateix."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7389
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_bright_sky_b117571b:

    # li "You were also reserved and mild-mannered, and patient to a fault with Hanako, yet curious about everything and everyone."
    li "També has estat reservat i bondadós, i has tingut moltíssima paciència amb la Hanako, però també curiositat per tot i tothom."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7394
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_bright_sky_1f703d78:

    # li "When I said I missed you while I was with my family, I wasn't lying or exaggerating. The thought of you was never far from my mind, and helped me through that time."
    li "Quan et vaig dir que t'havia trobat a faltar quan estava amb la meva família, no t'estava mentint ni  ho estava exagerant. No te'm podia treure del cap i em va ajudar durant aquella època."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7399
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_bright_sky_1d26b862:

    # li "That's why I was so confused about what to do when my family summoned me. Even after I thought I had made my decision, you tried your hardest to challenge me about it."
    li "Per això estava tan confusa quan la meva família em va demanar que tornés. Tot i que pensava que havia pres la decisió, et vas entestar al màxim en fer-m'ho qüestionar."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7404
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_bright_sky_76aa2618:

    # li "I didn't confess to you out of pity or believing you were somehow different from what you are. I confessed because I never want to lose you, and want you to always be a part of my life, no matter what might change."
    li "No em vaig confessar pas per compassió o perquè penses que fossis diferent de com ets. Em vaig confessar perquè no et volia perdre i volia que sempre fossis part de la meva vida, encara que canviés."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7409
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_bright_sky_73f30b4d:

    # li "You are a very beautiful person, Hisao. Your heart changes none of that, so please, don't apologize for yourself any more."
    li "Ets meravellós, Hisao. I el teu cor no ho canvia pas, així que si us plau, no et disculpis més per ser com ets."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7411
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_bright_sky_dee756b4:

    # "For a long time, silence reigns in the room."
    "Durant molta estona, el silenci regna a l'habitació."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7413
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_bright_sky_93dc67c6:

    # "I'm not really sure what this newly born feeling inside of me is, but it pales into insignificance as I wordlessly gaze at Lilly's smiling face, warm and gentle as it has always been."
    "No sé molt bé què és aquest sentiment que m'acaba de néixer a dins, però em sembla insignificant mentre contemplo sense paraules la cara somrient de la Lilly, càlida i suau com sempre."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7415
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_bright_sky_cb20daf1:

    # "It's only as her thumb crosses my cheek, wiping away a single drop of moisture, that I realize this is all I've ever wanted."
    "Només quan em passa el polze per la galta, tot eixugant-me una gota, m'adono que això és tot el que sempre he volgut."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7417
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_bright_sky_2a3df162:

    # "For what feels like the first time, I give an earnest, wide smile. As Lilly feels it against her palm, she returns the gesture."
    "Per primera vegada, faig un somriure sincer i ampli. Quan la Lilly el nota contra el seu palmell, em torna el gest."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7419
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_bright_sky_4bb65f62:

    # "More time passes before either of us says a word, neither of us needing speech to communicate our feelings to each other."
    "Passa més temps abans que cap de nosaltres digui res, no ens cal parlar per comunicar-nos els nostres sentiments."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7421
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_bright_sky_eb258c44:

    # hi "I know I can't promise you that I'll always be around, or that we'll be together forever."
    hi "Sé que no et puc prometre que sempre estaré a prop, ni que estarem junts per sempre."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7423
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_bright_sky_bc0b9eac:

    # "With some difficulty I slowly lift my hand, placing it on her pale shoulder."
    "Amb certa dificultat, aixeco lentament la mà i la poso sobre la seva pàl·lida espatlla."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7425
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_bright_sky_db42220a:

    # hi "But… I think I can at least take you to next year's Tanabata festival, to make up for making you miss this year's."
    hi "Però... crec que com a mínim et puc portar al festival Tanabata de l'any que ve, per compensar-te que t'hagis perdut el d'aquest any."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7430
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_bright_sky_1cab9f01:

    # "Lilly's expression is one of surprise, though I can't say I blame her."
    "La Lilly fa cara de sorpresa, encara que no puc dir que la culpi."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7432
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_bright_sky_1c36c51f:

    # li "You… remembered that?"
    li "Te... n'has recordat?"

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7434
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_bright_sky_4d2f29f3:

    # hi "I've got a pretty good memory. Sometimes."
    hi "Tinc una memòria força bona. De vegades."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7439
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_bright_sky_77f751b8:

    # "She raises her head a little and takes her hand from my cheek, giving a small, amused giggle. I smile absentmindedly at how earnest it is, almost girlish in its lightness."
    "Aixeca una mica el cap i em treu la mà de la galta, tot deixant anar una rialleta. Somric distret per com n'és de sincera, quasi infantil, quan és ella mateixa."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7444
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_bright_sky_6a658df9:

    # "Still smiling warmly, she collects herself and stands upright with a hand resting on my chest."
    "Sense parar de somriure, es recompon i s'aixeca amb la mà que tinc recolzada al pit."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7446
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_bright_sky_e79f1df2:

    # "It feels like I'm seeing her for the first time, the sun from the window glowing behind her just as it did when I first walked into that room where she was drinking tea."
    "És com si l'estigués veient per primera vegada, amb el sol que entra per la finestra brillant darrere seu, igual que quan vaig entrar per primera vegada a aquella habitació on estava bevent te."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7451
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_bright_sky_dc7a5795:

    # li "Very well then. Shall we make it a promise between the both of us to go to next year's Tanabata together?"
    li "Doncs molt bé. Així que prometem anar junts al Tanabata de l'any que ve?"

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7453
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_bright_sky_29a2dfca:

    # "Even if she can't see me doing so, I nod approvingly."
    "Encara que no pugui veure'm, assenteixo amb el cap."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7455
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_bright_sky_4d336ac5:

    # hi "I promise."
    hi "T'ho prometo."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7460
translate ca a4_lilly_under_a_bright_sky_f5f40482:

    # li "I promise."
    li "T'ho prometo."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7475
translate ca a4_lilly_forwards_32b484c6:

    # "Akira, Lilly and I silently sit on the grassy embankment high above the local town, the breeze gently blowing through the cloudless sky."
    "Akira, Lilly i jo seiem en silenci sobre un terraplè cobert d'herba amb vistes a la ciutat, bufa un ventet suau en un cel sense núvols."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7477
translate ca a4_lilly_forwards_759b72d6:

    # "We may be just a few minutes' walk from town, on a hill just outside its limits, but the view is entirely unexpected."
    "Pot ser que estiguem a pocs minuts caminant de la ciutat, en un turó just fora dels seus límits, però la vista és totalment inesperada."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7484
translate ca a4_lilly_forwards_859b56a1:

    # "Lilly sits beside me, her eyes closed, as the gentle breeze flows through her hair."
    "La Lilly s'asseu al meu costat i tanca els ulls, mentre la suau brisa flueix a través dels seus cabells."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7486
translate ca a4_lilly_forwards_7e54d1ec:

    # li "This is a nice area."
    li "Aquest és un bon lloc."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7488
translate ca a4_lilly_forwards_13a0a390:

    # hi "Yeah. I never knew a place like this was anywhere near Yamaku."
    hi "Sí. No sabia que hi hagués un lloc així tan a prop del Yamaku."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7495
translate ca a4_lilly_forwards_63e34fca:

    # aki "And I had to be the one to find it, of course."
    aki "És clar, l'havia de trobar jo."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7497
translate ca a4_lilly_forwards_e5b35ad2:

    # "Akira's grin is genuine, but her tone is slightly different from her usual carefree nature."
    "El somriure de l'Akira és genuí, però el seu to és lleugerament diferent de la seva naturalesa despreocupada habitual."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7502
translate ca a4_lilly_forwards_4dcd163f:

    # aki "It's good that you're outta the hospital though, Hisao."
    aki "M'alegro de saber que ja has sortit de l'hospital."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7504
translate ca a4_lilly_forwards_ae4a6915:

    # hi "Nobody's more glad than I am. I can't stand hospitals."
    hi "Ningú se n'alegra més que jo. No suporto els hospitals."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7506
translate ca a4_lilly_forwards_30595a73:

    # aki "So, you two going back to the school tomorrow?"
    aki "Així doncs, demà torneu a l'escola?"

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7513
translate ca a4_lilly_forwards_faf814a9:

    # "Akira chuckles in amusement before looking back out to the town below, the trees between the buildings swaying in the wind."
    "L'Akira es diverteix abans de mirar enrere cap a la ciutat que hi ha a baix, on els arbres entre els edificis es mouen amb el vent."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7515
translate ca a4_lilly_forwards_baf399b9:

    # hi "Pity we couldn't go up north for the summer holidays, or get to Tanabata."
    hi "Quina llàstima no haver pogut anar al nord a passar les vacances d'estiu, ni anar al Tanabata."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7520
translate ca a4_lilly_forwards_86fbe80f:

    # li "I wouldn't worry, there's always next time."
    li "No et preocupis, ho farem la propera."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7525
translate ca a4_lilly_forwards_ebaa5ca8:

    # aki "You'll be graduating before the next summer vacation, won't ya?"
    aki "Us gradueu abans de les pròximes vacances d'estiu, oi que sí?"

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7527
translate ca a4_lilly_forwards_f11b50fd:

    # hi "Yeah. There'll still be college after that, mind."
    hi "Sí. I després vindrà la universitat."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7529
translate ca a4_lilly_forwards_f327c455:

    # aki "Going to the same one?"
    aki "Anireu a la mateixa?"

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7534
translate ca a4_lilly_forwards_29dc8af0:

    # li "Likely. We both have high enough scores to meet the entry requirements."
    li "És possible. Tots dos tenim prou nota per poder-hi entrar."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7536
translate ca a4_lilly_forwards_48f749d6:

    # hi "You sound so sure…"
    hi "Sembles molt segura..."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7541
translate ca a4_lilly_forwards_58a7f7af:

    # li "Don't worry, you're better than I in most subjects."
    li "No et preocupis, ets millor que jo en moltes assignatures."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7543
translate ca a4_lilly_forwards_2bc2a90a:

    # hi "I guess we'll work it out in due time."
    hi "Suposo que ho solucionarem quan toqui."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7548
translate ca a4_lilly_forwards_26fdd67d:

    # aki "That's the way. Just enjoy yourselves in Yamaku while you're there."
    aki "Aquesta és l'actitud. Gaudiu del Yamaku mentre encara hi sou."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7553
translate ca a4_lilly_forwards_c3ddac0a:

    # "Lilly gives a sad sigh at the distinction made between Akira and the two of us."
    "La Lilly fa un sospir trist per la distinció que es fa entre l'Akira i nosaltres dos."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7558
translate ca a4_lilly_forwards_aee035fb:

    # li "Do you really need to go back to Scotland?"
    li "De debò has de tornar a Escòcia?"

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7563
translate ca a4_lilly_forwards_227b7ac8:

    # aki "Yeah. The folks are already out for my blood as it is."
    aki "Sí. Els meus pares ja em van al darrere."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7565
translate ca a4_lilly_forwards_ce116c03:

    # hi "You weren't meant to stay this long?"
    hi "No se suposava que et quedaries tan de temps?"

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7570
translate ca a4_lilly_forwards_7422dd8c:

    # "She gives her trademark wide grin."
    "Fa el seu somriure característic d'orella a orella."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7572
translate ca a4_lilly_forwards_666cc35e:

    # aki "Setting my boyfriend up with a passport took some time."
    aki "He trigat a aconseguir un passaport pel meu xicot."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7574
translate ca a4_lilly_forwards_ca2ffc34:

    # hi "You're taking him with you?"
    hi "Te l'emportaràs amb tu?"

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7579
translate ca a4_lilly_forwards_f31f27ae:

    # aki "Just for a while at first. He's a surprisingly worldly guy, so I think he'll do just fine."
    aki "Al principi, només una temporada. És un noi sorprenentment mundà, així que ja se'n sortirà."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7584
translate ca a4_lilly_forwards_0dbabcee:

    # "Akira gives an amused snort."
    "L'Akira riu per sota el nas."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7586
translate ca a4_lilly_forwards_4f150076:

    # aki "If our father had his way, I'd have gone a long while ago."
    aki "Si el nostre pare se n'hagués sortit, faria temps que me n'hauria anat."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7591
translate ca a4_lilly_forwards_0eb9e2c2:

    # aki "I just couldn't pass up an excuse to stay with my favorite little sister a little while longer though."
    aki "No podia deixar estar aquesta excusa per poder estar una mica més amb la meva germana petita preferida."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7596
translate ca a4_lilly_forwards_25edef44:

    # "She leans right and gives Lilly a tight playful hug, cheering her up considerably."
    "S'inclina cap a la dreta i li fa una abraçada trapella a la Lilly, que l'anima considerablement."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7598
translate ca a4_lilly_forwards_e77f4e77:

    # li "It's nice to be with you one last time, though."
    li "És agradable estar amb tu una última vegada."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7600
translate ca a4_lilly_forwards_68e4b766:

    # hi "For what it's worth, I'm in the same boat."
    hi "Per si et serveix, penso el mateix."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7605
translate ca a4_lilly_forwards_12678f27:

    # aki "Heh, thanks you two. I'll try and come back sometime, don't worry."
    aki "Heh, gràcies, parella. Intentaré tornar de tant en tant, no us preocupeu."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7610
translate ca a4_lilly_forwards_fa3a483c:

    # li "It's a shame that the business keeps you so busy."
    li "És una pena que el negoci et tingui tan ocupada."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7615
translate ca a4_lilly_forwards_a8f58acf:

    # aki "The place won't run itself, I'm afraid, and I think it's going to be just the same over there."
    aki "Per desgràcia l'empresa no funcionarà sola, i crec que passarà el mateix allà. "

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7620
translate ca a4_lilly_forwards_ae1fd58d:

    # aki "Considering that, I'd better get going."
    aki "Ara que hi penso, serà millor que vagi tirant."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7622
translate ca a4_lilly_forwards_207b4960:

    # hi "Have fun over there, Akira."
    hi "Que t'ho passis bé, Akira."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7627
translate ca a4_lilly_forwards_24e6f4bb:

    # aki "Haha, will do."
    aki "Haha, ho faré."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7632
translate ca a4_lilly_forwards_9ffafc9f:

    # "With a slight grunt, she lifts herself with her hands and stands up, dusting herself off as she does so."
    "Amb un esbufec, s'aixeca amb les mans i es posa dempeus, tot espolsant-se mentre ho fa."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7637
translate ca a4_lilly_forwards_cab22f6b:

    # aki "Well, I'd better be off. The plane won't wait for me, after all."
    aki "Bé, ja marxo. L'avió no m'esperarà pas només a mi."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7639
translate ca a4_lilly_forwards_58dcaa66:

    # "She has a certain unusual wistfulness in the tone of her voice, her eyes firmly planted on her sister."
    "Té una certa nostàlgia inusual en el seu to de veu, amb els ulls fixes a la seva germana."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7644
translate ca a4_lilly_forwards_d308e549:

    # li "I'll be okay, Akira."
    li "Estaré bé, Akira."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7649
translate ca a4_lilly_forwards_d8c6d600:

    # aki "Yeah, I know."
    aki "Sí, ho sé."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7654
translate ca a4_lilly_forwards_8064020e:

    # li "Come now, it isn't that bad. You'll be able to see us again soon."
    li "Au va, no és tan dolent. Ens podrem tornar a trobar aviat."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7656
translate ca a4_lilly_forwards_3aa32cdd:

    # "It is strange to have Lilly reassuring a doubting Akira for once. She really has changed."
    "És estrany que Lilly tranquil·litzi a la dubitativa Akira per una vegada. Ha canviat de debò."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7661
translate ca a4_lilly_forwards_6e80cf90:

    # li "Goodbye, Akira."
    li "Que vagi bé, Akira."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7663
translate ca a4_lilly_forwards_541372ee:

    # hi "'Bye."
    hi "Deu."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7668
translate ca a4_lilly_forwards_0a7d0e30:

    # "For a second, the dark-clad figure looks down at the both of us, smiling widely. Perhaps more widely than I've ever seen her do before."
    "Per un segon, la figura vestida de negre ens mira a tots dos, somrient àmpliament. Potser més àmpliament del que l'havia vist fer-ho abans."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7673
translate ca a4_lilly_forwards_8c32386f:

    # "She lets out a long, slightly wavering breath to steady herself before leaving, but eventually slips her hand in her pocket and turns on her heel."
    "Deixa anar un sospir llarg i lleugerament vacil·lant per calmar-se abans de marxar, però finalment es posa la mà a la butxaca i es gira sobre el taló."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7675
translate ca a4_lilly_forwards_56707843:

    # "And with that she walks away, one hand held in the air as she goes."
    "I se'n va amb una mà en l'aire."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7680
translate ca a4_lilly_forwards_2af6c6d9:

    # aki "Seeya later, you two!"
    aki "Fins aviat, parella!"

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7685
translate ca a4_lilly_forwards_4340d6dd:

    # "A jazz tune with no beat, melody or direction to the very end."
    "Una pista de jazz sense ritme, melodia ni direcció fins al final."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7691
translate ca a4_lilly_forwards_04e076ec:

    # "After a few moments of sitting silently, Lilly and I pick ourselves up and dust ourselves off."
    "Després d'uns instants asseguts en silenci, la Lilly i jo ens aixequem i ens espolsem."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7693
translate ca a4_lilly_forwards_1f4f26c5:

    # "Turning towards her with a broad smile, I hold out my hand."
    "Em giro cap a ella amb un ampli somriure, i li dono la mà."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7695
translate ca a4_lilly_forwards_40d81eda:

    # hi "Shall we be off, then?"
    hi "Marxem nosaltres també?"

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7697
translate ca a4_lilly_forwards_2fcd2c1a:

    # "She takes my hand in hers, with a gentle nod and a smile as beautiful and warm as ever."
    "M'agafa la mà, amb un assentiment suau i un somriure tan bonic i càlid com sempre."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7702
translate ca a4_lilly_forwards_2bc0fa66:

    # li "Indeed we shall, Hisao."
    li "I tant que sí, Hisao."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7719
translate ca a4_lilly_forwards_e9b18efc:

    # "As we set off towards the school, that wonderful smile engraves itself onto my memory. That wonderful smile that we both share."
    "Mentre ens dirigim cap a l'escola, aquest meravellós somriure se'm grava a la meva memòria. Aquest somriure meravellós que tots dos compartim."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7721
translate ca a4_lilly_forwards_186821f2:

    # "Our pasts may be scattered and at times overshadowed by sadness, but they're also an irrevocable part of our lives and personalities. Even if I could change a single thing, I wouldn't, because my past was what led me here."
    "Els nostres passats poden estar escampats i de vegades ser eclipsats per la tristesa, però també són una part irrevocable de les nostres vides i personalitats. Fins i tot si pogués canviar una sola cosa, no ho faria, perquè el meu passat va ser el que em va portar aquí."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7723
translate ca a4_lilly_forwards_7a9b305a:

    # "That's why, even with all that's happened to us before, and all that may well befall us… together, we'll keep walking forwards."
    "Per això, fins i tot amb tot el que ens ha passat abans, i tot el que ens pot passar... junts, seguirem endavant."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7725
translate ca a4_lilly_forwards_84586c45:

    # "Forwards… towards the future. Our future."
    "Endavant... cap al futur. El nostre futur."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7741
translate ca a4lc1o1_2d538351:

    # "The memory of that single letter Iwanako sent me comes back to my mind."
    "El record d'aquella carta que em va enviar la Iwanako em torna al cap."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7743
translate ca a4lc1o1_1b64d9c8:

    # hi "I never saw her again, but after I was sent to Yamaku… she wrote me one letter."
    hi "No l'he tornat a veure, però després de venir al Yamaku... em va escriure una carta."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7745
translate ca a4lc1o1_28001435:

    # "Lilly's face shows an expression I know well. I've piqued her interest. I'd be slightly offended that it's simply a matter of curiosity for her, but she's never been very good at masking her reactions."
    "La cara de la Lilly mostra una expressió que conec bé. He despertat el seu interès. M'ofendria una mica que fos simplement curiositat, però mai ha estat molt bona dissimulant les seves reaccions."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7747
translate ca a4lc1o1_2ee1611d:

    # hi "In hindsight, it really didn't say much. What was going on in my old class, how she was faring, and, almost as an afterthought, that it was probably best for the both of us that we don't see each other again."
    hi "En retrospectiva, realment no deia gaire. Què passava a la meva antiga classe, com li anava i, quasi com una reflexió, que era millor per tots dos que no ens tornéssim a veure mai més."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7749
translate ca a4lc1o1_5114d9f3:

    # hi "After reading it, I ended up reassessing a lot of things I thought I'd managed to work out. For the most part, that letter reminded me that the world around me was still moving, and just how much I'd become isolated from it."
    hi "Després de llegir-la, vaig acabar replantejant-me moltes coses que pensava que havia pogut solucionar. En gran part, aquella carta em va recordar que el món que m'envoltava continuava movent-se i que jo me n'havia aïllat."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7751
translate ca a4lc1o1_479782a2:

    # hi "And… I guess it also reminded me of what I'd lost."
    hi "I... suposo que també em va fer pensar en tot allò que m'havia perdut."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7756
translate ca a4lc1o1_7170cfd4:

    # "She gives the information some thought before her face lights up in realization. No doubt she's worked out that it was this letter which had contributed to my angst during that lunch on the rooftop."
    "Es queda pensativa abans que se li il·lumini la cara. Sens dubte, ha deduït que va ser aquesta carta la que va contribuir a la meva angoixa durant aquell dinar al terrat."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7758
translate ca a4lc1o1_77e457b9:

    # "It's a rare sight to see Lilly quite so lost for words, her entire persona is a little deflated from her earlier rapt interest. As charismatic as she is, in the end that isn't any replacement for life nor relationship experience."
    "És estrany veure la Lilly tan perduda, tota la seva personalitat està una mica desinflada respecte al seu anterior interès. Per molt carismàtica que sigui, al final això no és cap substitut de la vida ni de l'experiència en les relacions."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7763
translate ca a4lc1o1_f3f6e046:

    # li "Perhaps… it is better she sent it than not."
    li "Potser... va fer bé enviant-te aquella carta."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7765
translate ca a4lc1o1_53d71943:

    # hi "How's that?"
    hi "Què vols dir?"

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7770
translate ca a4lc1o1_0dd32b00:

    # li "It can be difficult to work out how best to communicate with those you haven't met in a long time. All the more so, considering your separate situations."
    li "Pot ser difícil trobar la millora manera de comunicar-te amb algú que fa temps que no veus. I més si tenim en compte que cadascú està en una situació diferent."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7772
translate ca a4lc1o1_ac0cb886:

    # li "Instead of doing what was easiest, she built up the courage to talk to you one last time; not only for her sake but, from how it sounds, for yours as well."
    li "En comptes de fer allò que era més fàcil, va armar-se de coratge per parlar amb tu una última vegada; no només pel seu bé, sinó també pel teu."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7774
translate ca a4lc1o1_5ee637ed:

    # hi "Maybe. I don't hate her for it, not that I really ever did, but… I don't know."
    hi "Podria ser. No l'odio pas per això, de fer no l'he odiat mai, però... no ho sé."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7776
translate ca a4lc1o1_facdac89:

    # "Probably a more noncommittal answer than I should give, but it isn't without cause. I've never looked at the situation from Iwanako's perspective like that before."
    "Probablement és una resposta més evasiva de la que hauria de donar, però no està exempta de causa. Mai havia mirat la situació des de la perspectiva de la Iwanako."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7781
translate ca a4lc1o2_27b3240a:

    # "I really don't want to bring up Iwanako any more than necessary. This date is, after all, for me and Lilly. I don't want to think about a previous relationship at a time like this."
    "No vull treure el tema de la Iwanako més del necessari. Al cap i a la fi, aquesta cita és per a mi i per a la Lilly. No vull pensar en una relació anterior en un moment com aquest."

# game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7783
translate ca a4lc1o2_71883ef2:

    # hi "No, that was the last I saw of her. We never talked again, either."
    hi "No, això va ser l'últim que vaig saber d'ella. No hem tornat a parlar mai més."

translate ca strings:

    # game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:2147
    old "Wrapped in my own little world, I shake my head before remembering the futility of the gesture."
    new "Embolicat en el meu petit món, sacsejo el cap abans de recordar que aquest gest no serveix de res."

    # game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:2147
    old "Mention the letter."
    new "Esmenta la carta."

    # game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:2147
    old "Drop the subject."
    new "Deixa estar el tema."

    # game/script-a4-lilly.rpy:7508
    old "Yup."
    new "Síp."

